#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; is an advanced network neighborhood browser and <ulink url=\"http://"
"www.samba.org\">Samba</ulink> share mounting utility. It provides many handy "
"features that ease your life in a &Windows;-dominated network environment."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; je napreden brskalnik omrežne soseske in pripomoček za priklop "
"skupnih virov <ulink url=\"http://www.samba.org\">Samba</ulink>. Ponuja "
"številne priročne zmožnosti, ki vam olajšajo življenje v omrežnem okolju, "
"kjer prevladuje &Windows;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This handbook describes &smb4k; 4.0.5 and later. To some extent, it is also "
"correct for earlier versions."
msgstr ""
"Ta priročnik opisuje &smb4k; 4.0.5 in novejše različice. Do neke mere velja "
"tudi za starejše različice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In 2025, several security vulnerabilities were found in the KAuth mount "
"helper program (see the <ulink url=\"https://security.opensuse."
"org/2025/12/10/smb4k-major-issues-in-kauth-helper.html\">report</ulink> by "
"the SUSE Security Team) and were fixed in version 4.0.5. Since the feature "
"set for mounts and unmounts has been restricted, these security improvements "
"have a noticeable impact on the entire program."
msgstr ""
"Leta 2025 je bilo v programu za pomoč pri priklopu KAuth odkritih več "
"varnostnih ranljivosti (glejte <ulink url=\"https://security.opensuse."
"org/2025/12/10/smb4k-major-issues-in-kauth-helper.html\">poročilo</ulink> "
"varnostne ekipe SUSE), ki so bile odpravljene v različici 4.0.5. Ker je bil "
"nabor zmožnosti za priklope in odklope omejen, imajo te varnostne izboljšave "
"opazen vpliv na celoten program."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "&smb4k; has got the following features:"
msgstr "&smb4k; je dobil naslednje zmožnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scanning for (active) workgroups, hosts, and shares using &Samba;'s client "
"library, DNS Service Discovery (DNS-SD) and, optionally, Web Services "
"Dynamic Discovery (WS-Discovery)"
msgstr ""
"Prečesavanje (aktivnih) delovnih skupin, gostiteljev in deljenih skupnih "
"virov z uporabo odjemalske knjižnice &Samba;, odkrivanja storitev DNS (DNS-"
"SD) in po izbiri dinamičnega odkrivanja spletnih storitev (WS-Discovery)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Support of the &CIFS; and &SMB3; file system under &Linux; as well as the "
"SMBFS file system under BSD"
msgstr ""
"Podpora &CIFS; in &SMB3; datotečnih sistemov pod &Linux; kot tudi datotečnih "
"sistemov SMBFS pod BSD"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mounting and unmounting of shares"
msgstr "Priklop in odklop deljenih skupnih diskov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Access to the files of a mounted share using a file manager or terminal"
msgstr ""
"Dostop do datotek priklopljenih skupnih diskov z uporabo upravitelja datotek "
"ali terminala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto-detection of external mounts and unmounts"
msgstr "Samodejno zaznavanje zunanjih priklopov in odklopov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remounting of previously used shares on program start"
msgstr ""
"Ponovna namestitev predhodno uporabljenih skupnih virov ob zagonu programa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Various information about remote network items and mounted shares"
msgstr ""
"Razne informacije o oddaljenih omrežnih elementih in priklopljenih skupnih "
"virih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Network search"
msgstr "Iskanje omrežja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview of the contents of a remote share"
msgstr "Predogled vsebine oddaljenih skupnih diskov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default login"
msgstr "Privzeta prijava"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Special handling of home shares"
msgstr "Posebna obravnava domačih skupnih diskov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ability to bookmark favorite shares"
msgstr "Možnost označevanja priljubljenih skupnih diskov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>System tray widget</para>"
msgstr "<para>Gradnik sistemske vrstice</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Support of selected mount options"
msgstr "Podpora za izbrane možnosti priklopa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Support of printer shares"
msgstr "Podpora za skupno rabo tiskalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Support of several secure storage solutions for the login credentials via "
"QtKeychain"
msgstr ""
"Podpora več varnih rešitev za shranjevanje poverilnic za prijavo prek "
"QtKeychain"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronization of a remote share with a local copy, and vice versa"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija oddaljenih skupnih diskov z lokalno kopijo in obratno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ability to define custom settings for individual servers and shares"
msgstr ""
"Možnost določanja nastavitev po meri za posamezne strežnike in skupne diske"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hardware support through the &solid; device integration framework, the "
"&kdbusaddons; convenience classes and the &Qt; Network module"
msgstr ""
"Podpora za strojno opremo prek &solid; ogrodje za integracijo naprav, "
"&kdbusaddons; priročni razredi in &Qt; Omrežni modul"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wake-On-LAN capabilities"
msgstr "Zmogljivosti Wake-On-LAN"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "&plasmoid; for desktop integration"
msgstr "&plasmoid; za integracijo namizja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Profiles for different network neighborhood setups"
msgstr "Profili za različne nastavitve omrežne soseščine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you encounter problems while using &smb4k;, please post a help request to "
"our <ulink url=\"https://sourceforge.net/p/smb4k/discussion/help/\">Help</"
"ulink> forum. In case you find a bug, please report it to our <ulink url="
"\"https://bugs.kde.org/enter_bug.cgi?format=guided&amp;product=smb4k\">bug "
"tracker</ulink>. For discussions about &smb4k;-related topics, there is the "
"<ulink url=\"https://sourceforge.net/p/smb4k/discussion/general/\">General "
"Discussion</ulink> forum, and we invite every user to participate."
msgstr ""
"Če med uporabo &smb4k; naletite na težave, objavite zahtevo za pomoč na "
"našem forumu <ulink url=\"https://sourceforge.net/p/smb4k/discussion/help/"
"\">Pomoč</ulink>. Če najdete napako, jo prijavite našemu <ulink url="
"\"https://bugs.kde.org/enter_bug.cgi?format=guided&amp;product=smb4k"
"\">sledilniku napak</ulink>. Za razprave o temah, povezanih z &smb4k;, "
"obstaja forum <ulink url=\"https://sourceforge.net/p/smb4k/discussion/"
"general/\">Splošna razprava</ulink>, k sodelovanju pa vabimo vse uporabnike ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &smb4k;"
msgstr "Uporaba &smb4k;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Running &smb4k;"
msgstr "Poganjanje &smb4k;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can either launch &smb4k; from the <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/"
"Plasma/Kickoff\">application launcher</ulink> or from <ulink url=\"https://"
"userbase.kde.org/Plasma/Krunner\">&krunner;</ulink> by typing "
"<userinput><command>smb4k</command></userinput>. &smb4k; comes with a <link "
"linkend=\"plasmoid\">&plasmoid;</link> for better desktop integration that "
"can be added as a widget to the desktop or panel."
msgstr ""
"Lahko zaženete &smb4k; iz <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Plasma/"
"Kickoff\">zaganjalnika aplikacij</ulink> ali iz <ulink url=\"https://"
"userbase.kde.org/Plasma/Krunner\"> &krunner;</ulink> tako, da vnesete "
"<userinput><command>smb4k</command></userinput>. &smb4k; prihaja z <link "
"linkend=\"plasmoid\">&plasmoid;om</link> za boljšo integracijo namizja. "
"Lahko ga dodate kot gradnik na namizje ali ploščo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &smb4k; encounters a problem on start-up or while running, the user will "
"be notified. For the solution of some common problems see the <link linkend="
"\"trouble_shooting\">Trouble Shooting</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Če &smb4k; naleti na težavo ob zagonu ali med delovanjem, bo uporabnik "
"obveščen. Za rešitev nekaterih pogostih težav glejte razdelek <link linkend="
"\"trouble_shooting\">Odpravljanje težav</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main Window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the first start-up, the main window of &smb4k; looks similar to the one "
"shown below. The network neighborhood browser (<guilabel>Network "
"Neighborhood</guilabel>) and the mounted shares view (<guilabel>Mounted "
"Shares</guilabel>) are arranged in tabs. Above them the menu bar and tool "
"bar are located, and below them there is the status bar."
msgstr ""
"Ob prvem zagonu je glavno okno &smb4k; podobno spodaj prikazanemu. Brskalnik "
"omrežne soseščine (<guilabel>Omrežna soseščina</guilabel>) in pogled "
"priklopljenih skupnih virov (<guilabel>Priklopljeni skupni viri</guilabel>) "
"sta urejena v zavihkih. Nad njima se nahajata menijska in orodna vrstica, "
"pod njima pa statusna vrstica."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the main window"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona glavnega okna"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tool bar contains some of the main actions, like <guimenuitem>Configure "
"&smb4k;</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>. It also "
"dynamically loads the actions of the dock widget that currently has the "
"focus. For additional information, please take a look at the sections "
"discussing the <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser\">network "
"neighborhood browser</link> and <link linkend=\"shares_view\">mounted shares "
"view</link>, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica vsebuje nekaj glavnih dejanj, kot sta "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &smb4k;</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Zapri</"
"guimenuitem>. Prav tako dinamično naloži dejanja pripomočka dok, ki ima "
"trenutno fokus. Za dodatne informacije si oglejte razdelke, ki obravnavajo "
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser\">brskalnik omrežne soseščine</"
"link> oziroma <link linkend=\"shares_view\">pogled priklopljenih skupnih "
"virov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar provides some information about the current status of "
"&smb4k;. If the application is processing a user request (&eg; mounting a "
"share), a descriptive message is displayed in the leftmost section and a "
"progress bar is shown with a busy indicator. The icon on the right side "
"indicates whether shares are mounted."
msgstr ""
"Statusna vrstica nudi nekaj informacij o trenutnem stanju &smb4k;. Če "
"aplikacija obdeluje zahtevo uporabnika (&eg; priklapljanje skupnega vira), "
"se v skrajnem levem delu prikaže opisno sporočilo in vrstica napredka z "
"indikatorjem zasedenosti. Ikona na desni strani označuje, ali so skupni viri "
"priklopljeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the dock widgets are arranged as tabs, the user gets additional visual "
"feedback. Each time a share is mounted or unmounted, the <guilabel>Mounted "
"Shares</guilabel> tab is highlighted for a few seconds."
msgstr ""
"Če so sidrni pripomočki za priklop razporejeni kot zavihki, uporabnik dobi "
"dodatne vizualne povratne informacije. Vsakič, ko je skupni vir priklopljen "
"ali odklopljen, je za nekaj sekund označen zavihek <guilabel>Priklopljeni "
"skupni viri</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main window is highly configurable. You can hide or show all tabbed "
"widgets via <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dock "
"Widgets</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. They can also be dragged around with the "
"mouse and docked to different areas in the main window. You can even detach "
"them from the main window. The status bar and the tool bar can be hidden or "
"shown by toggling the menu entry <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Toolbar</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Glavno okno je zelo prilagodljivo. Vse gradnike z zavihki lahko skrijete ali "
"prikažete prek <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sidrni "
"gradniki</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prav tako jih lahko povlečete z miško "
"in zasidrate na različna področja v glavnem oknu. Lahko jih celo ločite od "
"glavnega okna. Vrstico stanja in orodno vrstico lahko skrijete ali prikažete "
"tako, da preklopite menijski vnos <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži vrstico stanja</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži orodno vrstico</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Network Neighborhood Browser"
msgstr "Brskalnik omrežne soseščine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Network Neighborhood</guilabel> browser contains all network "
"items &#8212; &ie; domains or workgroups, servers, and shares &#8212; "
"&smb4k; was able to find. They are organized in a network tree, which you "
"can navigate through by either clicking on the control next to the item's "
"name or by executing the item itself."
msgstr ""
"Brskalnik <guilabel>Omrežna soseščina</guilabel> vsebuje vse omrežne "
"elemente &#8212; &ie; domene ali delovne skupine, strežnikov in skupne rabe "
"&#8212; &smb4k; kar mu je uspelo najti. Organizirani so v omrežnem drevesu, "
"po katerem se lahko pomikate s klikom na kontrolnik poleg imena elementa ali "
"z izvajanjem samega elementa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the network tree, the master browser in each workgroup or domain is "
"highlighted by a blue font color, if it was detected (&eg; when using DNS-"
"SD, the master browser of a &Windows; domain is not recognized). Mounted "
"shares are marked with the respective folder icon and an italic font."
msgstr ""
"V drevesu omrežja je glavni brskalnik v vsaki delovni skupini ali domeni "
"označen z modro barvo pisave, če je bil zaznan (&eg;. pri uporabi DNS-SD "
"glavni brskalnik domene &Windows; ni prepoznan). Priklopljeni skupni viri so "
"označeni z ustrezno ikono mape in ležečo pisavo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the network neighborhood browser"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona brskalnika omrežne soseščine"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "The network neighborhood browser"
msgstr "Brskalnik omrežne soseščine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The selection of multiple network items is supported. So, it is possible to "
"&eg; mount or preview several shares at once."
msgstr ""
"Podprta je izbira več omrežnih elementov. Torej je možno &eg;. namestitev "
"ali predogled več skupnih virov hkrati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing"
msgstr "Brskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; automatically scans the network neighborhood for active workgroups "
"and domains on start-up, and presents them in the network neighborhood "
"browser. For this purpose it uses &Samba;'s client library, <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zero-configuration_networking#DNS-SD\">DNS "
"Service Discovery (DNS-SD)</ulink> and, optionally, <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/WS-Discovery\">Web Services Dynamic Discovery (WS-"
"Discovery)</ulink>. The way &smb4k; browses the network neighborhood can be "
"adjusted on the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_network_basic_settings_browse_settings"
"\"><guilabel>Network</guilabel> configuration page</link>."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; ob zagonu samodejno pregleda omrežno sosesko za aktivne delovne "
"skupine in domene ter jih predstavi v brskalniku omrežne soseske. V ta namen "
"uporablja odjemalsko knjižnico &Samba;, <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Zero-configuration_networking#DNS-SD\">DNS Service Discovery (DNS-"
"SD)</ulink> in po želji <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WS-"
"Discovery\">Dinamično odkrivanje spletnih storitev (WS-Discovery)</ulink>. "
"Način &smb4k; brskanje po omrežni soseščini lahko prilagodite na <link "
"linkend=\"configuration_page_network_basic_settings_browse_settings"
"\"><guilabel>Omrežje</guilabel> strani za konfiguracijo</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; uses a traditional scan mode, where initially only workgroups and "
"domains are looked up and scans are only made when necessary &#8212; &ie;, "
"when you execute a network item. Due to the use of DNS-SD, you will most "
"likely find a domain called <emphasis>LOCAL</emphasis> in the network "
"neighborhood browser. This is the default local DNS domain used by services "
"like <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Avahi_(software)\">Avahi</"
"ulink> and not an actual &Windows; domain. Opening a domain or workgroup "
"item shows the servers belonging to it. If you want to access the shares of "
"one of the servers, you need to open the desired server."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; uporablja tradicionalni način prečesavanja, kjer se na začetku "
"iščejo samo delovne skupine in domene, pregledi pa se izvajajo le, ko je to "
"potrebno &#8212; &ie;, ko izvedete omrežni element. Zaradi uporabe DNS-SD "
"boste najverjetneje našli domeno z imenom <emphasis>LOCAL</emphasis> v "
"brskalniku omrežne soseščine. To je privzeta lokalna domena DNS, ki jo "
"uporabljajo storitve, kot je <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Avahi_(software)\">Avahi</ulink> in ne dejanska domena &Windows;. Odpiranje "
"elementa domene ali delovne skupine prikaže strežnike, ki ji pripadajo. Če "
"želite dostopati do skupnih diskov enega od strežnikov, morate odpreti "
"želeni strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using DNS Service Discovery and the Zeroconf daemon (Avahi) is "
"not running, &smb4k; shows an error notification. For details see the <link "
"linkend=\"trouble_shooting_zeroconf\">Trouble Shooting</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate odkrivanje storitev DNS in se demon Zeroconf (Avahi) ne "
"izvaja, &smb4k; prikaže obvestilo o napaki. Za podrobnosti glejte razdelek "
"<link linkend=\"trouble_shooting_zeroconf\">Odpravljanje težav</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also the possibility to wake up sleeping servers prior to scanning "
"the network neighborhood (Wake-On-LAN). If this feature is enabled, &smb4k; "
"sends a magic packet to each server that is to be awakened, then waits the "
"defined time until it starts to look up the workgroups and domains. The Wake-"
"On-LAN setting can be turned on in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_network_advanced_settings_wake_on_lan\">configuration "
"dialog</link>. The servers that should be awakened must be defined in the "
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_defining_custom_settings"
"\">Custom Settings</link> editor."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja tudi možnost, da prebudite speče strežnike pred prečesavanjem "
"omrežne soseske (Wake-On-LAN). Če je ta funkcija omogočena, &smb4k; pošlje "
"čarobni paket vsakemu strežniku, ki ga je treba prebuditi, nato pa počaka "
"določen čas, dokler ne začne iskati delovne skupine in domene. Nastavitev "
"Wake-On-LAN lahko vklopite v <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_network_advanced_settings_wake_on_lan\">pogovornem oknu "
"za konfiguracijo</link>. Strežnike, ki jih je treba prebuditi, je treba "
"določiti v urejevalniku <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_defining_custom_settings\">Nastavitve po "
"meri</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching"
msgstr "Iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To search the network neighborhood for shares that contain a certain search "
"item, execute the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Search</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> action (see also the <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_actions_popup_menu\">Actions and Popup Menu</"
"link> section below). The search tool bar opens at the bottom of the network "
"neighborhood browser."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v omrežni soseščini poiskati skupne diske, ki vsebujejo določen "
"iskalni element, izvedite <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; Dejanje <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>Iskanje</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (glejte tudi "
"razdelek <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_actions_popup_menu"
"\">Dejanja in pojavni meni</link> spodaj). Iskalna orodna vrstica se odpre "
"na dnu brskalnika omrežne soseščine."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Screenshot of the network neighborhood browser with visible search tool bar"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona brskalnika omrežne soseščine z vidno iskalno orodno vrstico"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "The network neighborhood browser with visible search tool bar"
msgstr "Brskalnik omrežne soseščine z vidno iskalno orodno vrstico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the search term in the line edit and press the &Enter; key, or click "
"the <guibutton>Search</guibutton> button. &smb4k; starts to search the "
"entire network neighborhood. When the search is finished, all shares "
"matching the search term are highlighted (selected). If you would like to do "
"something with <emphasis>all</emphasis> discovered shares (&eg; mount or "
"preview), you can do so now. Otherwise, you can use the <guibutton>Up</"
"guibutton> and <guibutton>Down</guibutton> buttons to jump to the individual "
"search results. The <guibutton>Clear</guibutton> button can be used to clear "
"the search. To close the search tool bar, press the <guibutton>Close</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"V vrstico za urejanje vnesite iskalni izraz in pritisnite &Enter; ali "
"kliknite gumb <guibutton>Išči</guibutton>. &smb4k; začne iskati celotno "
"soseščino omrežja. Ko je iskanje končano, so vsi skupni viri, ki ustrezajo "
"iskanemu izrazu, označeni (izbrani). Če bi radi nekaj naredili z "
"<emphasis>vsemi</emphasis> odkritimi skupnimi viri (&eg; priklop ali "
"predogled), lahko to storite zdaj. V nasprotnem primeru lahko uporabite "
"gumba <guibutton>Gor</guibutton> in <guibutton>Dol</guibutton> za skok na "
"posamezne rezultate iskanja. Gumb <guibutton>Počisti</guibutton> lahko "
"uporabite za brisanje iskanja. Če želite zapreti iskalno orodno vrstico, "
"pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Zapri</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:198 index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actions and Popup Menu"
msgstr "Dejanja in pojavni meni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several actions are defined for the network neighborhood browser. They are "
"present in the menu bar under <guimenu>Network</guimenu>, in the tool bar, "
"and in the popup menu. The following actions are available:"
msgstr ""
"Za brskalnik omrežne soseščine je definiranih več dejanj. Prisotni so v "
"menijski vrstici pod <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu>, v orodni vrstici in v "
"pojavnem meniju. Na voljo so naslednja dejanja:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Scan Network|Workgroup|"
"Computer</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Skeniraj omrežje|"
"Delovna skupina|Računalnik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scan the whole network neighborhood, the highlighted workgroup/domain, or "
"the computer for new entries. This action is visible by default and will be "
"replaced by the <guimenuitem>Abort</guimenuitem> action if a network scan is "
"running."
msgstr ""
"Preglejte celotno omrežno soseščine, označeno delovno skupino/domeno ali "
"računalnik za nove vnose. To dejanje je privzeto vidno in ga bo nadomestilo "
"dejanje <guimenuitem>Prekini</guimenuitem>, če se izvaja skeniranje omrežja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Abort</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Prekini</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Abort any running process of the network neighborhood browser. This action "
"is invisible by default and will only be visible when a network scan is "
"running."
msgstr ""
"Prekinite kateri koli tekoči proces brskalnika omrežne soseščine. To dejanje "
"je privzeto nevidno in bo vidno le, ko se izvaja skeniranje omrežja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Search</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Iskanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_searching\">Search the network "
"neighborhood</link> for a specified term. Activating this action opens the "
"search tool bar, where you can enter the search term and start the search."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_searching\">Išči v omrežni "
"soseščini</link> določen izraz. Z aktiviranjem tega dejanja se odpre iskalna "
"orodna vrstica, kjer lahko vnesete iskalni izraz in začnete iskanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:238 index.docbook:565 index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Dodaj zaznamek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding\">Add a bookmark</link> to the selected "
"remote shares. This action is disabled if there are no shares selected."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding\">Dodaj zaznamek</link> izbranim oddaljenim "
"skupnim rabam. To dejanje je onemogočeno, če ni izbranih skupnih diskov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:249 index.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Add Custom Settings</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Dodaj nastavitve po meri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <link linkend=\"custom_settings\">Custom Settings</link> editor "
"where you can set several custom settings for each selected server and "
"share. If a workgroup or no item is selected, this menu entry is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Odpri urejevalnik <link linkend=\"custom_settings\">Nastavitve po meri</"
"link>, kjer lahko nastavite več nastavitev po meri za vsak izbrani strežnik "
"in skupni disk. Če ni izbrana delovna skupina ali noben element, je ta vnos "
"v meniju onemogočen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Open Mount Dialog</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Odpri pogovorno okno za priklop</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_mounting\">dialog</"
"link> for mounting shares using their address (URL or UNC). This feature may "
"be needed if &smb4k; cannot find the server from which you want to mount a "
"certain shared resource."
msgstr ""
"Odprite <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_mounting\">pogovorno "
"okno</link> za priklop skupnih virov z njihovim naslovom (URL ali UNC). Ta "
"zmožnost bo morda potrebna, če &smb4k; ne najde strežnika, s katerega želite "
"priklopiti določen vir v skupni rabi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Authentication</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Avtentikacija</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_authentication"
"\">password dialog</link> where you can provice the user name and password "
"for each selected server and share. If a workgroup or no item is selected, "
"this action is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Odprite <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_authentication"
"\">pogovorno okno gesla</link>, kjer lahko zagotovite uporabniško ime in "
"geslo za vsak izbrani strežnik in skupni disk. Če ni izbrana delovna skupina "
"ali noben element, je to dejanje onemogočeno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Predogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_previewing\">Preview</link> the "
"contents of the selected remote shares. This action is only enabled if "
"shares are selected. Printer shares cannot be previewed."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_previewing\">Predogled</link> "
"vsebine izbranih oddaljenih skupnih rab. To dejanje je omogočeno samo, če so "
"izbrani skupni diski. Skupnih tiskalnikov ni mogoče predogledati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Print File</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Natisni datoteko</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_printing\">Print</link> a file "
"on a remote printer. This action is only available if at least one printer "
"share is selected."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_printing\">Natisnite</link> "
"datoteko na oddaljenem tiskalniku. To dejanje je na voljo le, če je izbran "
"vsaj en skupni tiskalnik."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>M</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Mount</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>M</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Priklop</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mount the selected remote shares. This action is visible by default as long "
"as you do not select mounted shares (see below). If you select anything "
"different than a share with type \"Disk\" or \"IPC\", this action is "
"disabled."
msgstr ""
"Priklopi izbrane oddaljene skupne vire. To dejanje je privzeto vidno, dokler "
"ne izberete priklopljenih skupnih virov (glejte spodaj). Če izberete kar "
"koli drugega kot skupni vir vrste \"Disk\" ali \"IPC\", je to dejanje "
"onemogočeno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:315 index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Unmount</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Odklopi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:321 index.docbook:4378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unmount the selected shares. System mounts, or shares that were mounted by "
"other users cannot be unmounted. This action is invisible by default and "
"will only be visible instead of the <guimenuitem>Mount</guimenuitem> action "
"if at least one mounted share is selected."
msgstr ""
"Odklopi izbrane skupne rabe. Sistemskih priklopov ali skupnih naprav, ki so "
"jih priklopili drugi uporabniki, ni mogoče odklopiti. To dejanje je privzeto "
"nevidno in bo vidno namesto dejanja <guimenuitem>Priklopi</guimenuitem> le, "
"če je izbrana vsaj ena priklopljena skupna raba."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the network neighborhood browser you can right click to open the popup "
"menu to access all available actions. Depending on the position where you "
"clicked (on a network item or on the viewport), some of them may be "
"disabled. The screenshot below shows the popup menu opened on a remote share."
msgstr ""
"V brskalniku omrežne soseščine lahko z desnim klikom odprete pojavni meni za "
"dostop do vseh razpoložljivih dejanj. Odvisno od položaja, kjer ste kliknili "
"(na omrežnem elementu ali v vidnem polju), bodo nekateri od njih morda "
"onemogočeni. Spodnji posnetek zaslona prikazuje pojavni meni, odprt v "
"oddaljenem skupnem disku."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the popup menu of the network neighborhood browser"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pojavnega menija brskalnika omrežne soseščine"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "The popup menu of the network neighborhood browser"
msgstr "Pojavni meni brskalnika omrežne soseščine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:346 index.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tooltips"
msgstr "Namigi orodij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each network item, a tooltip is provided that contains various "
"information like the name of the workgroup and master browser (if "
"available), the name and IP address of the host, the name of the share, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Za vsak element omrežja je na voljo opis orodja, ki vsebuje različne "
"informacije, kot so ime delovne skupine in glavni brskalnik (če je na "
"voljo), ime in naslov IP gostitelja, ime skupne rabe, &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tooltips can be disabled in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_user_interface_network\">configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Namige orodij lahko onemogočite v <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_user_interface_network\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem "
"oknu</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mounting Shares"
msgstr "Priklop skupnih virov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are three options available to mount a remote share:"
msgstr "Za priklop oddaljenih skupnih virov so na voljo tri možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Execute the icon representing the remote share in the network neighborhood "
"browser. (Depending on your &kde; settings, this is done by either single or "
"double clicking the icon.)"
msgstr ""
"Izvedite ikono, ki predstavlja oddaljeno skupni disk v brskalniku omrežne "
"soseščine. (Odvisno od vaših nastavitev &kde;, to storite z enim ali dvojnim "
"klikom na ikono.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the remote shares and click the <guimenuitem>Mount</guimenuitem> menu "
"entry. Alternatively, you can press the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo> keyboard shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Izberite oddaljene skupne vire in kliknite menijski vnos "
"<guimenuitem>Priklopi</guimenuitem>. Lahko pa pritisnete <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>M</keycap></keycombo> bližnjico na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>O</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Open Mount Dialog</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu entry to open the mount dialog:"
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Odpri pogovorno okno za "
"priklop</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in odpre se pogovorno okno za priklop:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the \"Mount Share\" dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna \"Priklop skupnega vira\""

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Mount Share\" dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno \"Priklop skupnega vira\""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can enter the location of the share as a <ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Uniform_Naming_Convention#Uniform_Naming_Convention"
"\">Uniform Naming Convention (UNC)</ulink> address in the form "
"<programlisting>//[USER@]SERVER/SHARE</programlisting> or <programlisting>\\"
"\\[USER@]SERVER\\SHARE</programlisting> or as an <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/URL\">URL</ulink> in the form <programlisting>[smb:]//"
"[user@]server[:port]/share</programlisting> The <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"button will be enabled and you can press it to mount the share. However, it "
"is advisable to enter the IP address and the workgroup of the server, too. "
"If you want to add the share to the bookmarks at the same time, click the "
"<guibutton>Bookmark >></guibutton> button. The dialog will extend, so that "
"you can tick the <guibutton>Add this share to the bookmarks</guibutton> "
"check box and enter a label and category for the bookmark. See the section "
"<link linkend=\"bookmarks\">Bookmarks</link> for more details."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko vnesete lokacijo skupnega vira kot naslov <ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Uniform_Naming_Convention#Uniform_Naming_Convention"
"\">Konvencija o enotnem poimenovanju (Uniform Naming Convention - UNC)</"
"ulink> v obliki <programlisting>//USER@]SERVER/SHARE</programlisting> ali "
"<programlisting>\\\\[USER@]SERVER\\SHARE</programlisting> ali kot URL v "
"obliki <programlisting>[smb:]//[user@]server[:port]/share</programlisting> "
"Gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> bo omogočen in lahko ga pritisnete, da "
"priklopite skupni vir. Vendar je priporočljivo, da vnesete tudi naslov IP in "
"delovno skupino strežnika. Če želite skupni vir hkrati dodati med zaznamke, "
"kliknite gumb <guibutton>Zaznamek >></guibutton>. Pogovorno okno se bo "
"razširilo, tako da boste lahko označili potrditveno polje <guibutton>Dodaj "
"ta skupni vir med zaznamke</guibutton> ter vnesite oznako in kategorijo za "
"zaznamek. Za več podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"bookmarks"
"\">Zaznamki</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this case a share is password protected, a <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_authentication\">password dialog</link> will "
"appear and you have to enter the correct user name (if not already present) "
"and password. &smb4k; will proceed with mounting the share unless a wrong "
"user name or password was entered. In that case, the authentication dialog "
"will reappear. If the mount process was successful, you will be shown a "
"notification and the share will appear in the <link linkend=\"shares_view"
"\">Mounted Shares</link> view. If mounting fails, a notification with the "
"error message that was returned by <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> (&Linux;) or <ulink url=\"man:/mount_smbfs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> (BSD) will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru je skupna raba zaščitena z geslom, prikazalo se bo <link "
"linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_authentication\">pogovorno okno za "
"geslo</link>, v katerega morate vnesti pravilno uporabniško ime (če ga še "
"ni) in geslo. &smb4k; bo nadaljeval z nameščanjem skupne rabe, razen če ste "
"vnesli napačno uporabniško ime ali geslo. V tem primeru se bo pogovorno okno "
"za preverjanje pristnosti znova prikazalo. Če je bil postopek nameščanja "
"uspešen, se bo prikazalo obvestilo in skupna raba se bo prikazala v pogledu "
"<link linkend=\"shares_view\">Priklopljene skupne rabe</link>. Če priklop ne "
"uspe, se prikaže obvestilo s sporočilom o napaki, ki ga je vrnil ukaz <ulink "
"url=\"man:/mount.cifs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> (&Linux;) ali "
"<ulink url=\"man:/mount_smbfs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> (BSD)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing Files on Remote Printers"
msgstr "Tiskanje datotek na oddaljenih tiskalnikih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To print a file on a remote printer, open the print dialog by clicking the "
"printer icon or choosing the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Print File</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite natisniti datoteko na oddaljenem tiskalniku, odprite pogovorno "
"okno za tiskanje tako, da kliknete ikono tiskalnika ali izberete "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Natisni datoteko</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"element menija."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the print dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za tiskanje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "The print dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za tiskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Information</guilabel> section displays various information "
"about the printer. Under <guilabel>File and Settings</guilabel> you must "
"provide the path to the file you want to print and the desired number of "
"copies. Press <guibutton>Print</guibutton> to start the print process."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek <guilabel>Informacije</guilabel> prikazuje različne informacije o "
"tiskalniku. Pod <guilabel>Datoteka in nastavitve</guilabel> morate podati "
"pot do datoteke, ki jo želite natisniti, in želeno število kopij. Pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Natisni</guibutton>, da začnete postopek tiskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; currently supports PDF, Postscript, image, and text files. If you "
"try to print a file with an unsupported mimetype, a notification with an "
"error message will appear telling you the mimetype is not supported. In this "
"case you should convert the file manually to Postscript or PDF and try again."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; trenutno podpira PDF, Postscript, slikovne in besedilne datoteke. Če "
"poskusite natisniti datoteko z nepodprto vrsto mime, se prikaže obvestilo s "
"sporočilom o napaki, ki vam pove, da vrsta mime ni podprta. V tem primeru "
"morate datoteko ročno pretvoriti v Postscript ali PDF in poskusiti znova."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "Previewing Shares"
msgstr "Predogled skupnih virov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; provides the ability to preview remote shares. If you click the "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"entry, the contents of the selected remote share will be opened in a preview "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; nudi možnost predogleda oddaljenih skupnih diskov. Če kliknete "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Predogled</guimenuitem></menuchoice> vnos "
"menija bo vsebina izbrane oddaljenega skupnega diska odprta v pogovornem "
"oknu za predogled."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the preview dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za predogled"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "The preview dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za predogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The preview dialog acts like a simple file manager. You can navigate through "
"the contents of the remote share by clicking the folder icons in the list "
"view. You can go one level up by using the <guibutton>Up</guibutton> button "
"and reload the contents of the current folder by pressing the "
"<guibutton>Reload</guibutton> button. The current location is displayed in "
"the combo box on the right hand side. You can also access already visited "
"folders with it."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno za predogled deluje kot preprost upravljalnik datotek. Po "
"vsebini oddaljenega skupnega diska se lahko pomikate s klikom na ikone map v "
"pogledu seznama. Z gumbom <guibutton>Gor</guibutton> se lahko pomaknete eno "
"raven višje in znova naložite vsebino trenutne mape s pritiskom na gumb "
"<guibutton>Znova naloži</guibutton>. Trenutna lokacija je prikazana v "
"kombiniranem polju na desni strani. Z njim lahko dostopate tudi do že "
"obiskanih map."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the preview dialog does not show hidden folders and files. You "
"can change this behavior in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_network_basic_settings_behavior\">configuration dialog</"
"link>. File transfers and the like are not possible."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto pogovorno okno za predogled ne prikazuje skritih map in datotek. To "
"vedenje lahko spremenite v <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_network_basic_settings_behavior\">pogovornem oknu "
"konfiguracije</link>. Prenosi datotek in podobno niso mogoči."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Providing Authentication Information"
msgstr "Zagotavljanje informacij za preverjanje pristnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case the server or share you want to access is password protected, a "
"password dialog appears asking you for the user name and password. The same "
"thing happens if you click the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>Authentication</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu entry."
msgstr ""
"Veliko strežnikov in oddaljenih skupnih diskov je zaščitenih z geslom. V tem "
"primeru se prikaže pogovorno okno za geslo, ki vas vpraša za uporabniško ime "
"in geslo. Enako se zgodi, če kliknete <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; vnos v meniju <keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>Avtentikacija</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the authentication dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za overovljanje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "The authentication dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za overovljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a user name has already been provided, it will be shown in the respective "
"field. If it is wrong, or no user name was provided, you have to enter one. "
"The password, however, may be left blank. Clicking the <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> button commits the data."
msgstr ""
"Če je uporabniško ime že vneseno, bo prikazano v ustreznem polju. Če je "
"napačno ali ni bilo navedeno uporabniško ime, ga morate vnesti. Geslo pa "
"lahko pustite prazno. S klikom na gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> "
"potrdite podatke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that you can also define default login information in the <link "
"linkend=\"configuration_page_authentication\">configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Namige orodij lahko onemogočite v <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_user_interface_network\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem "
"oknu</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:440 index.docbook:720
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defining Custom Settings"
msgstr "Določanje nastavitev po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For individual servers or shares you can define custom settings that deviate "
"from the global settings. To do so, access the custom settings editor by "
"clicking the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Add Custom Settings</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. See the section <link linkend="
"\"custom_settings\">Custom Settings</link> for more details."
msgstr ""
"Za posamezne strežnike ali skupne diske lahko določite nastavitve po meri, "
"ki odstopajo od globalnih nastavitev. Če želite to narediti, lahko dostopate "
"do urejevalnika nastavitev po meri s klikom na element menija "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Dodaj nastavitve po meri</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Za več podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend="
"\"custom_settings\">Nastavitve po meri</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:450 index.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Bookmarks"
msgstr "Dodajanje zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A bookmark is added by selecting a remote share (only these can be "
"bookmarked), and pressing the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</"
"keycap></keycombo> keyboard shortcut or selecting the <guimenuitem>Add "
"Bookmark</guimenuitem> menu item. The bookmark will then be accessible "
"through the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> menu. See the section <link linkend="
"\"bookmarks\">Bookmarks</link> for more details."
msgstr ""
"Zaznamek dodate tako, da izberete oddaljeni skupni disk (samo te lahko "
"dodate med zaznamke) in pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> bližnjico na tipkovnici ali izbiro menijske "
"postavke <guimenuitem>Dodaj zaznamek</guimenuitem>. Zaznamek bo nato "
"dostopen prek menija <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu>. Za več podrobnosti glejte "
"razdelek <link linkend=\"bookmarks\">Zaznamki</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "The bookmarks can be used to mount remote shares."
msgstr "Zaznamke lahko uporabite za priklop oddaljenih skupnih virov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Mounted Shares View"
msgstr "Pogled priklopljenih skupnih virov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the shares view, you can interact with the shares mounted on your system."
msgstr ""
"V pogledu skupnih virov lahko komunicirate s priklopljenimi skupnimi viri v "
"vašem sistemu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Different Views"
msgstr "Različni pogledi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; comes with two alternative views: an icon view and a list view. They "
"are both shown below. The icon view is the default."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; ima dva alternativna pogleda: pogled ikon in pogled seznama. Oba sta "
"prikazana spodaj. Pogled ikon je privzet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "The icon view:"
msgstr "Pogled ikon:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the shares icon view"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogleda ikon skupnih diskov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "The shares icon view"
msgstr "Pogled ikon skupnih diskov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "The list view:"
msgstr "Pogled seznama:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the shares list view"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogleda seznama skupnih diskov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "The shares list view"
msgstr "Pogled seznama skupnih diskov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can switch between the two views by selecting the appropriate entry in "
"the <guimenuitem>View Modes</guimenuitem> submenu of the tool bar, in the "
"menu bar under <link linkend=\"mainwindow_overview\"><guimenu>Shares</"
"guimenu></link> or in the shares view's <link linkend="
"\"shares_view_actions_popup_menu\">popup menu</link>."
msgstr ""
"Med obema pogledoma lahko preklapljate tako, da izberete ustrezen vnos v "
"podmeniju <guimenuitem>Načini pogleda</guimenuitem> v orodni vrstici v "
"menijski vrstici pod <link linkend=\"mainwindow_overview\"><guimenu>Skupni "
"diski</guimenu> </link> ali v <link linkend=\"shares_view_actions_popup_menu"
"\">pojavnem meniju</link> pogleda skupnih diskov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, only your own mounts are displayed. However, you can adjust "
"&smb4k; to show all mounts in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior\">configuration "
"dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto so prikazani samo vaši priklopljeni skupni viri. Vendar pa lahko v "
"&smb4k; prikažete vse priklope v <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior\">pogovornem oknu "
"konfiguriranja</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the shares view, several actions are defined. They are present in the "
"menu bar under <guimenu>Shares</guimenu>, in the tool bar, and in the popup "
"menu. The following actions are available:"
msgstr ""
"V pogledu skupnih virov je definiranih več dejanj. Prisotni so v menijski "
"vrstici pod <guimenu>Skupni viri</guimenu>, v orodni vrstici in v pojavnem "
"meniju. Na voljo so naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Modes"
msgstr "Načini pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:518 index.docbook:4400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose the view mode from the submenu."
msgstr "V podmeniju izberite način pogleda."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:522 index.docbook:1670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon View"
msgstr "Pogled ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:525 index.docbook:4411
#, no-c-format
msgid "The shares are shown in an icon view."
msgstr "Skupni diski so prikazani v pogledu ikon."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:530 index.docbook:1678
#, no-c-format
msgid "List View"
msgstr "Pogled seznama"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:533 index.docbook:4423
#, no-c-format
msgid "The shares are shown in a list view."
msgstr "Skupni diski so prikazani v pogledu seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:547 index.docbook:4438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unmount the selected shares. This action is restricted to the shares you "
"mounted, though. So, system mounts or shares that belong to other users "
"cannot be unmounted. If no share is selected in the shares view, this button "
"is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Odklopi izbrane skupne rabe. To dejanje je omejeno na skupne rabe, ki ste "
"jih priklopili. Torej sistemskih priklopov ali skupnih rab, ki pripadajo "
"drugim uporabnikom, ni mogoče odklopiti. Če v pogledu skupnih rab ni izbrana "
"nobena skupna raba, je ta gumb onemogočen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:548 index.docbook:560 index.docbook:4440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read the <link linkend=\"shares_view_unmounting\">Unmounting Shares</link> "
"section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Za več podrobnosti preberite razdelek <link linkend=\"shares_view_unmounting"
"\">Odstranjevanje skupnih virov</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Unmount All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Odklopi vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:559 index.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unmount all your shares at once. System mounts or shares that belong to "
"other users cannot be unmounted with this action. If you have not mounted "
"any shares, this button is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Odklopi vse svoje skupne rabe hkrati. Sistemskih priklopov ali skupnih rab, "
"ki pripadajo drugim uporabnikom, ni mogoče odklopiti s tem dejanjem. Če "
"niste priklopili nobenih skupnih rab, je ta gumb onemogočen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add bookmarks to the selected shares. This action is disabled if no share is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Dodaj zaznamke izbranim skupnim diskom. To dejanje je onemogočeno, če ni "
"izbranega nobenega skupnega diska."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read the <link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding\">Adding Bookmarks</link> section "
"for more details."
msgstr ""
"Za več podrobnosti preberite razdelek <link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding"
"\">Dodajanje zaznamkov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the custom settings editor for the selected shares."
msgstr "Odpri urejevalnik nastavitev po meri za izbrane skupne vire."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read the <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_defining_custom_settings\">Custom Settings</"
"link> section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Preberite <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_defining_custom_settings\">Nastavitve po "
"meri</link> za več podrobnosti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:589
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Synchronize</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Sinhroniziraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"shares_view_synchronization\">Synchronize</link> a share "
"with a local copy or vice versa. This action is only enabled if the program "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> is installed "
"and a share is selected."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"shares_view_synchronization\">Sinhroniziraj</link> skupni "
"vir z lokalno kopijo ali obratno. Ta dejavnost je omogočena le, če ste "
"namestili program <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> in je izbran je skupni vir."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Open with Konsole</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Odpri s Konsole</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the base folder of a share in &konsole;. This action is useful if you "
"need to run shell scripts, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Odpri osnovno mapo skupnega vira v &konsole;. Ta element menija je uporaben, "
"če morate zagnati shell skripte &etc;"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Open with File Manager</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Odpri z upravljalnikom datotek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the contents of a share in the default file manager."
msgstr "Odpri vsebino skupnega diska v privzetem upravljalniku datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The popup menu includes all the actions that can be performed on a mounted "
"share:"
msgstr ""
"Pojavni meni vključuje vsa dejanja, ki jih je mogoče izvesti na "
"priklopljenem skupnem viru:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the popup menu of the shares view"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pojavnega menija pogleda skupnih diskov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid "The popup menu of the shares view"
msgstr "Pojavni meni pogleda skupnih diskov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid "It can be opened by clicking the &RMB;."
msgstr "Odprete ga lahko s klikom &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tooltips provide information about the remote location of the share, the "
"mountpoint, the user and group, the login, the file system, the disk usage, "
"and the free disk space. If the share is <link linkend="
"\"shares_view_inaccessible_shares\">inaccessible</link>, these values are "
"marked as unknown."
msgstr ""
"Namigi orodij nudijo informacije o oddaljeni lokaciji skupnega vira, točki "
"priklopa, uporabniku in skupini, prijavi, datotečnem sistemu, uporabi diska "
"in prostem prostoru na viru. Če je skupni vir <link linkend="
"\"shares_view_inaccessible_shares\">nedostopen</link>, so te vrednosti "
"označene kot neznane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tooltips are enabled by default. You can deactivate them in the <link "
"linkend=\"configuration_page_user_interface_shares_view\">configuration "
"dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Namigi orodij so privzeto omogočeni. Deaktivirate jih lahko v <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_user_interface_shares_view\">konfiguracijskem "
"pogovornem oknu</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inaccessible Shares"
msgstr "Nedostopni skupni viri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; periodically checks all mounted shares if they are still accessible. "
"If an inaccessible share is encountered, it will be marked with a lock "
"symbol and you will not be able to open or synchronize it anymore. "
"Unmounting and adding a bookmark is still possible."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; občasno preveri vse priklopljene skupne vire, če so še dostopni. Če "
"naletite na nedostopni skupni vir, bo označen s simbolom ključavnice in ga "
"ne boste mogli več odpreti ali sinhronizirati. Priklop in dodajanje zaznamka "
"je še vedno možno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The program might freeze for a short period of time due to an inaccessible "
"share. It will recover afterwards."
msgstr ""
"Program lahko za kratek čas zamrzne zaradi nedostopnega skupnega diska. "
"Pozneje si bo opomogel."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shares Owned by Other Users"
msgstr "Skupni viri v lasti drugih uporabnikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shares owned by other users are only shown if you adjusted the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior\">settings</link> to "
"display them. You are not allowed to unmount these shares."
msgstr ""
"Skupne rabe v lasti drugih uporabnikov so prikazane le, če ste prilagodili "
"<link linkend=\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior"
"\">nastavitve</link>, da jih prikažete. Teh skupnih rab ne smete odklopiti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icons"
msgstr "Ikone"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A mounted share is indicated by a small, corresponding symbol in the lower "
"corner of the folder icon. This changes to a lock for shares that are not "
"accessible. For shares that belong to another user, it is replaced by a "
"warning sign."
msgstr ""
"Priklopljeni skupni vir je označen z majhnim ustreznim simbolom v spodnjem "
"kotu ikone mape. To se spremeni v zaklepanje skupnih virov, ki niso "
"dostopni. Pri skupnih virih, ki pripadajo drugemu uporabniku, se nadomesti z "
"opozorilnim znakom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag-and-Drop"
msgstr "Povleci in spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; supports drag-and-drop in the shares view. To transfer or link data "
"to a share, drag the files and/or folders over the share icon and drop them "
"there. A popup menu will open asking you what to do. Choose the appropriate "
"action (copy, move or link)."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; podpira povleci in spusti v pogledu skupnih diskov. Če želite "
"podatke prenesti ali povezati s skupnim diskom, povlecite datoteke in/ali "
"mape čez ikono za skupni disk in jih spustite tja. Odpre se pojavni meni z "
"vprašanjem, kaj storiti. Izberite ustrezno dejanje (kopiraj, premakni ali "
"poveži)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the shares view after the user dropped a file"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona pogleda skupnega diska, potem ko je uporabnik spustil "
"datoteko"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid "A popup menu opened after the user dropped a file onto a share"
msgstr ""
"Ko je uporabnik spustil datoteko v skupni disk, se je odprl pojavni meni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To avoid the popup menu, press the &Shift; key for moving, the &Ctrl; key "
"for copying and the <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;</keycombo> key combination for "
"linking while dragging and dropping. The transfer will only be successful if "
"the share was mounted with read and write permissions."
msgstr ""
"Če se želite izogniti pojavnemu meniju, pritisnite &Shift; tipka za "
"premikanje, &Ctrl; tipka za kopiranje in kombinacija tipk <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;</keycombo> za povezovanje med vlečenjem in spuščanjem. Prenos bo "
"uspešen le, če je bil skupni vir priklopljen z dovoljenji za branje in "
"pisanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also drag and drop the whole share to the desktop or to another "
"application (&eg; &dolphin;). Again, a popup menu will open asking you, what "
"to do. When choosing the appropriate operation, please remember that under "
"most circumstances moving and linking the share might not be a good idea."
msgstr ""
"Lahko tudi povlečete in spustite celotni skupni disk na namizje ali v drugo "
"aplikacijo (&eg; &dolphin;). Spet se bo odprl pojavni meni z vprašanjem, kaj "
"storiti. Ko izbirate ustrezno operacijo, ne pozabite, da v večini primerov "
"premikanje in povezovanje skupnega diska morda ni dobra ideja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unmounting Shares"
msgstr "Odklop skupnih virov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:709
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can unmount either a selection of your shares by using the "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Unmount</guimenuitem></menuchoice> action "
"or all of them with the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Unmount All</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> action."
msgstr ""
"Izbrane skupne rabe lahko odklopite z dejanjem "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Odklopi</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali vse "
"z dejanjem <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Odklopi vse</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that you can only umount the shares you mounted. System shares "
"or shares that were mounted by other users cannot be unmounted."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko odklopite samo tiste skupne rabe, ki ste jih "
"priklopili. Sistemskih skupnih rab ali skupnih rab, ki so jih priklopili "
"drugi uporabniki, ni mogoče odklopiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; provides the ability to force unmounting of shares (&Linux; only). "
"This can be useful with inaccessible shares that cannot be unmounted the "
"normal way. To enable this feature, you need to modify the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior\">settings</link> in "
"the configuration dialog. &smb4k; will then perform a <ulink url=\"man:/"
"umount(8)\">lazy unmount</ulink> on inaccessible shares."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; omogoča prisilni odklop skupnih rab (samo za &Linux;). To je lahko "
"uporabno pri nedostopnih skupnih rab, ki jih ni mogoče odklopiti na običajen "
"način. Če želite omogočiti to zmožnost, morate spremeniti <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior\">nastavitve</link> v "
"pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo. &smb4k; bo nato izvedel <ulink url=\"man:/"
"umount(8)\">leni odklop</ulink> na nedostopnih skupnih virih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After a successful unmount process, the user is <link linkend=\"notifications"
"\">notified</link>. If unmounting fails, a notification with the returned "
"error message is shown."
msgstr ""
"Po uspešnem postopku odklopa je uporabnik <link linkend=\"notifications"
"\">obveščen</link>. Če odklop ni uspel, se prikaže obvestilo z vrnjenim "
"sporočilom o napaki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For selected shares, custom settings can be defined. Click the "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Add Custom Settings</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> action to open the Custom Settings dialog. Read the <link "
"linkend=\"custom_settings\">Custom Settings</link> section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Za izbrane skupne vire je mogoče določiti nastavitve po meri. Kliknite "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; Dejanje <keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Dodaj nastavitve po meri</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da odprete pogovorno okno z nastavitvami po meri. "
"Za več podrobnosti preberite razdelek <link linkend=\"custom_settings"
"\">Nastavitve po meri</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:730 index.docbook:3222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronization"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Y</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Synchronize</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> action opens the synchronization dialog. It offers the mount "
"point of the share as the source and a path below the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_synchronization_basic_settings_default_destination"
"\">synchronization prefix</link> as the destination. To update the data on "
"the share, you can swap the destination with the source by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Swap Paths</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Dejanje <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Y</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Sinhroniziraj</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> odpre pogovorno okno za sinhronizacijo. Ponuja točko priklopa "
"skupnega vira kot vir in pot pod <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_synchronization_basic_settings_default_destination"
"\">sinhronizacijsko predpono</link> kot cilj. Če želite posodobiti podatke "
"na skupnem viru, lahko cilj zamenjate z izvorom, tako da kliknete gumb "
"<guibutton>Zamenjaj poti</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the synchronization input dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za vnos sinhronizacije"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid "&URL; requester for sync'ing"
msgstr "&URL; zahtevnik za sinhronizacijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the <guibutton>Synchronize</guibutton> button starts the "
"synchronization and a progress dialog is shown that shows details about the "
"transfer."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na gumb <guibutton>Sinhroniziraj</guibutton> se začne "
"sinhronizacija in prikaže se pogovorno okno napredka, ki prikazuje "
"podrobnosti o prenosu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the synchronization progress dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna napredka sinhronizacije"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid "Progress dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno napredka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The synchronization can be canceled at any time by pressing the stop button "
"to the right of the progress bar."
msgstr ""
"Sinhronizacijo lahko kadar koli prekličete s pritiskom na gumb za ustavitev "
"na desni strani vrstice napredka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opening a Share"
msgstr "Odpiranje skupnega vira"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid "&smb4k; provides two possibilities to open a mounted share:"
msgstr "&smb4k; nudi dve možnosti za odpiranje priklopljenega skupnega vira:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a share with &konsole;"
msgstr "Odpri skupni vir s &konsole;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can open the mounted share in &konsole; by selecting the "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Open with Konsole</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> action. This is useful if you need to run a shell script on the "
"share or do something similar."
msgstr ""
"Priklopljeni skupni vir lahko odprete v &konsole; z izbiro dejanja "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Odpri s Konsole</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"To je uporabno, če morate zagnati lupinski skript na skupnem viru ali "
"narediti kaj podobnega."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a share with the default file manager"
msgstr "Odprite skupni vir s privzetim upravljalnikom datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:772
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can open the share in the default file manager (&eg; &dolphin;) by "
"clicking the share icon or by selecting the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>Open with File Manager</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"action."
msgstr ""
"Skupni disk lahko odprete v privzetem upravljalniku datotek (&eg; &dolphin;) "
"s klikom na ikono za skupni disk ali z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Odpri z upravljalnikom datotek</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "If a share is marked as inaccessible, it cannot be opened."
msgstr "Če je skupni disk označen kot nedostopen, ga ni mogoče odpreti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid "The System Tray Widget"
msgstr "Gradnik sistemskega pladnja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location and Usage"
msgstr "Lokacija in uporaba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &smb4k; is started, a status icon appears in the system tray. Its "
"status is set to active if either workgroups or domains were discovered in "
"your network neighborhood or remote shares were mounted. Otherwise it is set "
"to inactive."
msgstr ""
"Ko se &smb4k; zažene, se v sistemski vrstici prikaže ikona stanja. Njeno "
"stanje je nastavljeno na aktivno, če so bile v vaši omrežni soseščini "
"odkrite priklopljene delovne skupine ali domene. Sicer je nastavljena kot "
"neaktivna."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:796
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the system tray widget"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona gradnika sistemskega pladnja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>System tray widget</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gradnik sistemskega pladnja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can minimize or restore the main window by left clicking the status "
"icon. A right click brings up a popup menu that contains several items "
"allowing you to work with the mounted shares, manage or mount your "
"bookmarks, select the profile you want to use, and configure &smb4k; without "
"opening the main window."
msgstr ""
"Glavno okno lahko pomanjšate ali obnovite z levim klikom na ikono stanja. Z "
"desnim klikom se odpre pojavni meni, ki vsebuje več elementov, ki vam "
"omogočajo delo z nameščenimi skupnimi viri, upravljanje ali pripenjanje "
"zaznamkov, izbiro profila, ki ga želite uporabiti, in konfiguracijo &smb4k; "
"brez odpiranja glavnega okna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:811
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menus and Menu Items"
msgstr "Meniji in menijski elementi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Mounted Shares</guimenuitem> menu lists all mounted shares "
"and some actions that can be performed on them."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenuitem>Priklopljeni skupni viri</guimenuitem> navaja vse "
"priklopljene skupne vire in nekatera dejanja, ki jih je mogoče izvesti na "
"njih."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:816
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Mounted Shares popup menu of the system tray widget"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona pojavnega menija priklopljenih skupnih virov v gradniku "
"sistemskega pladnja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid "System tray widget's Mounted Shares menu"
msgstr "Meni priklopljenih skupnih virov gradnika sistemskega pladnja"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unmount All"
msgstr "Odklopi vse"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each mounted share you can open a submenu that contains the following "
"entries. Read the shares view's <link linkend="
"\"shares_view_actions_popup_menu\">Actions and Popup Menu</link> section for "
"further information."
msgstr ""
"Za vsak nameščen skupni vir lahko odprete podmeni, ki vsebuje naslednje "
"vnose. Glejte razdelek v pogledu deljenja <link linkend="
"\"shares_view_actions_popup_menu\">Dejanja in pojavni meni</link> za dodatne "
"informacije."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unmount"
msgstr "Odklopi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unmount the share. This action is disabled for shares that do not belong to "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Odklopi skupni vir. To dejanje je onemogočeno za skupne vire, ki ne "
"pripadajo vam."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Bookmark"
msgstr "Dodaj zaznamek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add the selected share to the bookmarks."
msgstr "Dodaj izbrani skupni disk med zaznamke."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Custom Settings"
msgstr "Dodaj nastavitve po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:860
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the custom settings editor for the selected share."
msgstr "Odpri urejevalnik nastavitev po meri za izbran skupni vir."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:861
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For further information read the section about <link linkend="
"\"custom_settings\">Custom Settings</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za dodatne informacije preberite razdelek o <link linkend=\"custom_settings"
"\">nastavitvah po meri</link>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize the mounted share with a local copy or vice versa."
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj priklopljeni skupni vir z lokalno kopijo ali obratno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For further information read the section about <link linkend="
"\"shares_view_synchronization\">Synchronization</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za dodatne informacije preberite razdelek o <link linkend="
"\"shares_view_synchronization\">Sinhronizaciji</link>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:875
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open with &konsole;"
msgstr "Odpri s &konsole;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the base folder of the share in &konsole;."
msgstr "Odprite osnovno mapo skupnega diska v &konsole;."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:883
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open with File Manager"
msgstr "Odpri z upravljalnikom datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the contents of the share in the default file manager (&eg; &dolphin;)."
msgstr ""
"Odpri vsebino skupnega diska v privzetem upravljalniku datotek (&eg; "
"&dolphin;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Bookmarks</guimenuitem> menu contains all your bookmarks. "
"Read the <link linkend=\"bookmarks\">Bookmarks</link> section for further "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenuitem>Zaznamki</guimenuitem> vsebuje vse vaše zaznamke. Za "
"dodatne informacije preberite razdelek <link linkend=\"bookmarks\">Zaznamki</"
"link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Bookmarks menu of the system tray widget"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona menija Zaznamki gradnika sistemskega pladnja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid "System tray widget's Bookmarks menu"
msgstr "Meni zaznamkov gradnika sistemskega pladnja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Its layout is as described <link linkend=\"bookmarks_menu\">here</link>, "
"except that the <guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</guimenuitem> menu item is not "
"present."
msgstr ""
"Njegova postavitev je taka, kot je opisana <link linkend=\"bookmarks_menu"
"\">tukaj</link>, le da menijska postavka <guimenuitem>Dodaj zaznamek</"
"guimenuitem> ni prisotna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guimenuitem>Profiles</guimenuitem> menu, all your <link linkend="
"\"profiles\">profiles</link> are listed."
msgstr ""
"V meniju <guimenuitem>Profili</guimenuitem> so navedeni vsi <link linkend="
"\"profiles\">profili</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:905
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Profiles menu of the system tray widget"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona menija Profili gradnika sistemskega pladnja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid "System tray widget's Profiles menu"
msgstr "Meni Profili gradnika sistemskega pladnja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can activate a profile by clicking it. The profiles can be <link linkend="
"\"profiles\">managed</link> in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_profiles\">configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Profil lahko aktivirate s klikom nanj. Profile je mogoče <link linkend="
"\"profiles\">upravljati</link> v <link linkend=\"configuration_page_profiles"
"\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid "These are the four additional menu entries:"
msgstr "To so štirje dodatni vnosi menija:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:918
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open Mount Dialog"
msgstr "Odpri pogovorno okno za priklop"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_mounting\">mount "
"dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Odprite <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_mounting\">pogovorno "
"okno za priklop</link>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:926
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &smb4k;..."
msgstr "Konfiguriraj &smb4k;..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the configuration dialog. See the section about <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">the configuration</link> for a full list of available "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Odprite konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno. Glejte razdelek o <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">konfiguraciji</link> za celoten seznam razpoložljivih "
"nastavitev."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimize | Restore"
msgstr "Strni | Obnovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hide (minimize) or show (restore) the main window. The text shown depends on "
"the state of the main window."
msgstr ""
"Skrij (minimiziraj) ali prikaži (obnovi) glavno okno. Prikazano besedilo je "
"odvisno od stanja glavnega okna."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:945
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit the application."
msgstr "Zapri aplikacijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:957
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &plasmoid;"
msgstr "&plasmoid;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; comes with a &plasmoid; that can be added as a widget to the desktop "
"or the panel. It consists of five tabs: <guilabel>Network Neighborhood</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Mounted Shares</guilabel>, <guilabel>Bookmarks</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Profiles</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Configuration</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; prihaja z &plasmoid; ki ga je mogoče dodati kot pripomoček na "
"namizje ali ploščo. Sestavljen je iz petih zavihkov: <guilabel>Omrežna "
"soseščina</guilabel>, <guilabel>Priklopljeni skupni viri</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel>, <guilabel>Profili</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Konfiguracija</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the plasmoid on the desktop"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona plazmoida na namizju"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:965
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the plasmoid"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona plazmoida"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:974
#, no-c-format
msgid "Network Neighborhood Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Omrežna soseščina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>Network Neighborhood</guilabel> page the network items are "
"arranged in a list view:"
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Omrežna soseščina</guilabel> so omrežni elementi "
"razvrščeni v pogledu seznama:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the plasmoid's network neighborhood tab"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona zavihka plazmoida omrežne soseščine"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:982 index.docbook:1004 index.docbook:1024
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks tab of the plasmoid"
msgstr "Zavihek z zaznamki plazmoida"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking an entry you either enter the level below (&eg; clicking a "
"workgroup or domain item will show a list of all hosts belonging to it), "
"mount the selected share, or invoke the print dialog. To go one level up, "
"you need to click the <guibutton>Up</guibutton> button in the tool bar."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na vnos vnesete spodnjo raven (&eg; s klikom na postavko delovne "
"skupine ali domene se prikaže seznam vseh gostiteljev, ki ji pripadajo), "
"namestite izbrano skupno rabo ali pokličete pogovorno okno za tiskanje. Če "
"se želite pomakniti eno raven višje, morate v orodni vrstici klikniti gumb "
"<guibutton>Gor</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For hosts and shares, there are some action buttons to the right of the "
"network item's name. For hosts, there is one button with which you can open "
"the <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_defining_custom_settings"
"\">Custom Settings</link> editor. For shares, there are additional buttons "
"for <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_previewing\">previewing the "
"content of the selected share</link> and for <link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding"
"\">adding the share to the bookmarks</link>. The action buttons are "
"transparent by default and change to opaque when you move the mouse over "
"them. By left clicking, you initiate the chosen action."
msgstr ""
"Za gostitelje in skupne rabe je na desni strani imena omrežnega elementa "
"nekaj gumbov za dejanja. Za gostitelje obstaja en gumb, s katerim lahko "
"odprete urejevalnik <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_defining_custom_settings\">nastavitev po "
"meri</link>. Za skupne rabe so na voljo dodatni gumbi za <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_previewing\">predogled vsebine izbranega "
"skupnega diska</link> in za <link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding\">dodajanje "
"skupnega diska med zaznamke</link>. Gumbi za dejanja so privzeto prozorni in "
"se spremenijo v neprozorne, ko premaknete miško nad njimi. Z levim klikom "
"sprožite izbrano dejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides the <guibutton>Up</guibutton> button, the tool bar contains three "
"more entries: <guibutton>Rescan</guibutton>, <guibutton>Abort</guibutton> "
"and <guibutton>Mount Dialog</guibutton>. With these you can do a rescan, "
"abort any running action, or open the <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_mounting\">mount dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Poleg gumba <guibutton>Gor</guibutton> vsebuje orodna vrstica še tri vnose: "
"<guibutton>Ponovno skeniraj</guibutton>, <guibutton>Prekini</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>Pogovorno okno za priklop</guibutton>. S temi lahko izvedete "
"ponovno skeniranje, prekinete katero koli dejanje, ki se izvaja, ali odprete "
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_mounting\">pogovorno okno za "
"priklop</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mounted Shares Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek priklopljenega skupnega vira"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>Mounted Shares</guilabel> page all mounted shares are "
"listed:"
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Priklopljeni skupni viri</guilabel> so navedeni vsi "
"nameščeni skupni viri:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the plasmoid's mounted shares tab"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona zavihka plazmoida skupnega vira"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the right side of each entry, three action buttons are arranged. The "
"first is for <link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding\">adding a bookmark</link>, "
"the second is for <link linkend=\"shares_view_synchronization"
"\">synchronization</link>, and the third is for <link linkend="
"\"shares_view_unmounting\">unmounting the share</link>. The action buttons "
"are transparent by default and change to opaque when you move your mouse "
"over them. By left clicking you initiate the selected action."
msgstr ""
"Na desni strani vsakega vnosa so razporejeni trije akcijski gumbi. Prvi je "
"za <link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding\">dodajanje zaznamka</link>, drugi za "
"<link linkend=\"shares_view_synchronization\">sinhronizacijo</link> in "
"tretji za <link linkend=\"shares_view_unmounting\" >odklop skupnega vira</"
"link>. Gumbi za dejanja so privzeto prozorni in postanejo neprozorni, ko "
"premaknete miško nad njimi. Z levim klikom sprožite izbrano dejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1008
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tool bar contains the <guibutton>Unmount All</guibutton> action that "
"lets you unmount all your shares at once."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica vsebuje dejanje <guibutton>Odklopi vse</guibutton>, ki vam "
"omogoča, da odklopite vse skupne vire hkrati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Zaznamki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1018
#, no-c-format
msgid "The bookmarks are listed on the <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> page."
msgstr "Zaznamki so navedeni na strani <guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1021
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the plasmoid's bookmarks tab"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona zavihka z zaznamki plazmoida"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1028
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bookmarked shares can be mounted by left clicking the respective bookmark. "
"To edit or remove the bookmarks, press the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> "
"action button in the tool bar to open the <link linkend=\"bookmarks_editor"
"\">Bookmark Editor</link>. To get back to the top level from a category "
"folder, use the <guibutton>Back</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Zaznamovane skupne vire priklopite tako, da z levim klikom kliknete ustrezni "
"zaznamek. Če želite urediti ali odstraniti zaznamke, pritisnite akcijski "
"gumb <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton> v orodni vrstici, da odprete <link linkend="
"\"bookmarks_editor\">urejevalnik zaznamkov</link>. Za vrnitev na najvišjo "
"raven iz mape kategorij uporabite gumb <guibutton>Nazaj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid "Profiles Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Profili"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1038
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All defined profiles are listed on the <guilabel>Profiles</guilabel> page. "
"The currently active profile is marked with an appended <guilabel>(active)</"
"guilabel> label."
msgstr ""
"Vsi definirani profili so navedeni na strani <guilabel>Profili</guilabel>. "
"Trenutno aktivni profil je označen z dodano oznako <guilabel>(aktiven)</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1041
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the plasmoid's profiles tab"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona zavihka s profili plazmoida"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1044
#, no-c-format
msgid "Profiles tab of the plasmoid"
msgstr "Zavihek Profili plazmoida"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can activate a certain profile by clicking it. All profiles can be <link "
"linkend=\"profiles\">managed</link> via the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_profiles\">configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Določen profil lahko aktivirate s klikom nanj. Vse profile je mogoče <link "
"linkend=\"profiles\">upravljati</link> prek <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_profiles\">konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1056
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure the behavior of &smb4k;, you can launch the <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">configuration dialog</link> on the "
"<guilabel>Configuration</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati vedenje &smb4k;, lahko zaženete <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</link> na strani "
"<guilabel>Konfiguracija</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1061
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the plasmoid's configuration tab"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona konfiguracijskega zavihka plazmoida"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1064
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration tab of the plasmoid"
msgstr "Konfiguracijski zavihek plazmoida"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1069
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should not open two configuration dialogs (through the main application "
"and via the &plasmoid;) at the same time, because they might interfere with "
"each other."
msgstr ""
"Ne smete odpreti dveh konfiguracijskih pogovornih oken (prek glavne "
"aplikacije in prek &plasmoid;) hkrati, ker bi se lahko motila."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1080 index.docbook:4066
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks"
msgstr "Zaznamki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1089
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add bookmarks to your favorite shares from within the <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser\">network neighborhood browser</link>, the "
"<link linkend=\"shares_view\">shares view</link> and the <link linkend="
"\"plasmoid\">&plasmoid;</link>. In the main window, this is done by "
"selecting one or more shares and clicking the <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Add "
"Bookmark</guimenuitem></menuchoice> action. In the &plasmoid;, you click the "
"respective bookmark action next to the item's name. The <guilabel>Bookmark "
"Shares</guilabel> dialog will pop up, listing all shares that are to be "
"newly bookmarked."
msgstr ""
"Svojim priljubljenim skupnim virom lahko dodate zaznamke znotraj <link "
"linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser\">brskalnika omrežne soseske</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"shares_view\">pogleda skupnih virov</link> in <link linkend="
"\"plasmoid\">&plasmoid;</link>. V glavnem oknu to storite tako, da izberete "
"eno ali več skupnih virov in kliknete dejanje <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Dodaj "
"zaznamek</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. V &plasmoid;u kliknete ustrezno dejanje "
"zaznamka poleg imena predmeta. Odprlo se bo pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Označevanje skupnih virov</guilabel> s seznamom vseh skupnih "
"virov, ki jih želite na novo dodati med zaznamke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the bookmarks addition dialog"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za dodajanje zaznamkov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1094
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks addition dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za dodajanje zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a label or assign a category, double-click a bookmark. The input "
"widget will open and you can edit the corresponding entries."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati oznako ali dodeliti kategorijo, dvokliknite zaznamek. Odpre "
"se gradnik za vnos in uredite lahko ustrezne vnose."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1099
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the bookmarks addition dialog with opened input widget"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna za dodajanje zaznamkov z odprtim "
"pripomočkom za vnos"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks addition dialog with opened input widget"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za dodajanje zaznamkov z odprtim pripomočkom za vnos"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Defining categories may help you organize the bookmarks. In the <link "
"linkend=\"bookmarks_menu\">bookmark menu</link>, all bookmarks belonging to "
"the same category are arranged in a respective submenu."
msgstr ""
"Določitev kategorij vam lahko pomaga organizirati zaznamke. V <link linkend="
"\"bookmarks_menu\">meniju z zaznamki</link> so vsi zaznamki, ki pripadajo "
"isti kategoriji, razvrščeni v ustrezni podmeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The label can be any text describing the share. In case you define a label, "
"it will be displayed in the bookmarks menu instead of the location by "
"default. If you want to change this behavior, you can do so in the <link "
"linkend=\"configuration_page_user_interface_main_window\">configuration "
"dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka je lahko poljubno besedilo, ki opisuje skupni disk. V primeru, da "
"določite oznako, bo ta privzeto prikazana v meniju z zaznamki namesto "
"lokacije. Če želite spremeniti to vedenje, lahko to storite v <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_user_interface_main_window\">konfiguracijskem "
"pogovornem oknu</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accessing and Managing Bookmarks"
msgstr "Dostop do zaznamkov in upravljanje z njimi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the main window, the bookmarks can be accessed and managed through the "
"<guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> menu."
msgstr ""
"V glavnem oknu lahko do zaznamkov dostopate in jih upravljate prek menija "
"<guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the bookmark popup menu"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona pojavnega menija zaznamkov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark popup menu"
msgstr "Pojavni meni zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1126
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two static items in the menu:"
msgstr "V meniju sta dva statična elementa:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Bookmarks"
msgstr "Uredi zaznamke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"bookmarks_editor\">bookmark editor</link>. This "
"entry is disabled if there are no bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"Odpre <link linkend=\"bookmarks_editor\">urejevalnik zaznamkov</link>. Ta "
"vnos je onemogočen, če ni zaznamkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds bookmarks to the selected shares. At least one share must be selected "
"to enable this entry."
msgstr ""
"Izbranim skupnim diskom doda zaznamke. Za omogočanje tega vnosa mora biti "
"izbran vsaj en skupni disk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there are bookmarks present that are not assigned to a category, and are, "
"thus, shown directly at the top level of the menu, a third item is present:"
msgstr ""
"Če so prisotni zaznamki, ki niso dodeljeni kategoriji in so zato prikazani "
"neposredno na zgornji ravni menija, je prisoten tretji element:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount Bookmarks"
msgstr "Priklopi zaznamke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mount all top level bookmarks at once. This entry is disabled if all "
"bookmarked shares are already mounted."
msgstr ""
"Priklopi vse zaznamke najvišje ravni hkrati. Ta vnos je onemogočen, če so "
"vsi skupni viri z zaznamki že priklopljeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following entries are category submenus and bookmarks that do not belong "
"to any category. The entries are listed alphabetically and the bookmarks may "
"appear either with their location or a descriptive label. If you click a "
"bookmark, the respective share will be mounted. In case a bookmarked share "
"is already mounted, the entry is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji vnosi so podmeniji kategorij in zaznamki, ki ne pripadajo nobeni "
"kategoriji. Vnosi so razvrščeni po abecedi in zaznamki se lahko prikažejo s "
"svojo lokacijo ali z opisno oznako. Če kliknete zaznamek, bo ustrezna skupna "
"raba priklopljena. Če je skupni vir z zaznamki že priklopljen, je vnos "
"onemogočen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The category submenus contain the assigned bookmarks as well as a "
"<guimenuitem>Mount Bookmarks</guimenuitem> menu item. It can be used to "
"mount all bookmarks in that category at once."
msgstr ""
"Podmeniji kategorij vsebujejo dodeljene zaznamke in v vsakem primeru je "
"prisoten tudi menijski element <guimenuitem>Priklopi zaznamke</guimenuitem>. "
"Uporablja se lahko za priklop vseh zaznamkov v tej kategoriji hkrati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the system tray widget, there is a similar <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> "
"<link linkend=\"systemtray_menus\">submenu</link> which, however, does not "
"come with the <guilabel>Add Bookmark</guilabel> entry."
msgstr ""
"V gradniku sistemske vrstice je podoben <guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel> <link "
"linkend=\"systemtray_menus\">podmeni</link>, ki pa ne vsebuje vnosa "
"<guilabel>Dodaj zaznamek</guilabel> ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &plasmoid; provides a <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> <link linkend="
"\"plasmoid_bookmarks\">tab</link> where all bookmarks are arranged in a "
"similar manner as in the bookmark menu. For further details read <link "
"linkend=\"plasmoid_bookmarks\">this section</link>."
msgstr ""
"&plasmoid; nudi <guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel> <link linkend="
"\"plasmoid_bookmarks\">zavihek</link>, kjer so vsi zaznamki urejeni na "
"podoben način kot v meniju z zaznamki. Za nadaljnje podrobnosti preberite "
"<link linkend=\"plasmoid_bookmarks\">ta razdelek</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Bookmarks"
msgstr "Urejanje zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bookmarks may be edited or removed via the bookmark editor or the "
"<guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> page in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_bookmarks\">configuration dialog</link>. The bookmark "
"editor can be opened by clicking the <guimenuitem>Edit Bookmarks</"
"guimenuitem> entry in the <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> menu or the "
"<guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem> action in the <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> "
"tab of the &plasmoid;."
msgstr ""
"Zaznamke lahko uredite ali odstranite prek urejevalnika zaznamkov ali strani "
"<guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel> v <link linkend=\"configuration_page_bookmarks"
"\">pogovornem oknu konfiguracije</link>. Urejevalnik zaznamkov lahko odprete "
"tako, da kliknete vnos <guimenuitem>Uredi zaznamke</guimenuitem> v meniju "
"<guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel> ali dejanje <guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem> v "
"<guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel > zavihku &plasmoid;a."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the bookmark editor"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona urejevalnika zaznamkov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik zaznamkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the tree view, the bookmarks are arranged according to the categories "
"they belong to. Bookmarks without a category are located at the top level. "
"To rearrange bookmarks, the tree view offers drag and drop capabilities, so "
"you can move bookmarks around with the mouse."
msgstr ""
"V drevesnem pogledu so zaznamki razvrščeni glede na kategorije, ki jim "
"pripadajo. Zaznamki brez kategorije se nahajajo na najvišji ravni. Če želite "
"preurediti zaznamke, drevesni pogled ponuja možnosti povleci in spusti, tako "
"da lahko zaznamke premikate z miško."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to edit a bookmark, you can do so by either double-clicking or "
"selecting it and pressing the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton>button. The input "
"widget will then be shown. Here you can edit the label, category name, "
"login, workgroup or domain name and the IP address."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti zaznamek, lahko to storite tako, da dvokliknete ali ga "
"izberete in pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton>. Nato se prikaže "
"gradnik za vnos. Tukaj lahko uredite oznako, ime kategorije, prijavo, ime "
"delovne skupine ali domene in naslov IP."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the bookmark editor with opened input widget"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona urejevalnika zaznamkov z odprtim gradnikom za vnos"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark editor with opened input widget"
msgstr "Urejevalnik zaznamkov z odprtim gradnikom za vnos"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In most cases, you do not need to touch the IP address and the login, "
"because &smb4k; stores the correct values at the time you bookmark the "
"share. However, if the server got a different IP address (&eg; because DHCP "
"is used on your local network), or your login changed, these entries should "
"be adjusted. You also should adjust the workgroup or domain name, if its "
"name was discovered by DNS-SD (and is most likely called <emphasis>LOCAL</"
"emphasis>). With the label you can give each bookmark a custom description. "
"It will be used for display <emphasis>instead</emphasis> of the location, "
"but this can be changed in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_user_interface_main_window\">configuration dialog</"
"link>. Finally,the category entry helps you to organize your bookmarks. For "
"instance, if you use your notebook at home and also at work, and you do not "
"want to use <link linkend=\"profiles\">profiles</link>, it might be a good "
"idea to create two categories, \"Home\" and \"Work\", and categorize the "
"bookmarks accordingly."
msgstr ""
"V večini primerov se vam ni treba dotikati naslova IP in prijave, ker "
"&smb4k; shrani pravilne vrednosti v času, ko dodate skupno rabo med "
"zaznamke. Če pa je strežnik dobil drugačen naslov IP (&eg; ker se v vašem "
"lokalnem omrežju uporablja DHCP) ali se je vaša prijava spremenila, je treba "
"te vnose prilagoditi. Prilagodite tudi ime delovne skupine ali domene, če je "
"njegovo ime odkril DNS-SD (in se najverjetneje imenuje <emphasis>LOCAL</"
"emphasis>). Z oznako lahko vsakemu zaznamku daste opis po meri. Uporabljena "
"bo za prikaz <emphasis>namesto</emphasis> lokacije, vendar je to mogoče "
"spremeniti v <link linkend=\"configuration_page_user_interface_main_window"
"\">pogovornem oknu konfiguracije</link>. Končno, vnos kategorije vam pomaga "
"organizirati zaznamke. Če na primer uporabljate prenosni računalnik doma in "
"tudi v službi in ne želite uporabljati <link linkend=\"profiles\">profilov</"
"link>, bi bilo dobro ustvariti dve kategoriji, »Dom« in \"Delo\" ter "
"ustrezno kategorizirajte zaznamke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <guibutton>Add Category</guibutton> button, you can add a category. "
"The <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> button removes the selected bookmark and "
"the <guibutton>Clear List</guibutton> button clears the whole list of "
"bookmarks. As long as you have not saved the changes by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Save</guibutton> button, you can reset all your changes with the "
"<guibutton>Reset</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>Dodaj kategorijo</guibutton> lahko dodate kategorijo. "
"Gumb <guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton> odstrani izbrani zaznamek, gumb "
"<guibutton>Počisti seznam</guibutton> pa počisti celoten seznam zaznamkov. "
"Dokler niste shranili sprememb s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Shrani</"
"guibutton>, lahko ponastavite vse svoje spremembe z gumbom "
"<guibutton>Ponastavi</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1203 index.docbook:4098
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve po meri"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Custom Settings"
msgstr "Uporaba nastavitev po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides the global settings that can be defined in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">configuration dialog</link>, &smb4k; offers the "
"possibility to configure individual settings per server or share. You can "
"make use of these custom settings if you want to"
msgstr ""
"Poleg globalnih nastavitev, ki jih lahko definirate v <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</link>, &smb4k; ponuja "
"možnost konfiguriranja posameznih nastavitev na strežnik ali skupno rabo. Če "
"želite, lahko uporabite te nastavitve po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"define individual browse or mount settings for a single server or share that "
"deviate from the values defined in the configuration dialog,"
msgstr ""
"določi posamezne nastavitve priklopa ali brskanja za posamezen strežnik ali "
"skupni vir, ki odstopajo od vrednosti, določenih v pogovornem oknu "
"konfiguracije,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"define a server that should be awakened prior to network scans or mount "
"attempts (Wake-On-LAN feature, see <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_network_advanced_settings_wake_on_lan\">here</link>),"
msgstr ""
"določite strežnik, ki naj se prebudi pred pregledovanjem omrežja ali "
"poskusom priklopa (funkcija Wake-On-LAN, glejte <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_network_advanced_settings_wake_on_lan\">tukaj</link>),"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"always mount a particular share on start-up or when the corresponding "
"profile is loaded."
msgstr ""
"vedno namesti določen skupni vir ob zagonu ali ko je naložen ustrezen profil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Custom Settings"
msgstr "Dodajanje nastavitev po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To define custom settings, in both, the <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_actions_popup_menu\">network neighborhood "
"browser</link> and the <link linkend=\"shares_view_actions_popup_menu"
"\">shares view</link>, you can open the editor for the custom settings by "
"clicking the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Add Custom Settings</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu entry."
msgstr ""
"Če želite določiti nastavitve po meri tako v <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_actions_popup_menu\">brskalniku omrežne "
"soseščine</link> kot v <link linkend=\"shares_view_actions_popup_menu"
"\">pogledu skupnih virov</link> lahko odprete urejevalnik za nastavitve po "
"meri s klikom <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>in meniju Dodaj "
"nastavitve po meri</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the custom settings editor for a share"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona urejevalnika nastavitev po meri za skupno rabo"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid "The custom settings editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik nastavitev po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Custom settings that you defined for a server will also be applied to its "
"shares."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve po meri, ki ste jih določili za strežnik, bodo uporabljene tudi "
"za njegove skupne vire."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1235
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following settings can be made:"
msgstr "Nastavite lahko naslednje nastavitve:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1240
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Basic Settings</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Osnovne nastavitve</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set the IP address and the workgroup or domain of the server here. "
"If you selected a share, you can also check the <guibutton>Always remount "
"this share</guibutton> button to remount it every time you start &smb4k; or "
"load the respective <link linkend=\"profiles\">profile</link>."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko nastavite naslov IP in delovno skupino ali domeno strežnika. Če ste "
"izbrali skupni vir, lahko označite tudi gumb <guibutton>Vedno znova priklopi "
"ta skupni vir</guibutton>, da ga znova namestite vsakič, ko zaženete &smb4k; "
"ali naložite ustrezni <link linkend=\"profiles\">profil</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1247
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Common Mount Settings</guilabel> (&Linux; only)"
msgstr "<guilabel>Skupne nastavitve priklopa</guilabel> (samo &Linux;)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can define common settings related to mounting here. For detailed "
"information about these settings have a look at <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_common_mount_settings\">this section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko določite nastavitve v zvezi s priklopom. Za podrobne informacije "
"o teh nastavitvah si oglejte <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_mount_settings\">ta razdelek</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1255
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Advanced Mount Settings</guilabel> (&Linux; only)"
msgstr "<guilabel>Napredne nastavitve priklopa</guilabel> (samo &Linux;)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can define advanced settings related to mounting here. For detailed "
"information about these settings have a look at <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_advanced_mount_settings\">this section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko določite napredne nastavitve v zvezi s priklopom. Za podrobne "
"informacije o teh nastavitvah si oglejte <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_advanced_mount_settings\">ta razdelek</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1263
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Mount Settings</guilabel> (BSD only)"
msgstr "<guilabel>Nastavitve priklopa</guilabel> (samo BSD)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can define settings related to mounting here. For detailed information "
"about these settings have a look at <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_mount_settings\">this section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko določite nastavitve v zvezi s priklopom. Za podrobne informacije "
"o teh nastavitvah si oglejte <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_mount_settings\">ta razdelek</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1272
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Browse Settings</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Nastavitve brskanja</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can define the minimal and maximal SMB protocol versions as well as the "
"SMB port to be used. In addition, you can decide if Kerberos should be used "
"for authentication. For detailed information about these settings have a "
"look at <link linkend=\"configuration_page_network\">this section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Določite lahko najmanjšo in največjo različico protokola SMB ter uporabljena "
"vrata SMB. Poleg tega se lahko odločite, ali naj se za avtentikacijo "
"uporablja Kerberos. Za podrobne informacije o teh nastavitvah si oglejte "
"<link linkend=\"configuration_page_network\">ta razdelek</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wake-On-LAN Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve Wake-On-LAN"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make the Wake-On-LAN feature work, you must provide the MAC address of "
"the server you selected. Currently, &smb4k; has no way to determine the MAC "
"address, so you need to find it on your own. Afterwards, you can define if "
"the server should be woken up by sending a magic Wake-On-LAN packet before "
"the network neighborhood is scanned and/or one of its shares is mounted."
msgstr ""
"Da bo funkcija Wake-On-LAN delovala, morate vnesti naslov MAC izbranega "
"strežnika. Trenutno &smb4k; ne more določiti naslova MAC, zato ga morate "
"najti sami. Nato lahko določite, ali naj se strežnik prebudi s pošiljanjem "
"čarobnega paketa Wake-On-LAN, preden se pregleda omrežna soseščina in/ali "
"priklopi enega od njegovih skupnih virov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that you need to enable the Wake-On-LAN capabilities in the "
"<link linkend=\"configuration_page_network_advanced_settings_wake_on_lan"
"\">configuration dialog</link> to take advantage of these settings."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da morate omogočiti zmogljivosti Wake-On-LAN v <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_network_advanced_settings_wake_on_lan\">pogovornem oknu "
"konfiguracije</link>, če želite izkoristiti te nastavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> button you can reset all settings "
"in the editor to their default values as they are defined in the "
"configuration dialog. Custom settings that only contain default values are "
"removed. Using the <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> button, you can reset the "
"entries in the dialog to their initial values. Clicking the <guibutton>Save</"
"guibutton> button saves the custom settings and closes the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guibutton>Privzete</guibutton> lahko ponastavite vse nastavitve v "
"urejevalniku na privzete vrednosti, kot so določene v  pogovornem oknu "
"konfiguracije. Nastavitve po meri, ki vsebujejo samo privzete vrednosti, so "
"odstranjene. Z gumbom <guibutton>Ponastavi</guibutton> lahko ponastavite "
"vnose v pogovornem oknu na začetne vrednosti. S klikom na gumb "
"<guibutton>Shrani</guibutton> shranite nastavitve po meri in zaprete "
"pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that under BSD the dialog contains fewer entries than if you run "
"&Linux;, because several of the options are not supported."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da pod BSD pogovorno okno vsebuje manj vnosov, kot če zaženete "
"&Linux;, ker več možnosti ni podprtih."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Custom Settings"
msgstr "Urejanje nastavitev po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can edit or reset the settings of individual network items by opening "
"the custom settings editor. A complete overview of all custom settings "
"provides the <link linkend=\"configuration_page_custom_settings"
"\"><guilabel>Custom Settings</guilabel> configuration page</link>, where you "
"also can edit or remove the desired settings."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve posameznih omrežnih elementov lahko uredite ali ponastavite tako, "
"da odprete urejevalnik nastavitev po meri. Popoln pregled vseh nastavitev po "
"meri ponuja <link linkend=\"configuration_page_custom_settings"
"\"><guilabel>nastavitve po meri</guilabel> konfiguracijska stran</link>, "
"kjer lahko tudi uredite ali odstranite želene nastavitve."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1305 index.docbook:4129 index.docbook:4166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Profiles"
msgstr "Profili"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; offers the option to use different profiles. They are intended to "
"facilitate handling of different network neighborhoods, &eg;, if you are "
"using your laptop at home and also at work."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; ponuja možnost uporabe različnih profilov. Namenjeni so olajšanju "
"upravljanja z različnimi omrežnimi soseščinami, &eg; če uporabljate prenosni "
"računalnik doma in tudi v službi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the use of profiles is disabled. Most users won't have to change "
"this, because the default behavior satisfies their needs completely. "
"However, for some users this feature might be useful."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je uporaba profilov onemogočena. Večini uporabnikov tega ne bo "
"treba spremeniti, ker privzeto vedenje popolnoma zadovoljuje njihove "
"potrebe. Vendar pa je za nekatere uporabnike ta funkcija lahko koristna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1315
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enabling and Managing Profiles"
msgstr "Omogočanje in upravljanje profilov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The use of different profiles can be enabled in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_profiles\">configuration dialog</link> by ticking the "
"<guibutton>Use profiles</guibutton> checkbox. The initial active profile is "
"then set and indicated by the tick mark next to it in the list view. The "
"name of the active profile is also shown in parentheses in the title of the "
"<guilabel>Authentication</guilabel>, <guilabel>Bookmarks</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Custom Settings</guilabel> configuration pages."
msgstr ""
"Uporabo različnih profilov lahko omogočite v <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_profiles\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</link> "
"tako, da označite potrditveno polje <guibutton>Uporabi profile</guibutton>. "
"Začetni aktivni profil je nato nastavljen in označen s kljukico poleg njega "
"v pogledu seznama. Ime aktivnega profila je prikazano tudi v oklepajih v "
"naslovu konfiguracijskih strani <guilabel>Avtentikacija</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Zaznamki</guilabel> in <guilabel>Nastavitve po meri</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Screenshot of the title section of the Authentication "
"configuration page with indicated profile</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona naslovnega razdelka konfiguracijske strani za "
"avtentikacijo z navedenim profilom</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>Screenshot of the title section of the Authentication configuration "
"page with indicated profile</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona naslovnega odseka konfiguracijske strani za "
"avtentikacijoi z navedenim profilom</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two pre-defined profiles, <guilabel>Home</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Work</guilabel>, but you can have as many profiles as you want. A "
"new profile is added by entering its name into the input line and then "
"clicking the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata dva vnaprej določena profila, <guilabel>Doma</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Služba</guilabel>, vendar imate lahko poljubno število profilov po "
"želji. Nov profil dodate tako, da vnesete njegovo ime v vnosno vrstico in "
"nato kliknete gumb <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Profiles configuration page (add profile)"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona strani s konfiguracijo profilov (dodaj profil)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1337
#, no-c-format
msgid "Profiles configuration page (add profile)"
msgstr "Stran s konfiguracijo profilov (dodaj profil)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set the active profile, either double click the profile name or mark the "
"profile name and click the <guibutton>Set Active</guibutton> button. To "
"rename a profile, select it, click <guibutton>Rename</guibutton> and edit "
"the name in the list view. All custom settings, bookmarks and default login "
"credentials will be migrated seamlessly to the new name. To remove a "
"profile, select it and click <guibutton>Remove</guibutton>. You may also "
"change the order of the profiles with the <guibutton>Move Up</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Move Down</guibutton> buttons."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti aktivni profil, dvokliknite ime profila ali označite ime "
"profila in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Nastavi za aktivno</guibutton>. Če "
"želite preimenovati profil, ga izberite, kliknite <guibutton>Preimenuj</"
"guibutton> in uredite ime v pogledu seznama. Vse nastavitve po meri, "
"zaznamki in privzete poverilnice za prijavo bodo brezhibno preseljeni v novo "
"ime. Če želite odstraniti profil, ga izberite in kliknite "
"<guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton>. Vrstni red profilov lahko tudi spremenite z "
"gumboma <guibutton>Premakni gor</guibutton> in <guibutton>Premakni navzdol</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1349
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activating a Profile"
msgstr "Aktiviranje profila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The active profile can either be changed in the configuration dialog as "
"mentioned <link linkend=\"profiles_enable\">above</link>, or in the "
"<guimenu>Profiles</guimenu> menu of the main window or system tray widget, "
"or on the <guilabel>Profiles</guilabel> page of the plasmoid."
msgstr ""
"Aktivni profil lahko spremenite v konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu, kot je "
"omenjeno <link linkend=\"profiles_enable\">zgoraj</link>, ali v meniju "
"<guimenu>Profili</guimenu> glavnega okna ali gradnika sistemskega pladnja "
"ali na strani<guilabel>Profili</guilabel> plazmoida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1352
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a profile is activated, these things happen:"
msgstr "Ko je profil aktiviran, se zgodi naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid "All currently mounted shares are unmounted and scheduled for remount."
msgstr ""
"Vsi trenutno priklopljeni skupni viri so odklopljeni in načrtovani za "
"ponovni priklop."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All shares that were previously mounted under the newly activated profile "
"are remounted."
msgstr ""
"Vsi skupni viri, ki so bile predhodno priklopljeni pod novo aktiviranim "
"profilom, so znova priklopljeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default login credentials (if defined), bookmarks and custom settings "
"from the new profile are loaded."
msgstr ""
"Naložijo se privzete poverilnice za prijavo (če so določene), zaznamki in "
"nastavitve po meri iz novega profila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"So, don't be surprised when things change after you select a different "
"profile ..."
msgstr ""
"Torej, ne bodite presenečeni, ko se stvari spremenijo, ko izberete drug "
"profil ..."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1367
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notifications"
msgstr "Obvestila"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Behavior"
msgstr "Privzeto vedenje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Normal events like mounting and unmounting of a share as well as warnings "
"and errors are reported to the user via system notifications. By default, "
"when the user is notified about a normal event, a notification pops up "
"silently. With warnings and errors a sound is also played. The screenshot "
"below shows the notification that pops up after a share has been mounted."
msgstr ""
"Običajni dogodki, kot je priklop in odklop skupnega vira, ter opozorila in "
"napake so uporabniku sporočeni prek sistemskih obvestil. Privzeto, ko je "
"uporabnik obveščen o običajnem dogodku, se obvestilo tiho prikaže. Ob "
"opozorilih in napakah se predvaja tudi zvok. Spodnji posnetek zaslona "
"prikazuje obvestilo, ki se prikaže po priklopu skupnega mrežnega vira."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the notification after mounting a share"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona obvestila po priklopu skupnega vira"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notification after mounting a share"
msgstr "Obvestilo po priklopu skupnega vira"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default behavior of each notification can be changed via the <link "
"linkend=\"notifications_manage\">&systemsettings;</link>."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto vedenje vsakega obvestila je mogoče spremeniti prek <link linkend="
"\"notifications_manage\">&systemsettings;</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing Notifications"
msgstr "Upravljanje obvestil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Notifications can be managed via the &systemsettings;. To modify the "
"behavior of a notification, navigate to the <guibutton>Notifications</"
"guibutton> page. In the section <guilabel>Application-specific settings</"
"guilabel> click the <guibutton>Configure</guibutton> button and choose "
"&smb4k; from the list that appears. The following dialog is opened:"
msgstr ""
"Obvestila lahko upravljate prek &systemsettings;. Za spremembo vedenja "
"obvestila, se pomaknite na stran <guibutton>Obvestila</guibutton>. V "
"razdelku <guilabel>Nastavitve, specifične za aplikacijo</guilabel> kliknite "
"gumb <guibutton>Konfiguriraj</guibutton> in izberite &smb4k; s seznama, ki "
"se prikaže. Odpre se naslednje pogovorno okno:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the systemsettings notification module"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona modula za obvestila sistemskih nastavitev"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1397
#, no-c-format
msgid "Systemsettings notification module"
msgstr "Modul za obvestila sistemskih nastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1400
#, no-c-format
msgid "All notifications can be edited here according to your preferences."
msgstr "Vsa obvestila lahko tukaj uredite po svojih željah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid "Trouble Shooting"
msgstr "Odpravljanje težav"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Missing Programs"
msgstr "Manjkajoči programi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the system is missing some of the programs &smb4k; needs to operate "
"properly, it notifies the user:"
msgstr ""
"Če v sistemu manjkajo nekateri programi &smb4k; da bi pravilno deloval, "
"obvesti uporabnika:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the missing program notification"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona obvestila o manjkajočem programu"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid "The missing program notification"
msgstr "Obvestilo o manjkajočem programu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this case, please install the specified program or, if it is already "
"present, add its location to the <envar>PATH</envar> environment variable in "
"your shell's configuration file (for the <ulink url=\"man:/bash"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>bash</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> shell it is the <filename>~/.bashrc</"
"filename> file)."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru namestite navedeni program ali, če je že prisoten, dodajte "
"njegovo lokacijo spremenljivki okolja <envar>PATH</envar> v konfiguracijski "
"datoteki lupine (za <ulink url=\"man:/bash\" "
"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>bash</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></"
"citerefentry></ulink> ukazna lupina je datoteka <filename>~/.bashrc</"
"filename>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zeroconf Error"
msgstr "Napaka Zeroconf"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; uses the Zeroconf service (<application><ulink url=\"https://avahi."
"org\">Avahi</ulink></application>) to look up servers and shares in the "
"network neighborhood using DNS Service Discovery (DNS-SD). For this to work, "
"the Avahi daemon must be enabled and running on your system. If this is not "
"the case, &smb4k; shows an error message:"
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; uporablja storitev Zeroconf (<application><ulink url=\"https://avahi."
"org\">Avahi</ulink></application>) za iskanje strežnikov in skupnih diskov v "
"omrežni soseščini s pomočjo DNS Service Discovery (DNS-SD ). Da bi to "
"delovalo, mora biti demon Avahi omogočen in zagnan v vašem sistemu. Če temu "
"ni tako, &smb4k; prikaže sporočilo o napaki:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Zeroconf error notification"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona obvestila o napaki Zeroconf"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1444
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Zeroconf error notification"
msgstr "Obvestilo o napaki Zeroconf"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In most cases, the Avahi daemon is not running when an error is reported. "
"Under those &Linux; distributions that use <application>systemd</"
"application> you can start it by running the following or a similar command "
"from the terminal:"
msgstr ""
"V večini primerov se demon Avahi ne izvaja ob prijavi napake. Pod temi "
"&Linux; distribucijami, ki uporabljajo <application>systemd</application>, "
"jo lahko zaženete tako, da na terminalu zaženete naslednji ali podoben ukaz:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><prompt>$</prompt> <command>sudo</command> <command>systemctl</"
"command> enable --now avahi-daemon</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><prompt>$</prompt> <command>sudo</command> <command>systemctl</"
"command> enable --now avahi-daemon</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1450
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With all other &Linux; distributions and under BSD refer to the specific "
"documentation how to start the Avahi daemon."
msgstr ""
"Z vsemi drugimi &Linux; distribucijami in pod BSD se obrnite na posebno "
"dokumentacijo, kako zagnati demon Avahi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1458
#, no-c-format
msgid "Denied Privilege Escalation"
msgstr "Zavrnjeno stopnjevanje privilegijev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case the mount and unmount actions fail (most likely with an "
"<guilabel>AuthorizationDeniedError</guilabel> message), your polkit-1 setup "
"might need to be adjusted: Add a file, &eg; named <filename>10-mounthelper."
"rules</filename>, to the <filename class=\"directory\">$PREFIX/etc/polkit-1/"
"rules.d/</filename> directory with the following content:"
msgstr ""
"V primeru, da dejanja priklopa in odklopa ne uspejo (najverjetneje s "
"sporočilom <guilabel>AuthorizationDeniedError</guilabel>), bo morda treba "
"prilagoditi vašo nastavitev polkit-1: Dodajte datoteko, &eg; z imenom "
"<filename>10-mounthelper.rules</filename>, v imenik <filename class="
"\"directory\">$PREFIX/etc/polkit-1/rules.d/</filename> z naslednjo vsebino:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"polkit.addRule(function(action, subject) {\n"
"        if (action.id == \"org.kde.smb4k.mounthelper.mount\" &amp;&amp; \n"
"            subject.isInGroup(\"wheel\")) {\n"
"                return polkit.Result.YES;\n"
"        }\n"
"});\n"
"\n"
"polkit.addRule(function(action, subject) {\n"
"        if (action.id == \"org.kde.smb4k.mounthelper.unmount\" &amp;&amp;\n"
"            subject.isInGroup(\"wheel\")) {\n"
"                return polkit.Result.YES;\n"
"        }\n"
"});"
msgstr ""
"polkit.addRule(function(action, subject) {\n"
"        if (action.id == \"org.kde.smb4k.mounthelper.mount\" &amp;&amp; \n"
"            subject.isInGroup(\"wheel\")) {\n"
"                return polkit.Result.YES;\n"
"        }\n"
"});\n"
"\n"
"polkit.addRule(function(action, subject) {\n"
"        if (action.id == \"org.kde.smb4k.mounthelper.unmount\" &amp;&amp;\n"
"            subject.isInGroup(\"wheel\")) {\n"
"                return polkit.Result.YES;\n"
"        }\n"
"});"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows all users in the Unix group <emphasis>wheel</emphasis> to "
"execute the mount and unmount actions. You may adjust the group of "
"authorized users to any group you prefer to use (&eg; <emphasis>sudo</"
"emphasis> or <emphasis>operator</emphasis>)."
msgstr ""
"To omogoča vsem uporabnikom grupe <emphasis>wheel</emphasis> Unix, da "
"izvajajo dejanja priklopa in odklopa. Skupino pooblaščenih uporabnikov lahko "
"prilagodite kateri koli skupini, ki jo želite uporabljati (&eg; "
"<emphasis>sudo</emphasis> ali <emphasis>operator</emphasis>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mounting Problems Under BSD"
msgstr "Težave s priklopom pod BSD"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If mounting of shares from either a &Samba; or a &Windows; server fails, "
"this might be because <ulink url=\"man:/mount_smbfs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> only uses NTLMv1 authentication and "
"requires the SMB 1.0/&CIFS; protocol, and the server does not support those. "
"To fix mounting for a &Samba; server, you can add the following entries to "
"the [global] section of the <ulink url=\"man:/smb.conf"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle><filename>smb.conf</filename></"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>5</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> file of "
"<emphasis>the server</emphasis>:"
msgstr ""
"Če priklop skupnih diskov bodisi zaradi &Samba; ali strežnika &Windows; "
"odpove, to je morda zato, ker <ulink url=\"man:/mount_smbfs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> uporablja samo preverjanje pristnosti "
"NTLMv1 in zahteva SMB 1.0/&CIFS; protokol, strežnik pa jih ne podpira. Če "
"želite popraviti priklop na &Samba; strežnik, lahko dodate naslednje vnose v "
"razdelek [global] datoteke <ulink url=\"man:/smb.conf"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle><filename>smb.conf</filename></"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>5</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> datoteka "
"<emphasis>strežnika</emphasis>:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[global]\n"
"...\n"
"ntlm auth = yes\n"
"server min protocol = NT1\n"
"..."
msgstr ""
"[global]\n"
"...\n"
"ntlm auth = yes\n"
"server min protocol = NT1\n"
"..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to fix this issue for a &Windows; server, please contact the "
"sysadmin and tell her or him that NTLMv1 authentication and the SMB 1.0/"
"&CIFS; protocol should be switched on (if possible)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpraviti to težavo na strežniku &Windows;, se obrnite na "
"sistemskega skrbnika in ji ali mu povejte, da naj bosta vklopljena "
"avtentikacija in protokol NTLMv1 in SMB 1.0/&CIFS; (če je možno)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is not advisable to enable the SMB 1.0/&CIFS; protocol on a server, "
"because it is considered insecure (see &eg; <ulink url=\"https://"
"techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/storage-at-microsoft/stop-using-smb1/ba-"
"p/425858\">here</ulink>) and was thus disabled in newer &Samba; and "
"&Windows; versions (see &eg; <ulink url=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/"
"archive/blogs/josebda/the-deprecation-of-smb1-you-should-be-planning-to-get-"
"rid-of-this-old-smb-dialect\">here</ulink> and <ulink url=\"https://www."
"samba.org/samba/history/samba-4.11.0.html\">here</ulink>)."
msgstr ""
"Ni priporočljivo, da omogočite SMB 1.0/&CIFS; protokol na strežniku, ker "
"velja za nevarnega (glejte &eg; <ulink url=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft."
"com/t5/storage-at-microsoft/stop-using-smb1/ba-p/425858\"> tukaj</ulink>) in "
"je bil zato onemogočen v novejši &Samba; in &Windows; različice (glejte "
"&eg;. <ulink url=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/archive/blogs/josebda/"
"the-deprecation-of-smb1-you-should-be-planning-to-get- rid-of-this-old-smb-"
"dialect\">tukaj</ulink> in <ulink url=\"https://www.samba.org/samba/history/"
"samba-4.11.0.html\">tukaj</ulink>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1488
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Desktop Environments Than &plasma;"
msgstr "Druga namizna okolja kot &plasma;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When using a different desktop environment than &plasma;, &Qt; and &kde-"
"frameworks; applications might be missing some icons. In that case, you "
"might want to install the <application>qt6ct</application> (<ulink url="
"\"https://github.com/trialuser02/qt6ct\">download</ulink>) application. To "
"use it with your desktop environment, add the following to your <filename>~/."
"xinitrc</filename> or <filename>~/.profile</filename> file:"
msgstr ""
"Ko uporabljate drugo namizno okolje kot &plasma;, &Qt; in &kde-frameworks; "
"aplikacijam morda manjkajo nekatere ikone. V tem primeru boste morda želeli "
"namestiti aplikacijo <application>qt6ct</application> (<ulink url=\"https://"
"github.com/trialuser02/qt6ct\">prenos</ulink>). Če ga želite uporabljati z "
"namiznim okoljem, svoji datoteki <filename>~/.xinitrc</filename> ali "
"<filename>~/.profile</filename> dodajte naslednje:"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1491
#, no-c-format
msgid "X11:"
msgstr "X11:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1492
#, no-c-format
msgid "export QT_QPA_PLATFORMTHEME=qt6ct"
msgstr "export QT_QPA_PLATFORMTHEME=qt6ct"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wayland:"
msgstr "Wayland:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"export QT_QPA_PLATFORM=wayland\n"
"export QT_QPA_PLATFORMTHEME=qt6ct"
msgstr ""
"export QT_QPA_PLATFORM=wayland\n"
"export QT_QPA_PLATFORMTHEME=qt6ct"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1505
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &smb4k;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &smb4k;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section describes the settings that can be used to configure &smb4k;. "
"To open the configuration dialog, you must click the <link linkend="
"\"mainwindow_overview\"><guimenuitem>Configure &smb4k;...</guimenuitem></"
"link> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek opisuje nastavitve, ki jih lahko uporabite za konfiguracijo "
"&smb4k;. Če želite odpreti konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno, morate klikniti "
"menijsko postavko <link linkend=\"mainwindow_overview"
"\"><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &smb4k;...</guimenuitem></link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1514
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Interface"
msgstr "Uporabniški vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the appearance and behavior of several dialogs and widgets "
"with the options located here. Please note that if you want to change the "
"appearance of the main window, additional options are available under "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> in the <link linkend=\"mainwindow_overview"
"\">menu bar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Z možnostmi, ki se nahajajo tukaj, lahko spremenite videz in obnašanje več "
"pogovornih oken in gradnikov. Upoštevajte, da če želite spremeniti videz "
"glavnega okna, so dodatne možnosti na voljo pod <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> v <link linkend=\"mainwindow_overview\">menijski vrstici</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1518
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the \"User Interface\" configuration tab"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona konfiguracijskega zavihka »Uporabniški vmesnik«"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1521
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Appearance\" configuration tab"
msgstr "Konfiguracijski zavihek \"Videz\""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1534
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tab orientation"
msgstr "Usmerjenost zavihka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Define the location of the tabs if the dock widgets in the main window are "
"arranged as tabs. The following values can be chosen:"
msgstr ""
"Določite lokacijo zavihkov, če so pripomočki dok v glavnem oknu razporejeni "
"kot zavihki. Izberete lahko naslednje vrednosti:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1541
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Top</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Zgoraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1544
#, no-c-format
msgid "The tabs are located at the top."
msgstr "Zavihki se nahajajo na vrhu."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:1549
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bottom"
msgstr "Spodaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1552
