#: index.docbook:1763 index.docbook:1862 index.docbook:1871 index.docbook:2354
#: index.docbook:2450 index.docbook:3270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: selected"
msgstr "Privzeto: izbrano"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1592
#, no-c-format
msgid "Network Neighborhood"
msgstr "Omrežna soseščina"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon size"
msgstr "Velikost ikone"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the icon size in the network neighborhood browser. The size can be "
"adjusted in steps of 16 pixels from 16 x 16 pixels to 128 x 128 pixels."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite velikost ikone v brskalniku omrežne soseščine. Velikost je mogoče "
"prilagoditi v korakih po 16 slikovnih pik od 16 x 16 slikovnih pik do 128 x "
"128 slikovnih pik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1601 index.docbook:1703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: small icon size"
msgstr "Privzeto: majhna velikost ikone"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1606
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically expand domains and hosts"
msgstr "Samodejno razširi domene in gostitelje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically expand domain and host items when a list of associated network "
"items (domain members or shares) is added or updated. Please note that a "
"domain or host item will always be expanded when you execute it."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno razširi domeno in elemente gostitelja, ko je dodan ali posodobljen "
"seznam povezanih omrežnih elementov (člani domene ali skupne rabe). "
"Upoštevajte, da bo domena ali gostiteljski element vedno razširjen, ko ga "
"izvedete."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1615
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the type of the share"
msgstr "Pokažite vrsto skupnega vira"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1618
#, no-c-format
msgid "The type of the shares is shown (i. e. Disk, Printer, or IPC)."
msgstr "Prikaže se vrsta skupnega vira (npr. disk, tiskalnik ali IPC)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1624
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the IP address of the server"
msgstr "Pokaži naslov IP strežnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1627
#, no-c-format
msgid "The IP address of the remote servers is shown."
msgstr "Prikaže se naslov IP oddaljenih strežnikov."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1633
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the comment"
msgstr "Prikaži komentar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1636
#, no-c-format
msgid "The comment of a remote server or share is shown."
msgstr "Prikaže se komentar oddaljenega strežnika ali skupne rabe."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1642
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show tooltips for network items"
msgstr "Prikaži opise orodij za omrežne elemente"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A tooltip will be shown when you move the mouse pointer over an item in the "
"network neighborhood browser. It contains information about the network item "
"such as the workgroup or domain name, host name, comment, type, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Ko premaknete kazalec miške nad element v brskalniku omrežne soseščine, se "
"prikaže opis orodja. Vsebuje informacije o omrežnem elementu, kot je ime "
"delovne skupine ali domene, ime gostitelja, komentar, vrsta, &etc;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1657
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shares View"
msgstr "Pogled skupnih virov"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1662
#, no-c-format
msgid "View mode"
msgstr "Način pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1665
#, no-c-format
msgid "Define the view mode of the shares view."
msgstr "Določite način pogleda skupnih diskov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1666
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following modes are defined:"
msgstr "Določeni so naslednji načini:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1673
#, no-c-format
msgid "The icon view mode"
msgstr "Način pogleda ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1681
#, no-c-format
msgid "The list view mode"
msgstr "Način pogleda seznama"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1685
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: <guimenuitem>Icon View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "Privzeto: <guimenuitem>Pogled ikon</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon size for the icon view"
msgstr "Velikost ikone za pogled ikone"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the icon size in the icon view of the shares view. The size can be "
"adjusted in steps of 16 pixels from 16 x 16 pixels to 128 x 128 pixels."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite velikost ikone v pogledu ikon v pogledu skupnih rab. Velikost je "
"mogoče prilagoditi v korakih po 16 slikovnih pik od 16 x 16 slikovnih pik do "
"128 x 128 slikovnih pik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1694
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: desktop icon size"
msgstr "Privzeto: velikost ikone na namizju"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1699
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon size for the list view"
msgstr "Velikost ikone za pogled seznama"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1702
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the icon size in the list view of the shares view. The size can be "
"adjusted in steps of 16 pixels from 16 x 16 pixels to 128 x 128 pixels."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite velikost ikone v pogledu seznama pogleda skupne rabe. Velikost je "
"mogoče prilagoditi v korakih po 16 slikovnih pik od 16 x 16 slikovnih pik do "
"128 x 128 slikovnih pik."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1708
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show tooltips for mounted shares"
msgstr "Prikaži opise orodij za priklopljene skupne vire"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A tooltip will be shown when you move the mouse pointer over an item in the "
"shares view. It contains information about the mounted share such as the "
"share name, UNC address, mount point, owner and group, login (&CIFS; file "
"system, &Linux; only), disk usage, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Ko premaknete kazalec miške nad element v pogledu skupnih virov, se prikaže "
"namig orodja. Vsebuje informacije o priklopljenem skupnem viru, kot so ime "
"skupnega vira, naslov UNC, točka priklopa, lastnik in skupina, prijava "
"(&CIFS; datotečni sistem, samo &Linux;), uporaba diska, &etc;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1724
#, no-c-format
msgid "Network"
msgstr "Omrežje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings located here influence the network communication. You can "
"modify the browse settings and behavior in the <guibutton>Basic Settings</"
"guibutton> tab and the more advanced options for Samba and the Wake-On-LAN "
"capabilities in the <guibutton>Advanced Settings</guibutton> tab."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve, ki se nahajajo tukaj, vplivajo na omrežno komunikacijo. "
"Nastavitve in vedenje brskanja lahko spremenite na zavihku "
"<guibutton>Osnovne nastavitve</guibutton>, naprednejše možnosti za Sambo in "
"zmožnosti Wake-On-LAN pa na zavihku <guibutton>Napredne nastavitve</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1729
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the \"Network\" configuration tab"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona konfiguracijskega zavihka »Omrežje«"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1732
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Network\" configuration tab"
msgstr "Konfiguracijski zavihek »Omrežje«"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1741 index.docbook:2034 index.docbook:3239
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Basic Settings</title>"
msgstr "<title>Osnovne nastavitve</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1744
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Browse Settings</title>"
msgstr "<title>Nastavitve brskanja</title>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1749
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use Web Services Dynamic Discovery (WS-Discovery) for browsing"
msgstr ""
"Za brskanje uporabite dinamično odkrivanje spletnih storitev (WS-Discovery)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Web Services Dynamic Discovery (WS-Discovery) protocol is used to browse "
"the local network and discover workgroups, domains and hosts. This is useful "
"if your network neighborhood is dominated by servers with modern &Windows; "
"versions."
msgstr ""
"Protokol dinamičnega odkrivanja spletnih storitev (WS-Discovery) se "
"uporablja za brskanje po lokalnem omrežju in odkrivanje delovnih skupin, "
"domen in gostiteljev. To je uporabno, če v vaši omrežni soseščini "
"prevladujejo strežniki s sodobnimi različicami &Windows;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1753
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting is optional, and only appears if you compiled &smb4k; with WS-"
"Discovery support."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev ni obvezna in se prikaže le, če ste prevedli &smb4k; s podporo "
"WS-Discovery."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1759
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use DNS Service Discovery (DNS-SD) for browsing"
msgstr "Za brskanje uporabite DNS Service Discovery (DNS-SD)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The DNS Service Discovery (DNS-SD) interface is used to browse the local "
"network and discover servers that provide shared SMB resources. The "
"discovered domains correspond to the local DNS domains (&eg; named LOCAL) "
"and most likely not the ones defined in the network neighborhood. However, "
"this does not influence the browsing."
msgstr ""
"Vmesnik DNS Service Discovery (DNS-SD) se uporablja za brskanje po lokalnem "
"omrežju in odkrivanje strežnikov, ki zagotavljajo skupne vire SMB. Odkrite "
"domene ustrezajo lokalnim domenam DNS (&eg;. z imenom LOCAL) in "
"najverjetneje ne tistim, ki so definirane v omrežni soseščini. Vendar to ne "
"vpliva na brskanje."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1768
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set minimal and maximal SMB protocol version"
msgstr "Nastavite najmanjšo in največjo različico protokola SMB"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the minimal and maximal SMB protocol version that is used by &Samba;'s "
"client library to browse the network neighborhood. This will override the "
"settings in the smb.conf file. Normally, you do not need to use this option, "
"because the right protocol versions should be negotiated between the client "
"and the server while establishing a connection. Please note that this "
"setting might not be appropriate to make the discovery of workgroups and "
"domains work while keeping undisturbed connectivity to servers. Use DNS "
"Service Discovery (DNS-SD) or Web Services Dynamic Discovery (WS-Discovery) "
"for domain and workgroup lookups instead."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite najmanjšo in največjo različico protokola SMB, ki jo uporablja "
"odjemalska knjižnica &Samba; za brskanje po omrežni soseščini. To bo "
"preglasilo nastavitve v datoteki smb.conf. Običajno vam ni treba uporabiti "
"te možnosti, ker se morata odjemalec in strežnik med vzpostavljanjem "
"povezave dogovoriti o pravih različicah protokola. Upoštevajte, da ta "
"nastavitev morda ne bo primerna za delovanje odkrivanja delovnih skupin in "
"domen ob ohranjanju nemotene povezave s strežniki. Namesto tega uporabite "
"odkrivanje storitev DNS (DNS-SD) ali dinamično odkrivanje spletnih storitev "
"(WS-Discovery) za iskanje domen in delovnih skupin."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1772
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings below for the minimal and maximal SMB protocol version are "
"enabled by checking this checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Spodnje nastavitve za najmanjšo in največjo različico protokola SMB so "
"omogočene s potrditvijo tega potrditvenega polja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The maximal SMB protocol version must be equal to or greater than the "
"minimal SMB protocol version."
msgstr ""
"Največja različica protokola SMB mora biti enaka ali večja od minimalne "
"različice protokola SMB."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1774 index.docbook:1880 index.docbook:1949 index.docbook:1958
#: index.docbook:1967 index.docbook:1976 index.docbook:1993 index.docbook:2048
#: index.docbook:2077 index.docbook:2086 index.docbook:2095 index.docbook:2410
