"&Windows; Server 2008."
msgstr ""
"To povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> uporablja SMBv2.002 protokol. To je bilo "
"prvotno predstavljeno v &Microsoft; &Windows; Vista Service Pack 1 in "
"&Windows; strežnik 2008."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that the initial release version of &Microsoft; &Windows; Vista "
"spoke a slightly different dialect (2.000) that is not supported."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je prvotna izdaja &Microsoft; &Windows; Vista je govorila "
"nekoliko drugačen dialekt (2.000), ki ni podprt."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2501
#, no-c-format
