msgstr ""
"To povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> uporablja SMBv3.0 različica protokola in "
"novejša."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2542
#, no-c-format
msgid "default (Negotiate the highest version)"
msgstr "privzeto (pogajaj se o najvišji različici)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This causes <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to try to negotiate the highest SMBv2+ "
"version supported by both the client and server."
msgstr ""
"To povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> poskuša izpogajati najvišjo Različica "
"SMBv2+, ki jo podpirata odjemalec in strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Default: not selected; VERS: <guibutton>default (Negotiate the highest "
"version)</guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto: ni izbrano; VERS: <guibutton>privzeto (izpogajaj se o najvišji "
"različici)</guibutton>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2554
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cache mode"
msgstr "Način predpomnilnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2557
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>cache=ARG</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>cache=ARG</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Define how read and write requests are handled. In case you choose to not "
"cache file data at all, the client never utilizes the cache for normal reads "
"and writes. It always accesses the server directly to satisfy a read or "
"write request. If you choose to follow the &CIFS;/SMB2 protocol strictly, "
"the cache is only trusted if the client holds an oplock. If the client does "
"not hold an oplock, then the client bypasses the cache and accesses the "
"server directly to satisfy a read or write request. Choosing to allow loose "
"caching semantics can sometimes provide better performance on the expense of "
"cache coherency. This option might cause data corruption, if several clients "
"access the same set of files on the server at the same time. Because of "
"this, the strict cache mode is recommended."
msgstr ""
"Določi, kako se obravnavajo zahteve za branje in pisanje. Če se odločite, da "
"podatkov datoteke sploh ne boste predpomnili, odjemalec nikoli ne bo "
"uporabil predpomnilnika za običajno branje in pisanje. Vedno neposredno "
"dostopa do strežnika, da zadovolji zahtevo za branje ali pisanje. Če se "
"odločite dosledno upoštevati protokol &CIFS;/SMB2, je predpomnilnik zaupanja "
"vreden samo, če ima odjemalec oplock. Če odjemalec ne zadrži oplock-a, potem "
"odjemalec zaobide predpomnilnik in neposredno dostopa do strežnika, da "
"zadovolji zahtevo za branje ali pisanje. Če se odločite, da omogočite "
"ohlapno semantiko predpomnjenja, lahko včasih zagotovite boljšo zmogljivost "
"na račun koherentnosti predpomnilnika. Ta možnost lahko povzroči poškodbe "
"podatkov, če več odjemalcev hkrati dostopa do istega niza datotek na "
"strežniku. Zaradi tega je priporočljiv način strogega predpomnilnika."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2563
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not cache file data at all"
msgstr "Sploh ne predpomnite podatkov datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This causes <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to not cache file data at all."
msgstr ""
"To povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> ne predpomni podatkov datoteke na vse."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Follow the &CIFS;/SMB2 protocol strictly"
msgstr "Dosledno upoštevaj protokol &CIFS;/SMB2"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This causes <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to follow the &CIFS;/SMB2 protocol "
"strictly."
msgstr ""
"To povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> strogo sledi &CIFS;/ SMB2 protokol."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2579
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow loose caching semantics"
msgstr "Dovoli ohlapno semantiko predpomnjenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This causes <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to allow loose caching semantics."
msgstr ""
"To povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> omogoča ohlapno semantiko predpomnjenja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Default: not selected; ARG: <guibutton>Follow the &CIFS;/SMB2 protocol "
"strictly</guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto: ni izbrano; ARG: <guibutton>Dosledno upoštevaj protokol &CIFS;/"
"SMB2</guibutton>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2591
#, no-c-format
msgid "Security mode"
msgstr "Varnostni način"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Security mode. To be able to use this option, the &CIFS; kernel module 1.40 "
"or later is needed."
msgstr ""
"Varnostni način. Da bi lahko uporabili to možnost, &CIFS; potreben je modul "
"jedra 1.40 ali novejši."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2595
#, no-c-format
msgid "The allowed values are:"
msgstr "Dovoljene vrednosti so:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2599
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connect as a null user (no name)"
msgstr "Poveži se kot null uporabnik (brez imena)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <option>sec=none</option> command line argument is used. This causes "
"<ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to attempt to "
"connect as a null user (no name)."
msgstr ""
"Uporabljen je argument ukazne vrstice <option>sec=none</option>. To "
"povzroči, da se <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> poskuša povezati kot null uporabnik (brez "
"imena)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kerberos 5 authentication"
msgstr "Preverjanje pristnosti Kerberos 5"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <option>sec=krb5</option> command line argument is used. This causes "
"<ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to use "
"Kerberos version 5 authentication."
msgstr ""
"Uporabljen je argument ukazne vrstice <option>sec=krb5</option>. To "
"povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> uporablja preverjanje pristnosti Kerberos "
"različice 5 ."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2615
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kerberos 5 authentication and packet signing"
msgstr "Preverjanje pristnosti in podpisovanje paketov Kerberos 5"

