"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> uporablja enkapsulirano zgoščevanje gesel "
"NTLMv2 v neobdelanem sporočilu NTLMSSP. Ker &Linux; različica jedra 3.8 je "
"to privzeta nastavitev."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2663
#, no-c-format
msgid "NTLMSSP protocol and packet signing"
msgstr "Protokol NTLMSSP in podpisovanje paketov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <option>sec=ntlmssp</option> command line argument is used. This causes "
"<ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to use NTLMv2 "
"password hashing encapsulated in a Raw NTLMSSP message and force packet "
"signing."
msgstr ""
"Uporabljen je argument ukazne vrstice <option>sec=ntlmssp</option>. To "
"povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/mount.cifs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount.cifs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> uporablja enkapsulirano zgoščevanje gesel "
"NTLMv2 v neobdelanem sporočilu NTLMSSP in vsili podpisovanje paketa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; <guibutton>NTLMSSP protocol</guibutton>"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; <guibutton>Protokol NTLMSSP</guibutton>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount Settings (BSD only)"
msgstr "Nastavitve priklopa (samo BSD)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Mount Settings</guilabel> tab is only available under FreeBSD, "
"NetBSD and DragonFly BSD. The settings present under &Linux; can be found in "
"the <link linkend=\"configuration_page_mounting_common_mount_settings"
"\">Common Mount Settings (&Linux; only)</link> and <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_advanced_mount_settings\">Advanced Mount "
"Settings (&Linux; only)</link> sections."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Nastavitve priklopa</guilabel> je na voljo samo v FreeBSD, "
"NetBSD in DragonFly BSD. Nastavitve v &Linux; najdete v razdelkih <link "
"linkend=\"configuration_page_mounting_common_mount_settings\">Skupne "
"nastavitve namestitve (samo &Linux;)</link> in <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_advanced_mount_settings\">Napredne nastavitve "
"namestitve (samo &Linux;)</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2694
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options: <option>-u UID</option> and <option>-g GID</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-u UID</option> in <option>-g GID</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2708
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-f MODE</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-F MODE</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2709
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the permissions that are applied to files. The value is given in octal "
"and may have 3 or 4 digits. The SUID, SGID and sticky bit are not allowed. "
"To learn more about the file mode, you should read the <ulink url=\"man:/"
"mount_smbfs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> and <ulink url="
"\"man:/umask(2)\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>umask</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>2</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> manual pages."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi dovoljenja, ki veljajo za datoteke. Vrednost je podana v osmiškem "
"sistemu in ima lahko 3 ali 4 števke. SUID, SGID in lepljivi bit niso "
"dovoljeni. Če želite izvedeti več o načinu datoteke, preberite strani "
"priročnika <ulink url=\"man:/mount_smbfs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> in <ulink url=\"man:/"
"umask(2)\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>umask</refentrytitle><manvolnum>2</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2710 index.docbook:2720
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: 0755"
msgstr "Privzeto: 0755"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2718
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-d MODE</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-d MODE</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the permissions that are applied to directories. The value is given in "
"octal and may have 3 or 4 digits. The SUID, SGID and sticky bit are not "
"allowed. To learn more about the directory mode, you should read the <ulink "
"url=\"man:/mount_smbfs\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> and <ulink url="
"\"man:/umask(2)\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>umask</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>2</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> manual pages."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi dovoljenja, ki veljajo za imenike. Vrednost je podana v osmiškem "
"sistemu in ima lahko 3 ali 4 števke. SUID, SGID in lepljivi bit niso "
"dovoljeni. Če želite izvedeti več o načinu imenika, preberite strani "
"priročnika <ulink url=\"man:/mount_smbfs"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>mount_smbfs</refentrytitle><manvolnum>8</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> in <ulink url=\"man:/"
"umask(2)\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>umask</refentrytitle><manvolnum>2</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2727
#, no-c-format
msgid "Character Sets"
msgstr "Nabori znakov"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2732
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use character sets"
msgstr "Uporabi nabor znakov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2735
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-E cs1:cs2</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-E cs1:cs2</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the specified local and server's character sets."
msgstr "Uporabi navedene lokalne in strežniške nabore znakov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2744
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this character set for the client side. These character sets are "
"available:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabi ta nabor znakov za stran odjemalca. Na voljo so ti nabori znakov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2751
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default character set used by the client's kernel."
msgstr "Privzeti nabor znakov, ki ga uporablja odjemalčevo jedro."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2931
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: <guimenuitem>default</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "Privzeto: <guimenuitem>privzeto</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:2936
#, no-c-format
msgid "Server character set"
msgstr "Nabor znakov strežnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this character set for the server side. These character sets are "
"available:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabi ta nabor znakov za strežniško stran. Na voljo so ti nabori znakov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2946
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default character set used by the server."
msgstr "Privzeti nabor znakov, ki ga uporablja strežnik."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2951
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp437"
msgstr "cp437"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 437 is the character set of the original IBM PC (personal "
"computer). It is also known as CP437, OEM-US, OEM 437, PC-8, or DOS Latin "
"US. The set includes all printable ASCII characters, extended codes for "
"accented letters (diacritics), some Greek letters, icons, and line-drawing "
"symbols."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 437 je nabor znakov originalnega IBM PC (osebnega računalnika). "
"Znan je tudi kot CP437, OEM-US, OEM 437, PC-8 ali DOS Latin US. Komplet "
"vključuje vse natisljive znake ASCII, razširjene kode za naglašene črke "
"(diakritike), nekatere grške črke, ikone in simbole za risanje črt."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2959
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp720"
msgstr "cp720"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 720 is a code page used to write Arabic in Egypt, Iraq, Jordan, "
"Saudi Arabia, and Syria."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 720 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja za pisanje arabščine v "
"Egiptu, Iraku, Jordaniji, Savdski Arabiji in Siriji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2967
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp737"
msgstr "cp737"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 737 is a code page used to write the Greek language in Greece."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 737 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja za pisanje grškega jezika v "
"Grčiji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2975
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp775"
msgstr "cp775"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 775 is a code page used to write the Estonian, Lithuanian and "
"Latvian languages."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 775 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja za pisanje estonskega, "
"litovskega in latvijskega jezika."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2983
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp850"
msgstr "cp850"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2986
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code page 850 is a code page used in Western Europe."
msgstr "Kodna stran 850 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja v zahodni Evropi."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2991
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp852"
msgstr "cp852"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2994
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 852 is a code page used to write Central European languages that "
"use Latin script (such as Bosnian, Croatian, Czech, Hungarian, Polish, "
"Romanian, Serbian, Slovak or Slovene)."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 852 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja za pisanje srednjeevropskih "
"jezikov, ki uporabljajo latinično pisavo (kot so bosanščina, hrvaščina, "
"češčina, madžarščina, poljščina, romunščina, srbščina, slovaščina ali "
"slovenščina)."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2999
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp855"
msgstr "cp855"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 855 is a code page used to write Cyrillic script. Code page 872 is "
"the euro currency update of code page 855."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 855 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja za pisanje cirilice. Kodna "
"stran 872 je posodobitev valute euro kodne strani 855."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3007
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp857"
msgstr "cp857"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 857 is a code page used in Turkey to write Turkish. It is based on "
"code page 850, but with many changes. It includes all characters from ISO "
"8859-9."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 857 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja v Turčiji za pisanje v "
"turščini. Temelji na kodni strani 850, vendar z veliko spremembami. "
"Vključuje vse znake iz ISO 8859-9."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3015
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp858"
msgstr "cp858"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3018
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 858 is a code page used to write Western European languages. Like "
"code page 850, Code page 858 supports the entire repertoire of ISO 8859-1, "
"but in a different arrangement."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 858 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja za pisanje zahodnoevropskih "
"jezikov. Tako kot kodna stran 850 tudi kodna stran 858 podpira celoten "
"repertoar standarda ISO 8859-1, vendar v drugačni ureditvi."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3023
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp860"
msgstr "cp860"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 860 is a code page used in Portugal to write Portuguese, and it is "
"also suitable to write Spanish and Italian."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 860 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja na Portugalskem za pisanje v "
"portugalščini, primerna pa je tudi za pisanje v španščini in italijanščini."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3031
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp861"
msgstr "cp861"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 861 is a code page used in Iceland to write the Icelandic language "
"(as well as other Nordic languages)."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 861 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja na Islandiji za zapis "
"islandskega jezika (pa tudi drugih nordijskih jezikov)."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3039
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp862"
msgstr "cp862"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code page 862 is a code page in Israel for Hebrew."
msgstr "Kodna stran 862 je kodna stran v Izraelu za hebrejščino."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3047
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp863"
msgstr "cp863"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 863 is a code page used in Canada to write French (mainly in "
"Quebec) although it lacks some letters."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 863 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja v Kanadi za pisanje "
"francoščine (predvsem v Quebecu), čeprav nima nekaterih črk."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3055
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp864"
msgstr "cp864"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 864 is a code page used to write Arabic in Egypt, Iraq, Jordan, "
"Saudi Arabia, and Syria."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 864 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja za pisanje arabščine v "
"Egiptu, Iraku, Jordaniji, Savdski Arabiji in Siriji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3063
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp865"
msgstr "cp865"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3066
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 865 is a code page used in Denmark and Norway to write Nordic "
"languages (except Icelandic, for which code page 861 is used)."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 865 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja na Danskem in Norveškem za "
"pisanje nordijskih jezikov (razen islandščine, za katero se uporablja kodna "
"stran 861)."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3071
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp866"
msgstr "cp866"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3074
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code page 866 is a code page used in Russia to write Cyrillic script."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 866 je kodna stran, ki se v Rusiji uporablja za pisanje cirilice."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3079
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp869"
msgstr "cp869"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3082
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code page 869 is a code page used to write Greek language."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 869 je kodna stran, ki se uporablja za pisanje grškega jezika."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3087
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp874"
msgstr "cp874"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3090
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 874, also known as Code page 9066, is used to write the Thai "
"language."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 874, znana tudi kot kodna stran 9066, se uporablja za pisanje "
"tajskega jezika."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3095
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp932"
msgstr "cp932"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3098
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 932 is the &Microsoft; &Windows; code page for the Japanese "
"language, which is an extended variant of the Shift JIS Japanese character "
"encoding."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 932 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran za japonski jezik, ki "
"je razširjena različica kodiranja japonskih znakov Shift JIS."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3103
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp936"
msgstr "cp936"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 936 is the &Microsoft; &Windows; code page for simplified Chinese."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 936 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran za poenostavljeno "
"kitajščino."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3111
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp949"
msgstr "cp949"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 949 is the &Microsoft; &Windows; code page for the Korean language."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 949 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran za korejski jezik."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3119
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp950"
msgstr "cp950"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 950 is the &Microsoft; &Windows; code page for Traditional Chinese."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 950 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran za tradicionalno "
"kitajščino."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3127
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp1250"
msgstr "cp1250"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 1250 is a &Microsoft; &Windows; code page to represent texts in "
"Central European and Eastern European languages that use Latin script, such "
"as Polish, Czech, Slovak, Hungarian, Slovene, Bosnian, Croatian, Serbian "
"(Latin script), Romanian (before 1993 spelling reform) and Albanian. It may "
"also be used with the German language."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 1250 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran za predstavitev "
"besedil v srednjeevropskih in vzhodnoevropskih jezikih, ki uporabljajo "
"latinico, kot so poljščina, češčina, slovaščina, madžarščina, slovenščina, "
"bosanščina, hrvaščina, srbščina (latinica), romunščina (pred pravopisno "
"reformo leta 1993) in albanščina. Lahko se uporablja tudi z nemškim jezikom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 1251 is a &Microsoft; &Windows; code page designed to cover "
"languages that use the Cyrillic script such as Russian, Bulgarian, Serbian "
"Cyrillic, and other languages."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 1251 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran, zasnovana tako, da "
"pokriva jezike, ki uporabljajo cirilico, kot so ruska, bolgarska, srbska "
"cirilica in drugi jeziki."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3143
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp1252"
msgstr "cp1252"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 1252 is a &Microsoft; &Windows; code page used for English and "
"many European languages including Spanish, French, and German."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 1252 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran, ki se uporablja za "
"angleščino in številne evropske jezike, vključno s španščino, francoščino in "
"nemščino."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3151
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp1253"
msgstr "cp1253"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 1253 is a &Microsoft; &Windows; code page used to write modern "
"Greek. It is not capable of supporting the older polytonic Greek."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 1253 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran, ki se uporablja za "
"pisanje sodobne grščine. Ni sposoben podpirati starejše politonične grščine."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3159
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp1254"
msgstr "cp1254"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 1254 is a &Microsoft; &Windows; code page used to write Turkish."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 1254 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran, ki se uporablja za "
"pisanje v turščini."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3167
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp1255"
msgstr "cp1255"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 1255 is a &Microsoft; &Windows; code page used to write Hebrew."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 1255 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran, ki se uporablja za "
"pisanje hebrejščine."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3175
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp1256"
msgstr "cp1256"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 1256 is a &Microsoft; &Windows; code page write Arabic (and "
"possibly some other languages that use Arabic script, like Persian and Urdu)."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 1256 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran napiše arabščino (in "
"morda še nekatere druge jezike, ki uporabljajo arabsko pisavo, kot sta "
"perzijščina in urdujščina)."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3183
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp1257"
msgstr "cp1257"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 1257 is a &Microsoft; &Windows; code page to support the Estonian, "
"Latvian and Lithuanian languages."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 1257 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran za podporo estonskega, "
"latvijskega in litovskega jezika."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3191
#, no-c-format
msgid "cp1258"
msgstr "cp1258"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code page 1258 is a &Microsoft; &Windows; code page to represent Vietnamese "
"texts. It makes use of combining diacritical marks."
msgstr ""
"Kodna stran 1258 je &Microsoft; &Windows; kodna stran za predstavitev "
"vietnamskih besedil. Uporablja kombiniranje diakritičnih znakov."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:3199
#, no-c-format
msgid "unicode"
msgstr "unicode"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unicode is an information technology standard for the consistent encoding, "
"representation, and handling of text expressed in most of the world's "
"writing systems."
msgstr ""
"Unicode je standard informacijske tehnologije za dosledno kodiranje, "
"predstavitev in ravnanje z besedilom, izraženim v večini svetovnih pisnih "
"sistemov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: <guilabel>default</guilabel>"
msgstr "Privzeto: <guilabel>privzeto</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This configuration page contains options that influence the behavior of the "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> command that "
"is used to synchronize remote shares with local copies and vice versa. It is "
"only available, if <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> is installed on your system. It is "
"recommended that you read the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">manual page</ulink> "
"before you use the synchronization feature the first time. However, safe "
"settings are pre-defined. You will do no harm, if you start right away."
msgstr ""
"Ta konfiguracijska stran vsebuje možnosti, ki vplivajo na delovanje ukaza "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> ki se "
"uporablja za sinhronizacijo oddaljenih skupnih rab z lokalnimi kopijami in "
"obratno. Na voljo je le, če je v vašem sistemu nameščen <ulink url=\"man:/"
"rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>. Priporočamo, da pred prvo uporabo "
"funkcije sinhronizacije preberete <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">stran s "
"priročnikom</ulink>. Vendar so varne nastavitve vnaprej določene. Ne boste "
"naredili nič škode, če začnete takoj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:3227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the \"Synchronization\" configuration page"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona konfiguracijske strani »Sinhronizacija«"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3230
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Synchronization\" configuration page"
msgstr "Konfiguracijska stran \"Sinhronizacija\""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronization Directory"
msgstr "Imenik za sinhronizacijo"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronization prefix"
msgstr "Sinhronizacijska predpona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the base folder below which &smb4k; stores the transferred data "
"using <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>. It can be "
"changed by using the &URL; requester (Click the button with the folder "
"icon.) or by directly entering the new path into the text box. Path "
"variables like $HOME are recognized."
msgstr ""
"To je osnovna mapa, pod katero &smb4k; shrani prenesene podatke z uporabo "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>. Spremenite ga "
"lahko z &URL; zahtevnik (Kliknite gumb z ikono mape.) ali z neposrednim "
"vnosom nove poti v besedilno polje. Spremenljivke poti, kot je $HOME, so "
"prepoznane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each share you synchronize, a new subdirectory below this prefix will be "
"generated. If you want to synchronize the contents of a share to a different "
"folder, you can define it in the <link linkend=\"shares_view_synchronization"
"\">synchronization dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za vsako skupno rabo, ki jo sinhronizirate, bo ustvarjen nov podimenik pod "
"to predpono. Če želite sinhronizirati vsebino skupne rabe v drugo mapo, jo "
"lahko definirate v <link linkend=\"shares_view_synchronization\">pogovornem "
"oknu za sinhronizacijo</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/smb4k_sync/</filename>"
msgstr "Privzeto: <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/smb4k_sync/</filename>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive mode"
msgstr "Arhivski način"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Option: <option>-a</option>/<option>--archive</option>, same as <option>-"
"rlptgoD</option> (no <option>-A</option>, <option>-X</option>, <option>-U</"
"option>, <option>-N</option>, <option>-H</option>)"
msgstr ""
"Možnost: <option>-a</option>/<option>--archive</option>, enako kot <option>-"
"rlptgoD</option> (brez <option>-A</option>, <option>- X</option>, <option>-"
"U</option>, <option>-N</option>, <option>-H</option>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the archive mode on. This is a quick way of saying you want recursion "
"and want to preserve almost everything. Note that <option>-a</option> does "
"not preserve hardlinks (<option>-H</option>), access control lists (ACLs, "
"<option>-A</option>), extended attributes (xattrs, <option>-X</option>), "
"access (use) times (<option>-U</option>) nor create times (<option>-N</"
"option>). You must separately specify these options. The only exception to "
"the above equivalence is when <option>--files-from</option> is specified, in "
"which case <option>-r</option> is not implied."
msgstr ""
"Vklopite način arhiviranja. To je hiter način, da poveste, da želite "
"rekurzijo in želite ohraniti skoraj vse. Upoštevajte, da <option>-a</option> "
"ne ohrani trdih povezav (<option>-H</option>), seznamov za nadzor dostopa "
"(ACL, <option>-A</option>), razširjenih atributov (xattrs, <option>-X</"
"option>), časi dostopa (uporaba) (<option>-U</option>) niti ustvarjanje "
"časov (<option>-N</option>). Te možnosti morate posebej določiti. Edina "
"izjema od zgornje enakovrednosti je podana <option>--files-from</option>, v "
"tem primeru <option>-r</option> ni impliciran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case you do not want to run <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> in archive mode, choose the appropriate "
"arguments in the settings yourself."
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite zagnati <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> v arhivskem načinu, sami izberite ustrezne "
"argumente v nastavitvah."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recurse into subdirectories"
msgstr "Rekurzivno v podimenike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3278
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-r</option>/<option>--recursive</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-r</option>/<option>--recursive</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recurse into subdirectories."
msgstr "Rekurzivno v podimenike."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use relative path names"
msgstr "Uporabite relativna imena poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-R</option>/<option>--relative</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-R</option>/<option>--relative</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use relative path names. This means that the full path names specified on "
"the command line are sent to the server rather than just the last parts of "
"the file names."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite relativna imena poti. To pomeni, da se strežniku pošljejo celotna "
"imena poti, določena v ukazni vrstici, in ne samo zadnji deli imen datotek."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not send implied directories"
msgstr "Ne pošiljajte impliciranih imenikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--no-implied-dirs</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--no-implied-dirs</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option affects the default behavior of the <option>--relative</option> "
"option. When it is specified, the attributes of the implied directories from "
"the source names are not included in the transfer. This means that the "
"corresponding path elements on the destination system are left unchanged if "
"they exist, and any missing implied directories are created with default "
"attributes. This even allows these implied path elements to have big "
"differences, such as being a symlink to a folder on one side of the "
"transfer, and a real folder on the other side."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vpliva na privzeto vedenje možnosti <option>--relative</option>. "
"Ko je podano, atributi implicitnih imenikov iz izvornih imen niso vključeni "
"v prenos. To pomeni, da ustrezni elementi poti v ciljnem sistemu ostanejo "
"nespremenjeni, če obstajajo, vsi manjkajoči implicirani imeniki pa so "
"ustvarjeni s privzetimi atributi. To celo omogoča, da imajo ti implicirani "
"elementi poti velike razlike, na primer simbolna povezava do mape na eni "
"strani prenosa in prava mapa na drugi strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3300 index.docbook:3386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For further information you ought to read the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\">manual page</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za dodatne informacije bi morali prebrati <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">stran s "
"priročnikom</ulink>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transfer directories without recursing"
msgstr "Prenos imenikov brez rekurzije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-d</option>/<option>--dirs</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-d</option>/<option>--dirs</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tell the sending side to include any directories that are encountered. "
"Unlike <option>--recursive</option>, a folders contents is not copied unless "
"the folder name specified is \".\" or ends with a trailing slash (&eg; \"."
"\", \"dir/.\", \"dir/\", &etc;). Without this option or the <option>--"
"recursive</option> option, <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> will skip all directories it encounters "
"(and output a message to that effect for each one). If you specify both "
"<option>--dirs</option> and <option>--recursive</option>, <option>--"
"recursive</option> takes precedence."
msgstr ""
"Povejte strani pošiljateljici, naj vključi vse imenike, na katere naleti. Za "
"razliko od <option>--recursive</option> se vsebina mape ne kopira, razen če "
"je podano ime mape \".\" ali se konča s poševnico na koncu (&eg; \".\", "
"\"dir/.\", \"dir/\" &etc;). Brez te možnosti ali možnosti <option>--"
"recursive</option>, <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry ></ulink> bo preskočil vse imenike, na katere bo "
"naletel (in za vsakega izdal ustrezno sporočilo). Če podate tako <option>--"
"dirs</option> kot <option>--recursive</option>, ima <option>--recursive</"
"option> prednost."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backups"
msgstr "Varnostne kopije"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Make backups"
msgstr "Naredite varnostne kopije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-b</option>/<option>--backups</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-b</option>/<option>--backups</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this option, preexisting destination files are renamed as each file is "
"transferred or deleted. You can control where the backup file goes and what "
"(if any) suffix gets appended using the <option>--backup-dir</option> and "
"<option>--suffix</option> options."
msgstr ""
"S to možnostjo se že obstoječe ciljne datoteke preimenujejo, ko se vsaka "
"datoteka prenese ali izbriše. Z možnostma <option>--backup-dir</option> in "
"<option>--suffix</option> lahko nadzorujete, kam gre datoteka varnostne "
"kopije in katera (če obstaja) pripona se doda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that if you don't specify <option>--backup-dir</option>, (1) the "
"<option>--omit-dir-times</option> option will be implied, and (2) if "
"<option>--delete</option> is also in effect (without <option>--delete-"
"excluded</option>), <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> will add a \"protect\" filter-rule for the "
"backup suffix to the end of all your existing excludes (&eg; <option>-f \"P "
"*~\"</option>). This will prevent previously backed-up files from being "
"deleted. Note that if you are supplying your own filter rules, you may need "
"to manually insert your own exclude/protect rule somewhere higher up in the "
"list so that it has a high enough priority to be effective (&eg;, if your "
"rules specify a trailing inclusion/exclusion of '*', the auto-added rule "
"would never be reached)."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da če ne podate <option>--backup-dir</option>, (1) bo nakazana "
"možnost <option>--omit-dir-times</option> in (2) če <option>--delete</"
"option> je tudi v veljavi (brez <option>--delete-excluded</option>), <ulink "
"url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle "
"><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> bo dodal pravilo filtra "
"\"protect\" za rezervno pripono na konec vseh vaših obstoječih izključitev "
"(&eg;<option>-f \"P *~ «</option>). To bo preprečilo brisanje predhodno "
"varnostno kopiranih datotek. Upoštevajte, da boste morda morali ročno "
"vstaviti lastno pravilo za izključitev/zaščito nekje višje na seznamu, da bo "
"imelo dovolj visoko prioriteto, da bo učinkovito (&eg; če vaša pravila "
"določajo končno vključitev/izključitev '*', samodejno dodano pravilo ne bi "
"bilo nikoli doseženo)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backup suffix"
msgstr "Rezervna pripona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--suffix=SUFFIX</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--suffix=SUFFIX</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to override the default backup suffix used with the "
"<option>--backup</option> option. The default suffix is a <emphasis>~</"
"emphasis> if no <option>--backup-dir</option> was specified, otherwise it is "
"an empty string."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča, da preglasite privzeto pripono za varnostno "
"kopiranje, uporabljeno z možnostjo <option>--backup</option>. Privzeta "
"pripona je <emphasis>~</emphasis>, če ni podana nobena možnost <option>--"
"backup-dir</option>, sicer je prazen niz."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3338 index.docbook:3349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is only available if you ticked the <guilabel>Make backups</"
"guilabel> option above."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je na voljo samo, če ste zgoraj označili možnost <guilabel>Naredi "
"varnostne kopije</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; SUFFIX: ~"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; SUFFIX: ~"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backup directory"
msgstr "Rezervni imenik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3347
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--backup-dir=DIR</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--backup-dir=DIR</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In combination with the <option>--backup</option> option, this tells <ulink "
"url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to store all "
"backups in the specified folder. This is very useful for incremental "
"backups. You can additionally specify a backup suffix using the <option>--"
"suffix</option> option (otherwise the files backed up in the specified "
"folder will keep their original filenames)."
msgstr ""
"V kombinaciji z možnostjo <option>--backup</option> to pove <ulink url="
"\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> za "
"shranjevanje vseh varnostnih kopij v navedeno mapo. To je zelo uporabno za "
"inkrementalne varnostne kopije. Dodatno lahko določite pripono za varnostno "
"kopijo z možnostjo <option>--suffix</option> (sicer bodo datoteke, varnostno "
"kopirane v navedeni mapi, obdržale izvirna imena datotek)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; DIR: <envar>$HOME</envar>"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; DIR: <envar>$HOME</envar>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3363
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Handling"
msgstr "Ravnanje z datotekami"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3366 index.docbook:3864
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3371
#, no-c-format
msgid "Update files"
msgstr "Posodobite datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-u</option>/<option>--update</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-u</option>/<option>--update</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This forces <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to skip any "
"files that exist on the destination and have a modification time that is "
"newer than the one of the source file. (If an existing destination file has "
"a modification time equal to the source file's, it will be updated if the "
"sizes are different.)"
msgstr ""
"To prisili <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, da preskoči "
"vse datoteke, ki obstajajo na cilju, in imajo čas spreminjanja, ki je "
"novejši od časa izvorne datoteke. (Če ima obstoječa ciljna datoteka čas "
"spreminjanja enak času izvorne datoteke, bo posodobljena, če so velikosti "
"drugačne.)"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Update files in place"
msgstr "Posodobite datoteke na mestu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3384
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--inplace</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--inplace</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This causes <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> not to create "
"a new copy of the file and then move it into place. Instead <ulink url="
"\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> will overwrite "
"the existing file, meaning that the rsync algorithm cannot accomplish the "
"full amount of network reduction it might be able to otherwise. One "
"exception to this is if you combine the option with <option>--backup</"
"option>, since <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> is smart "
"enough to use the backup file as the basis file for the transfer."
msgstr ""
"To povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> ne ustvari nove kopije datoteke in nato ga "
"premaknite na svoje mesto. Namesto tega <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> prepiše obstoječo datoteko, kar pomeni, da "
"algoritem rsync ne more doseči celotnega obsega zmanjšanja omrežja, ki bi ga "
"sicer lahko. Ena izjema pri tem je, če kombinirate možnost z <option>--"
"backup</option>, saj <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> je dovolj pameten, da uporabi varnostno "
"kopijo kot osnovno datoteko za prenos."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handle sparse files efficiently"
msgstr "Učinkovito ravnajte z redkimi datotekami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3395
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-S</option>/<option>--sparse</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-S</option>/<option>--sparse</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try to handle sparse files efficiently so they take up less space on the "
"destination. Conflicts with <option>--inplace</option> because it's not "
"possible to overwrite data in a sparse fashion."
msgstr ""
"Poskusi učinkovito obravnavati redke datoteke, da zavzamejo manj prostora na "
"cilju. V sporu z <option>--inplace</option>, ker podatkov ni mogoče "
"prepisati na redek način."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not use this option when the destination is a &Solaris; \"tmpfs\" file "
"system. It doesn't seem to handle seeks over null regions correctly and ends "
"up corrupting the files."
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti ne uporabljajte, če je cilj &Solaris; datotečni sistem \"tmpfs"
"\". Zdi se, da ne obravnava pravilno iskanja po ničelnih regijah in na koncu "
"poškoduje datoteke."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3403
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy files whole (no rsync algorithm)"
msgstr "Kopiraj cele datoteke (brez algoritma rsync)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-W</option>/<option>--whole-file</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-W</option>/<option>--whole-file</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this option the incremental <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> algorithm is not used and the whole file "
"is sent as-is instead. The transfer may be faster if this option is used "
"when the bandwidth between the source and destination machines is higher "
"than the bandwidth to disk (especially when the \"disk\" is actually a "
"networked file system). This is the default when both the source and "
"destination are specified as local paths."
msgstr ""
"Pri tej možnosti se inkrementalni algoritem <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> ne uporablja in celoten namesto tega je "
"datoteka poslana takšna, kot je. Prenos je lahko hitrejši, če je ta možnost "
"uporabljena, ko je pasovna širina med izvornim in ciljnim strojem višja od "
"pasovne širine do diska (še posebej, če je \"disk\" dejansko omrežni "
"datotečni sistem). To je privzeto, če sta izvor in cilj navedena kot lokalni "
"poti."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only update files that already exist"
msgstr "Posodobi samo datoteke, ki že obstajajo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Option: <option>--existing</option>/<option>--ignore-non-existing</option>"
msgstr ""
"Možnost: <option>--existing</option>/<option>--ignore-non-existing</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to skip "
"updating files that do not exist yet on the destination. If this option is "
"combined with the <option>--ignore-existing</option> option, no files will "
"be updated (which can be useful if all you want to do is to delete missing "
"files)."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj preskoči "
"posodabljanje datotek, ki še ne obstajajo na cilj. Če je ta možnost "
"kombinirana z možnostjo <option>--ignore-existing</option>, nobena datoteka "
"ne bo posodobljena (kar je lahko koristno, če želite samo izbrisati "
"manjkajoče datoteke)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3423
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore files that already exist"
msgstr "Ignoriraj datoteke, ki že obstajajo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3426
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--ignore-existing</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--ignore-existing</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to skip "
"updating files that already exist on the destination. See also <option>--"
"ignore-non-existing</option>."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj preskoči "
"posodabljanje datotek, ki že obstajajo na cilju . Glejte tudi <option>--"
"ignore-non-existing</option>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3435
#, no-c-format
msgid "Links"
msgstr "Povezave"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve symlinks"
msgstr "Ohrani simbolne povezave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-l</option>/<option>--links</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-l</option>/<option>--links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3444
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy symlinks as symlinks."
msgstr "Kopiraj simbolne povezave kot simbolne povezave."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transform symlinks"
msgstr "Pretvori simbolne povezave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-L</option>/<option>--copy-links</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-L</option>/<option>--copy-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When symlinks are encountered, the item that they point to is copied, rather "
"than the symlink."
msgstr ""
"Ko se najde simbolna povezava, se kopira element, na katerega kaže, namesto "
"simbolne povezave."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transform unsafe symlinks"
msgstr "Pretvori nevarne simbolne povezave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3463
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--copy-unsafe-links</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--copy-unsafe-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only transform \"unsafe\" symlinks. This means if a symlink is encountered "
"that is pointing outside the copied tree, the referenced item is transferred "
"rather than the symlink itself."
msgstr ""
"Preoblikuj samo \"nevarne\" simbolne povezave. To pomeni, da se v primeru "
"simbolne povezave, ki kaže zunaj kopiranega drevesa, prenese referenčna "
"postavka in ne sama simbolna povezava."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3470
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore unsafe symlinks"
msgstr "Ignoriraj nevarne simbolne povezave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--safe-links</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--safe-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to ignore any "
"symbolic links which point outside the copied tree. All absolute symlinks "
"are also ignored. Using this option in conjunction with <option>--relative</"
"option> may give unexpected results."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj prezre "
"vse simbolne povezave, ki kažejo zunaj kopiranega drevo. Prezrte so tudi vse "
"absolutne simbolne povezave. Uporaba te možnosti v povezavi z <option>--"
"relative</option> lahko da nepričakovane rezultate."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3480
#, no-c-format
msgid "Munge symlinks"
msgstr "Predelaj simbolne povezave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3483
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--munge-links</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--munge-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to (1) modify "
"all symlinks on the receiving side in a way that makes them unusable but "
"recoverable, or (2) to unmunge symlinks on the sending side that had been "
"stored in a munged state. This is useful if you do not quite trust the "
"source of the data to not try to slip in a symlink to an unexpected place. "
"For further information on this argument, please see the manual page of "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, da (1) "
"spremeni vse simbolne povezave na prejemniku strani na način, zaradi "
"katerega so neuporabne, vendar jih je mogoče obnoviti, ali (2) za "
"razveljavitev simbolnih povezav na pošiljateljevi strani, ki so bile "
"shranjene v razpršenem stanju. To je uporabno, če ne zaupate povsem viru "
"podatkov, da ne poskušate vstaviti simbolne povezave na nepričakovano mesto. "
"Za več informacij o tem argumentu si oglejte priročnik za <ulink url=\"man:/"
"rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink >."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve hard links"
msgstr "Ohrani trde povezave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-H</option>/<option>--hard-links</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-H</option>/<option>--hard-links</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to look for "
"hard-linked files in the transfer and link together the corresponding files "
"on the receiving side. Without this option, hard-linked files in the "
"transfer are treated as though they were separate files."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj v prenosu "
"poišče trdo povezane datoteke in povežite ustrezne datoteke na sprejemni "
"strani. Brez te možnosti se trdo povezane datoteke v prenosu obravnavajo kot "
"ločene datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3495
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> can only "
"detect hard links if both parts of the link are in the list of files being "
"sent."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevaj, da lahko <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> zazna trde povezave le, če oba dela "
"povezave so na seznamu datotek, ki se pošiljajo."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3501
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy directory symlinks"
msgstr "Kopiraj simbolne povezave imenika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3504
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-k</option>/<option>--copy-dirlinks</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-k</option>/<option>--copy-dirlinks</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option causes the sending side to treat a symlink to a directory as "
"though it were a real directory. This is useful if you don’t want symlinks "
"to non-directories to be affected, as they would be using <option>--copy-"
"links</option>."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost povzroči, da pošiljatelj obravnava simbolično povezavo do "
"imenika, kot da bi bil pravi imenik. To je uporabno, če ne želite, da to "
"vpliva na simbolne povezave do neimenikov, saj bi uporabljale <option>--copy-"
"links</option>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3511
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep directory symlinks"
msgstr "Ohrani simbolne povezave imenika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-K</option>/<option>--keep-dirlinks</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-K</option>/<option>--keep-dirlinks</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option causes the receiving side to treat a symlink to a directory as "
"though it were a real directory, but only if it matches a real directory "
"from the sender. Without this option, the receiver's symlink would be "
"deleted and replaced with a real directory."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost povzroči, da sprejemna stran obravnava simbolno povezavo do "
"imenika, kot da bi šlo za pravi imenik, vendar le, če se ujema z resničnim "
"imenikom pošiljatelja. Brez te možnosti bi bila prejemnikova simbolna "
"povezava izbrisana in nadomeščena s pravim imenikom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3524
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Attributes &amp; Ownership"
msgstr "Atributi datoteke &amp; Lastništvo"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3526
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Attributes"
msgstr "Atributi datoteke"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve permissions"
msgstr "Ohrani dovoljenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-p</option>/<option>--perms</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-p</option>/<option>--perms</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option causes the receiving side to set the destination permissions to "
"be the same as the source permissions."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost povzroči, da sprejemna stran nastavi ciljna dovoljenja tako, da "
"so enaka dovoljenjem vira."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3540
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve access control lists (ACLs)"
msgstr "Ohranjanje seznamov za nadzor dostopa (ACL)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3543
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-A</option>/<option>--acls</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-A</option>/<option>--acls</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Preserve access control lists. This option causes <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to update the destination ACLs to be the "
"same as the source ACLs. The option also implies --perms. The source and "
"destination systems must have compatible ACL entries for this option to work "
"properly."
msgstr ""
"Ohrani sezname za nadzor dostopa. Ta možnost povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/"
"rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> posodobi ciljne ACL-je, da so enaki kot "
"izvorni ACL. Možnost vključuje tudi --perms. Izvorni in ciljni sistem morata "
"imeti združljive vnose ACL, da ta možnost deluje pravilno."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3550
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve extended attributes"
msgstr "Ohrani razširjene atribute"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3553
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-X</option>/<option>--xattrs</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-X</option>/<option>--xattrs</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Preserve extended attributes. This option causes <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to update the destination extended "
"attributes to be the same as the source ones."
msgstr ""
"Ohrani razširjene atribute. Ta možnost povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> posodobi ciljne razširjene atribute kot "
"enake izvornim."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve access times"
msgstr "Ohrani dostopne čase"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3563
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-U</option>/<option>--atimes</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-U</option>/<option>--atimes</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Preserve access times. This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to set the access (use) times of the "
"destination files to the same value as the source files."
msgstr ""
"Ohrani dostopne čase. To sporoča <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, da nastavi čas dostopa (uporabe) ciljne "
"datoteke na isto vrednost kot izvorne datoteke."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve create times"
msgstr "Ohrani čas ustvarjanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3573
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-N</option>/<option>--crtimes</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-N</option>/<option>--crtimes</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Preserve create times. This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to set the create times (newness) of the "
"destination files to the same value as the source files."
msgstr ""
"Ohrani čas ustvarjanja. To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, da nastavi čas ustvarjanja (novost) "
"ciljne datoteke na isto vrednost kot izvorne datoteke."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve device and special files"
msgstr "Ohrani napravo in posebne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-D</option>/<option>--devices --specials</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-D</option>/<option>--devices --specials</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option causes <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to transfer character and block device "
"files as well as special files (such as named sockets and fifos) to the "
"remote system. This option has no effect if the receiving side is not run as "
"the super user and <option>--super</option> is not specified."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> prenese tudi znake in blokira datoteke "
"naprave kot posebne datoteke (kot so imenovane vtičnice in fifos) v "
"oddaljeni sistem. Ta možnost nima učinka, če sprejemna stran ni zagnana kot "
"super uporabnik in <option>--super</option> ni podana."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve times"
msgstr "Ohrani čase"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3593
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-t</option>/<option>--times</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-t</option>/<option>--times</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to transfer "
"modification times along with the files and update them on the remote system."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj prenese "
"čase spreminjanja skupaj z datotekami in posodobi jih na oddaljenem sistemu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3600
#, no-c-format
msgid "Omit directories when preserving times"
msgstr "Pri ohranjanju časov izpusti imenike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3603
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-O</option>/<option>--omit-dir-times</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-O</option>/<option>--omit-dir-times</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to omit "
"directories when it is preserving modification times (see <option>--times</"
"option>)."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj izpusti "
"imenike, ko ohranja čase spreminjanja (glejte <option>--times</option>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3612
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ownership"
msgstr "Lastništvo"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3616
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve owner"
msgstr "Ohrani lastnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-o</option>/<option>--owner</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-o</option>/<option>--owner</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option causes <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to set the owner of the destination file "
"to be the same as the one of the source file. By default, the preservation "
"is done by name, but may fall back to using the ID number in some "
"circumstances (see the <option>--numeric-ids</option> option for a full "
"discussion). This option has no effect if the receiving <ulink url=\"man:/"
"rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> is not run as the super user and <option>--"
"super</option> is not specified."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> nastavi lastnika ciljne datoteke na biti "
"enak tistemu v izvorni datoteki. Privzeto se ohranitev izvaja po imenu, "
"vendar se lahko v nekaterih okoliščinah vrne k uporabi ID številke (glejte "
"možnost <option>--numeric-ids</option> za celotno razpravo). Ta možnost nima "
"učinka, če se sprejemni <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> ne izvaja kot super uporabnik in <option>--"
"super</option> ni določen."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preserve group"
msgstr "Ohrani skupino"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3629
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-g</option>/<option>--group</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-g</option>/<option>--group</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option causes <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to set the group of the destination file "
"to be the same as the on of the source file. If the receiving program is not "
"running as the super-user (or with the <option>--no-super</option> option), "
"only groups that the receiver is a member of will be preserved."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost povzroči, da <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> nastavi skupino ciljne datoteke na biti "
"enak kot on izvorne datoteke. Če program prejemnik ne deluje kot "
"superuporabnik (ali z možnostjo <option>--no-super</option>), bodo ohranjene "
"samo skupine, katerih član je prejemnik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3643
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Transfer"
msgstr "Prenos datoteke"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3645
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compression"
msgstr "Stiskanje"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3649
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compress data during transfer"
msgstr "Stisni podatke med prenosom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3652
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-z</option>/<option>--compress</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-z</option>/<option>--compress</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3653
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compress file data during the transfer."
msgstr "Stisni podatke datoteke med prenosom."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set compression level"
msgstr "Nastavi stopnjo stiskanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3662
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--compress-level=NUM</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--compress-level=NUM</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Explicitly set the compression level to use. If NUM is non-zero, the "
"<option>--compress</option> argument is implied."
msgstr ""
"Izrecno nastavite stopnjo stiskanja, ki jo želite uporabiti. Če NUM ni nič, "
"je impliciran argument <option>--compress</option>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3664 index.docbook:3848 index.docbook:3991
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; NUM: 0"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; NUM: 0"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3669
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skip compression for following file suffixes"
msgstr "Preskoči stiskanje za naslednje pripone datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3672
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--skip-compress=LIST</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--skip-compress=LIST</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Overwrite the list of file suffixes that will not be compressed. The LIST "
"should be one or more file suffixes (without the dot) separated by slashes. "
"You may specify an empty string to indicate that no file should be skipped. "
"The default list of suffixes will be replaced by this list. For further "
"details, see the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>manual page of rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Prepiši seznam pripon datotek, ki ne bodo stisnjene. LIST mora biti ena ali "
"več končnic datoteke (brez pike), ločenih s poševnicami. Podate lahko prazen "
"niz, ki nakazuje, da se nobena datoteka ne sme preskočiti. Privzeti seznam "
"pripon bo nadomeščen s tem seznamom. Za nadaljnje podrobnosti si oglejte "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>stran s priročnikom "
"za rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3674
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; LIST: empty"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; LIST: prazen"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Files"
msgstr "Datoteke"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3685
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not transfer any file smaller than"
msgstr "Ne prenašaj datotek, manjših od"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3688
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--min-size=SIZE</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--min-size=SIZE</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to avoid "
"transferring any file that is smaller than the specified SIZE, which can "
"help in not transferring small, junk files."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj se izogne "
"prenosu datotek, ki so manjše od določeno SIZE, kar lahko pomaga preprečiti "
"prenos majhnih neželenih datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3690 index.docbook:3700
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; SIZE: 0 kB"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; SIZE: 0 kB"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3695
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not transfer any file larger than"
msgstr "Ne prenašajte datotek, večjih od"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--max-size=SIZE</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--max-size=SIZE</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to avoid "
"transferring any file that is larger than the specified SIZE."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj se izogne "
"prenosu datotek, ki so večje od določene SIZE."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3705
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep partially transferred files"
msgstr "Ohrani delno prenesene datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3708
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--partial</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--partial</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3709
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> will delete "
"any partially transferred file if the transfer is interrupted. In some "
"circumstances it is more desirable to keep partially transferred files. "
"Using the <option>--partial</option> option tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to keep the partial file which should make "
"a subsequent transfer of the rest of the file much faster."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> privzeto "
"izbriše vse delno prenesene datoteke, če prenos je prekinjen. V nekaterih "
"okoliščinah je bolj zaželeno ohraniti delno prenesene datoteke. Uporaba "
"možnosti <option>--partial</option> pove <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, da obdržite delno datoteko, zaradi česar "
"bi moral biti kasnejši prenos preostale datoteke veliko hitrejši."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put partially transferred files into"
msgstr "Delno prenesene datoteke vstavi v"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3718
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--partial-dir=DIR</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--partial-dir=DIR</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A better way to keep partial files than the <option>--partial</option> "
"option is to specify a folder DIR that will be used to hold the partial data "
"(instead of writing it out to the destination file). On the next transfer, "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> will use a "
"file found in this folder as data to speed up the resumption of the transfer "
"and then delete it after it has served its purpose. Before you tick this "
"option, you should read the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">manual page</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Boljši način za shranjevanje delnih datotek kot možnost <option>--partial</"
"option> je, da določite mapo DIR, ki bo uporabljena za hrambo delnih "
"podatkov (namesto zapisovanja v ciljno datoteko). Pri naslednjem prenosu bo "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> uporabil "
"datoteko, ki jo najdete v tem mapo kot podatke, da pospešite nadaljevanje "
"prenosa, in jo nato izbrišite, ko je služila svojemu namenu. Preden izberete "
"to možnost, preberite <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">stran s priročnikom</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Default: not selected; DIR: <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME</filename>"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto: ni izbrano; DIR: <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME</filename>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3727 index.docbook:3968 index.docbook:4008
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Razno"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3731
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set bandwidth limit:"
msgstr "Nastavi omejitev pasovne širine:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--bwlimit=RATE</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--bwlimit=RATE</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3735
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the maximum data transfer RATE in kilobytes per second."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi največjo hitrost RATE prenosa podatkov v kilobajtih na sekundo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; RATE: 0 kB/s"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; RATE: 0 kB/s"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3748
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Deletion"
msgstr "Brisanje datoteke"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3751
#, no-c-format
msgid "Files &amp; Directories"
msgstr "Datoteke &amp; Imeniki"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3756
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove synchronized source files"
msgstr "Odstrani sinhronizirane izvorne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3759
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--remove-source-files</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--remove-source-files</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to remove from "
"the sending side the files (meaning non-directories) that are a part of the "
"transfer and have been successfully duplicated on the receiving side."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj odstrani "
"datoteke s strani pošiljatelja (kar pomeni neimeniki), ki so del prenosa in "
"so bili uspešno podvojeni na sprejemni strani."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3766
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete extraneous files"
msgstr "Izbriši odvečne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delete</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--delete</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to delete "
"extraneous files from the receiving side (ones that aren't on the sending "
"side), but only for the directories that are being synchronized. You must "
"have asked <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to send the "
"whole folder (&eg; \"<filename class=\"directory\">dir</filename>\" or "
"\"<filename class=\"directory\">dir/</filename>\") without using a wildcard "
"for the folders contents (&eg; \"<filename class=\"directory\">dir/*</"
"filename>\") since the wildcard is expanded by the shell and <ulink url="
"\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> thus gets a "
"request to transfer individual files, not the files' parent folder. Files "
"that are excluded from transfer are also excluded from being deleted unless "
"you use the <option>--delete-excluded</option> option or mark the rules as "
"only matching on the sending side."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj izbriše "
"odvečne datoteke s sprejemne strani (enih ki niso na strani pošiljatelja), "
"ampak samo za imenike, ki se sinhronizirajo. Zagotovo ste prosili <ulink url="
"\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> za pošiljanje "
"celotne mape (&eg; \"<filename class=\"directory\">dir</filename>\" ali "
"\"<filename class=\"directory\">dir/</filename>\") brez uporabe nadomestnega "
"znaka za vsebino map (&eg; \"<filename class=\"directory\">dir/*</filename>"
"\"), ker je nadomestni znak razširjen z lupino in <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum "
"></citerefentry></ulink> tako dobi zahtevo za prenos posameznih datotek, ne "
"nadrejene mape datotek. Datoteke, ki so izključene iz prenosa, so tudi "
"izključene iz brisanja, razen če uporabite možnost <option>--delete-"
"excluded</option> ali označite pravila kot ujemajoča se samo na strani "
"pošiljatelja."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3776
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete files before transfer"
msgstr "Pred prenosom izbriši datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3779
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delete-before</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--delete-before</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Request that the file deletions on the receiving side be done before the "
"transfer starts. This is the default if <option>--delete</option> or "
"<option>--delete-excluded</option> is specified without one of the <option>--"
"delete-WHEN</option> options."
msgstr ""
"Zahtevaj, da se brisanje datotek na prejemni strani izvede pred začetkom "
"prenosa. To je privzeto, če je <option>--delete</option> ali <option>--"
"delete-excluded</option> podana brez ene od možnosti <option>--delete-WHEN</"
"option>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3786
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete files after transfer"
msgstr "Izbriši datoteke po prenosu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3789
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delete-after</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--delete-after</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Request that the file deletions on the receiving side be done after the "
"transfer has completed."
msgstr ""
"Zahtevaj, da se brisanje datotek na sprejemni strani opravi po končanem "
"prenosu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3796
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete files during transfer"
msgstr "Izbriši datoteke med prenosom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3799
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delete-during</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--delete-during</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Request that the file deletions on the receiving side be done incrementally "
"as the transfer happens. This is a faster method than choosing the before- "
"or after-transfer algorithm, but it is only supported beginning with <ulink "
"url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> version 2.6.4."
msgstr ""
"Zahtevajte, da se brisanje datotek na sprejemni strani izvaja postopoma, ko "
"poteka prenos. To je hitrejša metoda kot izbira algoritma pred ali po "
"prenosu, vendar je podprta le, če se začne z <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> različica 2.6.4."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3806
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete excluded files"
msgstr "Izbriši izključene datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3809
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delete-excluded</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--delete-excluded</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to deleting the files on the receiving side that are not on the "
"sending side, this tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to also delete any files on the receiving "
"side that are excluded (see <option>--exclude</option>)."
msgstr ""
"Poleg brisanja datotek na strani prejemnika, ki niso na strani pošiljatelja, "
"to sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum> </citerefentry></ulink>, da izbriše "
"tudi vse datoteke na sprejemni strani, ki so izključene (glejte <option>--"
"exclude</option>)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3816
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete even if I/O errors occur"
msgstr "Izbriši, tudi če pride do V/I napak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3819
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--ignore-errors</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--ignore-errors</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tells <option>--delete</option> to go ahead and delete files even when there "
"are I/O errors."
msgstr ""
"Pove <option>--delete</option>, naj nadaljuje in izbriše datoteke, tudi če "
"pride do V/I napak."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Force deletion of non-void directories"
msgstr "Vsili brisanje neveljavnih imenikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3829
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--force</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--force</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to delete a non-empty folder when it is to "
"be replaced by a non-folder. This is only relevant if deletions are not "
"active (see <option>--delete</option>)."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost pove <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, da izbriše mapo, ki ni prazna, ko je "
"treba nadomestiti z ne-mapo. To je pomembno le, če brisanja niso aktivna "
"(glejte <option>--delete</option>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3838
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restrictions"
msgstr "Omejitve"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3843
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not delete more than this many files"
msgstr "Ne izbriši več kot toliko datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3846
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--max-delete=NUM</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--max-delete=NUM</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> not to delete "
"more than NUM files or directories (NUM must be non-zero). This is useful "
"when mirroring very large trees to prevent disasters."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj ne "
"izbriše več kot NUM datotek ali imenikov (NUM mora biti različna od nič). To "
"je uporabno pri zrcaljenju zelo velikih dreves za preprečevanje nesreč."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3861
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering"
msgstr "Filtriranje"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3869
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto-ignore files in the same way CVS does"
msgstr "Samodejno prezri datoteke na enak način kot CVS"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3872
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-C</option>/<option>--cvs-exclude</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-C</option>/<option>--cvs-exclude</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3873
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a useful shorthand for excluding a broad range of files that you "
"often don't want to transfer between systems. It uses the same algorithm "
"that CVS uses to determine if a file should be ignored."
msgstr ""
"To je uporabna okrajšava za izključitev širokega nabora datotek, ki jih "
"pogosto ne želite prenašati med sistemi. Uporablja isti algoritem, ki ga CVS "
"uporablja za ugotavljanje, ali naj se datoteka prezre."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3879
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exclude files matching this pattern"
msgstr "Izključi datoteke, ki se ujemajo s tem vzorcem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3882
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--exclude=PATTERN</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--exclude=PATTERN</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3883
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is a simplified form of the <option>--filter</option> option "
"that defaults to an exclude rule and does not allow the full rule-parsing "
"syntax of normal filter rules."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je poenostavljena oblika možnosti <option>--filter</option>, ki "
"je privzeto nastavljena na izključitveno pravilo in ne dovoljuje celotne "
"sintakse razčlenjevanja pravil običajnih pravil filtra."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3884 index.docbook:3904
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; PATTERN: empty"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; PATTERN: prazen"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3889
#, no-c-format
msgid "Read exclude patterns from"
msgstr "Preberi izključi vzorce iz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3892
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--exclude-from=FILE</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--exclude-from=FILE</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3893
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is related to the <option>--exclude</option> option, but it "
"specifies a FILE that contains exclude patterns (one per line). Blank lines "
"in the file and lines starting with ';' or '#' are ignored. You have to "
"choose an existing file to make this option work."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je povezana z možnostjo <option>--exclude</option>, vendar podaja "
"FILE, ki vsebuje vzorce izključitev (enega na vrstico). Prazne vrstice v "
"datoteki in vrstice, ki se začnejo z ';' ali '#' so prezrti. Za delovanje te "
"možnosti morate izbrati obstoječo datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3894
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; FILE: <filename>$HOME/exclude.txt</filename>"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; FILE: <filename>$HOME/exclude.txt</filename>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3899
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include files matching this pattern"
msgstr "Vključi datoteke, ki se ujemajo s tem vzorcem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3902
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--include=PATTERN</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--include=PATTERN</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is a simplified form of the <option>--filter</option> option "
"that defaults to an include rule and does not allow the full rule-parsing "
"syntax of normal filter rules."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je poenostavljena oblika možnosti <option>--filter</option>, ki "
"je privzeto vključeno pravilo in ne dovoljuje celotne sintakse "
"razčlenjevanja pravil običajnih pravil filtra."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3909
#, no-c-format
msgid "Read include patterns from"
msgstr "Preberite vključite vzorce iz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3912
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--include-from=FILE</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--include-from=FILE</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3913
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is related to the <option>--include</option> option, but it "
"specifies a FILE that contains include patterns (one per line). Blank lines "
"in the file and lines starting with ';' or '#' are ignored. You have to "
"choose an existing file to make this option work."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je povezana z možnostjo <option>--include</option>, vendar podaja "
"FILE, ki vsebuje vzorce vključitve (enega na vrstico). Prazne vrstice v "
"datoteki in vrstice, ki se začnejo z ';' ali '#' so prezrti. Za delovanje te "
"možnosti morate izbrati obstoječo datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3914
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; FILE: <filename>$HOME/include.txt</filename>"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; FILE: <filename>$HOME/include.txt</filename>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3921
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter Rules"
msgstr "Pravila filtra"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3926
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use --filter='dir-merge /.rsync-filter' filter rule"
msgstr "Uporabi pravilo filtra --filter='dir-merge /.rsync-filter'"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3929
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-F</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-F</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to look for per-folder <filename>.rsync-"
"filter</filename> files that have been sprinkled through the hierarchy and "
"use their rules to filter the files in the transfer."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj išče <filename> za posamezno mapo ."
"rsync-filter</filename> datoteke, ki so bile razpršene po hierarhiji in "
"uporabljajo svoja pravila za filtriranje datotek v prenosu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3931 index.docbook:3942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See the FILTER RULES section of the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">manual page</"
"ulink> for detailed information on how this option works."
msgstr ""
"Glejte razdelek FILTER RULES <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">strani s priročnikom</"
"ulink> za podrobne informacije o delovanju te možnosti."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3937
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use --filter='exclude .rsync-filter' filter rule"
msgstr "Uporabi pravilo filtra --filter='exclude .rsync-filter'"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3940
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-FF</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-FF</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option filters out the <filename>.rsync-filter</filename> files "
"themselves from the transfer."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost filtrira same datoteke <filename>.rsync-filter</filename> iz "
"prenosa."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3948
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom filter rules"
msgstr "Pravila filtra po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3951
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-f</option>/<option>--filter=RULE</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-f</option>/<option>--filter=RULE</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can define one or more filter rules here. Each rule has to be prefixed "
"with the <option>--filter=</option> or <option>-f</option> option string, "
"because the contents of the text box will be passed to the <ulink url=\"man:/"
"rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> command AS IS."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko določite eno ali več pravil filtra. Vsako pravilo mora imeti "
"predpono z nizom možnosti <option>--filter=</option> ali <option>-f</"
"option>, ker bo vsebina besedilnega polja posredovana <ulink url=\"man :/"
"rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> ukaz AS IS."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3953
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to add rules to selectively exclude certain files "
"from the list of files to be transferred. This is most useful in combination "
"with a recursive transfer."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča dodajanje pravil za selektivno izključitev določenih "
"datotek s seznama datotek za prenos. To je najbolj uporabno v kombinaciji z "
"rekurzivnim prenosom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may use as many <option>--filter</option> options as you like to build "
"up the list of files to exclude."
msgstr ""
"Za sestavo seznama datotek, ki jih želite izključiti, lahko uporabite "
"poljubno število možnosti <option>--filter</option>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3955
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See the FILTER RULES section of the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">manual page</"
"ulink> for detailed information on this option."
msgstr ""
"Glejte razdelek FILTER RULES <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\">stran s priročnikom</"
"ulink> za podrobne informacije o tej možnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3956
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; RULES: empty"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; RULES: prazno"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3971
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checksums"
msgstr "Kontrolne vsote"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3976
#, no-c-format
msgid "Force fixed checksum block size"
msgstr "Vsili fiksno velikost bloka kontrolne vsote"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3979
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-B</option>/<option>--block-size=SIZE</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-B</option>/<option>--block-size=SIZE</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3980
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This forces the block size used in the rsync algorithm to a fixed value. It "
"is normally selected based on the size of each file being updated. See the "
"<ulink url=\"http://rsync.samba.org/tech_report/\">technical report</ulink> "
"for details."
msgstr ""
"To prisili velikost bloka, uporabljenega v algoritmu rsync, na fiksno "
"vrednost. Običajno je izbran glede na velikost posamezne datoteke, ki se "
"posodablja. Za podrobnosti glejte <ulink url=\"http://rsync.samba.org/"
"tech_report/\">tehnično poročilo</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3981
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default: not selected; SIZE: 0"
msgstr "Privzeto: ni izbrano; SIZE: 0"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3986
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set block/file checksum seed"
msgstr "Nastavite seme kontrolne vsote bloka/datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3989
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--checksum-seed=NUM</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--checksum-seed=NUM</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3990
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the MD4 checksum seed to the integer NUM. This 4 byte checksum seed is "
"included in each block and file MD4 checksum calculation. By default the "
"checksum seed is generated by the server and defaults to the current time(). "
"This option is used to set a specific checksum seed, which is useful for "
"applications that want repeatable block and file checksums, or in the case "
"where the user wants a more random checksum seed. Note that setting NUM to 0 "
"causes rsync to use the default of time() for checksum seed."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite seme kontrolne vsote MD4 na celo število NUM. To 4-bajtno seme "
"kontrolne vsote je vključeno v vsak izračun kontrolne vsote bloka in "
"datoteke MD4. Privzeto seme kontrolne vsote ustvari strežnik in je privzeto "
"nastavljen na trenutni čas(). Ta možnost se uporablja za nastavitev "
"določenega semena kontrolne vsote, kar je uporabno za aplikacije, ki želijo "
"ponovljive kontrolne vsote blokov in datotek, ali v primeru, ko uporabnik "
"želi bolj naključno seme kontrolne vsote. Upoštevajte, da nastavitev NUM na "
"0 povzroči, da rsync uporabi privzeto vrednost time() za seme kontrolne "
"vsote."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:3996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skip files based on checksum"
msgstr "Preskoči datoteke na podlagi kontrolne vsote"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3999
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-c</option>/<option>--checksum</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-c</option>/<option>--checksum</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This forces the sender to checksum every regular file using a 128-bit MD4 "
"checksum. It does this during the initial file system scan as it builds the "
"list of all available files. The receiver then checksums its version of each "
"file (if it exists and it has the same size as its sender-side counterpart) "
"in order to decide which files need to be updated: files with either a "
"changed size or a changed checksum are selected for transfer. Since this "
"whole-file checksumming of all files on both sides of the connection occurs "
"in addition to the automatic checksum verifications that occur during a "
"file's transfer, this option can be quite slow."
msgstr ""
"To prisili pošiljatelja, da kontrolno vsoto vsake običajne datoteke uporabi "
"128-bitno kontrolno vsoto MD4. To stori med začetnim pregledom datotečnega "
"sistema, ko sestavi seznam vseh razpoložljivih datotek. Prejemnik nato "
"preveri svojo različico vsake datoteke (če obstaja in ima enako velikost kot "
"nasprotna stran pošiljatelja), da se odloči, katere datoteke je treba "
"posodobiti: datoteke s spremenjeno velikostjo ali spremenjeno kontrolno "
"vsoto so izbrane za prenos. Ker se ta kontrolna vsota celotne datoteke vseh "
"datotek na obeh straneh povezave pojavi poleg samodejnih preverjanj "
"kontrolne vsote, do katerih pride med prenosom datoteke, je ta možnost lahko "
"precej počasna."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:4012
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not cross file system boundaries"
msgstr "Ne prestopaj meja datotečnega sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4015
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>-x</option>/<option>--one-file-system</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>-x</option>/<option>--one-file-system</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4016
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tells <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> to avoid "
"crossing a file system boundary when recursing. This does not limit the "
"user's ability to specify items to copy from multiple file systems, just "
"<ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>'s recursion "
"through the hierarchy of each folder that the user specified, and also the "
"analogous recursion on the receiving side during deletion. Also keep in mind "
"that <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> treats a \"bind"
"\" mount to the same device as being on the same file system."
msgstr ""
"To sporoči <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink>, naj se pri "
"ponavljanju izogne prečkanju meje datotečnega sistema. To ne omejuje "
"možnosti uporabnika, da določi elemente za kopiranje iz več datotečnih "
"sistemov, samo <ulink url=\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> skozi "
"hierarhijo vsake mape, ki jo je določil uporabnik, in tudi analogna "
"rekurzija na sprejemni strani med brisanjem. Upoštevajte tudi, da <ulink url="
"\"man:/rsync\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> obravnava "
"\"povezavo\" namestitve na enaka naprava kot v istem datotečnem sistemu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:4022
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delay updates until the end of transfer"
msgstr "Odloži posodobitve do konca prenosa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4025
#, no-c-format
msgid "Option: <option>--delay-updates</option>"
msgstr "Možnost: <option>--delay-updates</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option puts the temporary file from each updated file into a holding "
"folder until the end of the transfer, at which time all the files are "
"renamed into place in rapid succession."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost postavi začasno datoteko iz vsake posodobljene datoteke v "
"zadrževalno mapo do konca prenosa, pri čemer se vse datoteke hitro "
"preimenujejo na svoje mesto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is strongly recommended that you read the <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\">manual page</ulink> before using this option."
msgstr ""
"Močno priporočamo, da pred uporabo te možnosti preberete <ulink url=\"man:/"
"rsync\">stran s priročnikom</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "Avtentikacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4044
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can enter the default login credentials. If you use profiles, they "
"are only valid for the active profile."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko vnesete privzete poverilnice za prijavo. Če uporabljate profile, "
"veljajo samo za aktivni profil."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:4047
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the \"Authentication\" configuration page"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona konfiguracijske strani \"Avtentikacija\""

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4053
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Authentication\" configuration page"
msgstr "Konfiguracijska stran \"Avtentikacija\""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All login credentials are stored in your password manager (&eg; &kwallet;, "
"GNOME Keyring or KeePassXC). To change them, you can use the <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_authentication\">password dialog</link> or "
"your password manager. To delete individual entries, you need to use your "
"password manager."
msgstr ""
"Vse poverilnice za prijavo so shranjene v vašem upravitelju gesel (&eg; "
"&kwallet; ali GNOME Keyring ali KeePassXC). Če jih želite spremeniti, lahko "
"uporabite <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_authentication"
"\">pogovorno okno za geslo</link>. Če želite izbrisati posamezne vnose, "
"uporabite upravitelja gesel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4068
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this configuration page, you can edit your bookmarks. If you use "
"profiles, only those of the active profile are shown."
msgstr ""
"Na tej konfiguracijski strani lahko urejate svoje zaznamke. Če uporabljate "
"profile, so prikazani samo tisti iz aktivnega profila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:4071
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the \"Bookmarks\" configuration page"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona konfiguracijske strani \"Zaznamki\""

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4074
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Bookmarks\" configuration page"
msgstr "Konfiguracijska stran \"Zaznamki\""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit a category or bookmark, double click it or select it and click the "
"<guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button on the righthand side. Categories can "
"directly be renamed. For bookmarks, the editor opens and you can set the "
"label, the category and the username for login as well as the workgroup or "
"domain and the ip address of its host."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti kategorijo ali zaznamek, ga dvakrat kliknite ali kliknite "
"gumb <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton> na desni strani. Kategorije je mogoče "
"neposredno preimenovati. Za zaznamke se odpre urejevalnik in lahko nastavite "
"oznako, kategorijo in uporabniško ime za prijavo ter delovno skupino ali "
"domeno in ip naslov njenega gostitelja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:4081
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the \"Bookmarks\" configuration page with open editor"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona konfiguracijske strani \"Zaznamki\" z odprtim urejevalnikom"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4084
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Bookmarks\" configuration page with open editor"
msgstr "Konfiguracijska stran \"Zaznamki\" z odprtim urejevalnikom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4088
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Categories can be added by either using the <guibutton>Add Category</"
"guibutton> button, or by entering a new category name in the editor. "
"Individual entries or the entire list can be deleted by pressing the "
"<guibutton>Remove</guibutton> or <guibutton>Clear List</guibutton> button. "
"To undo your changes, click the <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Kategorije lahko dodate z uporabo gumba <guibutton>Dodaj kategorijo</"
"guibutton> ali z vnosom novega imena kategorije v urejevalnik. Posamezne "
"vnose ali celoten seznam lahko izbrišete s pritiskom na gumb "
"<guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Počisti seznam</guibutton>. "
"Če želite razveljaviti svoje spremembe, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Ponastavi</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4089
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For further information about bookmarks, read this <link linkend=\"bookmarks"
"\">section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za dodatne informacije o zaznamkih preberite ta <link linkend=\"bookmarks"
"\">razdelek</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All servers and shares for which you defined custom settings are listed "
"here. If you use profiles, only those of the active profile are shown."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj so navedeni vsi strežniki in viri v skupni rabi, za katere ste "
"določili nastavitve po meri. Če uporabljate profile, so prikazani samo tisti "
"iz aktivnega profila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:4103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the \"Custom Settings\" configuration tab"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona konfiguracijskega zavihka »Nastavitve po meri«"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4106
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Custom Settings\" configuration tab"
msgstr "Konfiguracijski zavihek »Nastavitve po meri«"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can edit the custom settings for a network item by either double "
"clicking it or by selecting it and clicking the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> "
"button on the righthand side. The editor will then open and you can change "
"all the desired settings."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve po meri za omrežni element lahko urejate tako, da dvakrat "
"kliknete nastavitev ali pa ga izberete in kliknete gumb <guibutton>Uredi</"
"guibutton> na desni strani. Nato se odpre urejevalnik, kjer lahko spremenite "
"vse želene nastavitve."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:4113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Screenshot of the \"Custom Settings\" configuration page with open editor"
msgstr ""
"Posnetek zaslona konfiguracijske strani »Nastavitve po meri« z odprtim "
"urejevalnikom"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4116
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Custom Settings\" configuration page with open editor"
msgstr "Konfiguracijska stran »Nastavitve po meri« z odprtim urejevalnikom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove an entry, select it and click the <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> "
"button. All network items may be removed at once by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Clear List</guibutton> button. To reset your changes, click the "
"<guibutton>Reset</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti vnos, ga izberite in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Odstrani</"
"guibutton>. Vse omrežne elemente lahko naenkrat odstranite s klikom na gumb "
"<guibutton>Počisti seznam</guibutton>. Za ponastavitev sprememb kliknite "
"gumb <guibutton>Ponastavi</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For further information about custom settings, read this <link linkend="
"\"custom_settings\">section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za nadaljnje informacije o nastavitvah po meri preberite ta <link linkend="
"\"custom_settings\">razdelek</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can enable the use of profiles and manage your profiles."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani lahko omogočite uporabo profilov in upravljate svoje profile."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:4134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the \"Profiles\" configuration tab"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona konfiguracijskega zavihka »Profili«"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4137
#, no-c-format
msgid "The \"Profiles\" configuration tab"
msgstr "Konfiguracijski zavihek \"Profili\""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:4151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use profiles"
msgstr "Uporabite profile"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make Smb4K use profiles. This enables you to define different bookmarks and "
"custom settings for each profile. This is especially useful if you are using "
"a laptop in different network neighborhoods, &eg; at home and at work. When "
"enabling this setting the first time, the first entry in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_profiles_profiles\">profiles list</link> will be the "
"active profile."
msgstr ""
"Naj Smb4K uporablja profile. To vam omogoča, da za vsak profil določite "
"različne zaznamke in nastavitve po meri. To je še posebej uporabno, če "
"uporabljate prenosnik v različnih omrežnih soseščinah, &eg; doma in v "
"službi. Ko to nastavitev omogočite prvič, bo prvi vnos na <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_profiles_profiles\">seznamu profilov</link> aktivni "
"profil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can manage your profiles. By default, there are two pre-defined "
"ones (<guilabel>Home</guilabel> and <guilabel>Work</guilabel>). To add a new "
"profile, enter it into the line edit and click the <guibutton>Add</"
"guibutton> button. Entries can be deleted by selecting them and clicking the "
"<guibutton>Remove</guibutton> button. To change the order, you can use the "
"<guibutton>Move Up</guibutton> and <guibutton>Move Down</guibutton> buttons. "
"The active profile can be changed by either double clicking the profile name "
"in the list or by selecting the profile and using the <guibutton>Set Active</"
"guibutton> button. To rename a profile, select it and click the "
"<guibutton>Rename</guibutton> button. You will then be able to change the "
"name in the list widget. All settings of the renamed profile are migrated "
"automatically. To reset your changes, click the <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko upravljate svoje profile. Privzeto sta dva vnaprej določena "
"(<guilabel>Dom</guilabel> in <guilabel>Delo</guilabel>). Če želite dodati "
"nov profil, ga vnesite v vrstico za urejanje in kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>. Vnose lahko izbrišete tako, da jih izberete in "
"kliknete gumb <guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton>. Če želite spremeniti vrstni "
"red, lahko uporabite gumba <guibutton>Premakni gor</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>Premakni dol</guibutton>. Aktivni profil lahko spremenite tako, "
"da dvokliknete ime profila na seznamu ali izberete profil in uporabite gumb "
"<guibutton>Nastavi za aktivno</guibutton>. Če želite preimenovati profil, ga "
"izberite in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Preimenuj</guibutton>. Nato boste lahko "
"spremenili ime v gradniku seznama. Vse nastavitve preimenovanega profila se "
"samodejno preselijo. Za ponastavitev sprememb kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Ponastavi</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For further information about profiles, read this <link linkend=\"profiles"
"\">section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za dodatne informacije o profilih preberite ta <link linkend=\"profiles"
"\">razdelek</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4179
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4186
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Profiles</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Profili</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the profile to use. This menu entry is disabled if the user did not "
"enabled the use of profiles."
msgstr ""
"Izberi profil, ki ga želite uporabiti. Ta menijski vnos je onemogočen, če "
"uporabnik ni omogočil uporabe profilov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Two profiles are predefined:"
msgstr "Prednastavljena sta dva profila:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Profiles</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Home</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Profili</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Domov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4209
#, no-c-format
msgid "A profile for use at home"
msgstr "Profil za uporabo doma"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Profiles</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Work</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Profili</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Delo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4221
#, no-c-format
msgid "A profile for use at work"
msgstr "Profil za uporabo pri delu"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &smb4k;."
msgstr "Zapri &smb4k;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4247
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Network Menu"
msgstr "Meni omrežja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Network</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Scan Network|Workgroup|Computer</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Skeniraj omrežje|Delovna skupina|Računalnik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scan the whole network neighborhood, the highlighted workgroup/domain or "
"computer for new entries. This action is visible by default and will be "
"replaced by the <guimenuitem>Abort</guimenuitem> action if a network scan is "
"running."
msgstr ""
"Preglejte celotno omrežno soseščino, označeno delovno skupino/domeno ali "
"računalnik za nove vnose. To dejanje je privzeto vidno in ga bo nadomestilo "
"dejanje <guimenuitem>Prekini</guimenuitem>, če se izvaja skeniranje omrežja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Network</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Abort</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prekini</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Abort any running process of the network neighborhood browser. This action "
"is invisible by default and will only be visible instead of the "
"<guimenuitem>Scan Network|Workgroup|Computer</guimenuitem> action when a "
"network scan is running."
msgstr ""
"Prekinite kateri koli tekoči proces brskalnika omrežne soseščine. To dejanje "
"je privzeto nevidno in bo vidno samo namesto dejanja <guimenuitem>Skeniraj "
"omrežje|Delovna skupina|Računalnik</guimenuitem>, ko se izvaja skeniranje "
"omrežja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Network</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Search</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Iskanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the search tool bar in the network neighborhood browser."
msgstr "Odpri iskalno orodno vrstico v brskalniku omrežne soseščine."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4288
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Network</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj zaznamek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a bookmark to the currently selected remote share. This action is "
"disabled if no share is selected. Read the <link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding"
"\">Adding Bookmarks</link> section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte zaznamek v trenutno izbrano oddaljen skupni disk. To dejanje je "
"onemogočeno, če ni izbranega nobenega skupnega diska. Za več podrobnosti "
"preberite razdelek <link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding\">Dodajanje zaznamkov</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Network</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Custom Settings</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj nastavitve po meri</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_defining_custom_settings\">Custom Settings</"
"link> editor. You can set several custom settings for the selected server or "
"share. If a workgroup or no item is selected, this menu entry is disabled. "
"Read the <link linkend=\"custom_settings_adding\">Adding Custom Settings</"
"link> section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Odprite urejevalnik <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_defining_custom_settings\">Nastavitve po "
"meri</link>. Za izbrani strežnik ali skupni vir lahko nastavite več "
"nastavitev po meri. Če ni izbrana delovna skupina ali noben element, je ta "
"vnos v meniju onemogočen. Za več podrobnosti preberite razdelek <link "
"linkend=\"custom_settings_adding\">Dodajanje nastavitev po meri</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Network</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Mount Dialog</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri pogovorno okno za "
"priklop</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_mounting\">dialog</"
"link> for mounting shares \"manually\". This feature may be needed if "
"&smb4k; cannot find a server from which you want to mount a certain shared "
"resource."
msgstr ""
"Odprite <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_mounting\">pogovorno "
"okno</link> za \"ročno\" nameščanje skupnih virov. Ta funkcija bo morda "
"potrebna, če &smb4k; ne najde strežnika, s katerega želite priklopiti "
"določen skupni vir."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Network</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Authentication</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Avtentikacija</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_authentication"
"\">authentication dialog</link>. You can provide the login and password for "
"the selected server or share. If a workgroup or no item is selected, this "
"action is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Odpri <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_authentication"
"\">pogovorno okno za preverjanje pristnosti</link>. Vnesete lahko prijavo in "
"geslo za izbrani strežnik ali skupni vir. Če ni izbrana delovna skupina ali "
"noben element, je to dejanje onemogočeno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Network</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_previewing\">Preview</link> the "
"contents of the selected remote share. This action is only enabled if a "
"share is selected. Printer shares cannot be previewed."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_previewing\">Predogled</link> "
"vsebine izbrane oddaljenega skupnega vira. To dejanje je omogočeno le, če je "
"izbran skupni vir. Skupnih tiskalnikov ni mogoče ogledovati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Network</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print File</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni datoteko</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_printing\">Print</link> a file "
"on a remote printer. This action is only available if a printer share is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_printing\">Natisni</link> "
"datoteko na oddaljenem tiskalniku. To dejanje je na voljo samo, če je izbran "
"skupni tiskalnik."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>M</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Network</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mount</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>M</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Namestitev</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mount the selected remote share. By default and if you clicked anything "
"different than a share with type \"Disk\" or \"IPC\", this action is "
"disabled. If you selected a mounted share, this action is replaced by the "
"<guimenuitem>Unmount</guimenuitem> action."
msgstr ""
"Priklopi izbrani oddaljeni skupni vir. Privzeto in če ste kliknili kaj "
"drugega kot skupno rabo z vrsto »Disk« ali »IPC«, je to dejanje onemogočeno. "
"Če ste izbrali priklopljeni skupni vir, se to dejanje nadomesti z dejanjem "
"<guimenuitem>Odklopi</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Network</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Unmount</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Omrežje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odklopi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4389
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Shares Menu"
msgstr "Meni Skupni diski"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4394
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Shares</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View Modes</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Skupni diski</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Načini pogleda</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Shares</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View Modes</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Icon View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Skupni diski</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Načini pogleda</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pogled ikon</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Shares</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View Modes</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>List View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Skupni diski</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Načini pogleda</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pogled seznama</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Shares</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Unmount</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Skupni viri</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odklopi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&smb4k; provides the ability to force unmounting of shares (&Linux; only). "
"This can be useful for inaccessible shares that cannot be unmounted in the "
"normal way. To enable this feature, you need to modify the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior\">settings</link> in "
"the configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"&smb4k; omogoča prisilni odklop skupnih virov (samo &Linux;). To je lahko "
"uporabno za nedostopne skupne vire, ki jih ni mogoče odklopiti na običajen "
"način. Če želite omogočiti to zmožnost, morate spremeniti <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior\">nastavitve</link> v "
"pogovornem oknu kofiguracije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Shares</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Unmount All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Skupni vir</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odklopi vse</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unmount all shares at once. The restrictions noted above also apply here. If "
"you do not have any shares mounted, this button is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Odklopi vse skupne vire hkrati. Zgoraj navedene omejitve veljajo tudi tukaj. "
"Če nimate priklopljenih nobenih skupnih virov, je ta gumb onemogočen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4457
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Shares</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Skupni disk</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj zaznamek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a bookmark to the currently selected mounted share. This action is "
"disabled if no share is selected. Read the <link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding"
"\">Adding Bookmarks</link> section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte zaznamek v trenutno izbran priklopljen skupni vir. To dejanje je "
"onemogočeno, če ni izbran noben skupni vir. Za več podrobnosti preberite "
"razdelek <link linkend=\"bookmarks_adding\">Dodajanje zaznamkov</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Shares</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Custom Settings</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Skupni disk</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj nastavitve po "
"meri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_defining_custom_settings\">Custom Settings</"
"link> editor. You can set several custom settings for the selected share. "
"Read the <link linkend=\"custom_settings_adding\">Adding Custom Settings</"
"link> section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Odpri urejevalnik <link linkend="
"\"network_neighborhood_browser_defining_custom_settings\">Nastavitve po "
"meri</link>. Za izbran skupni disk lahko nastavite več nastavitev po meri. "
"Za več podrobnosti preberite razdelek <link linkend=\"custom_settings_adding"
"\">Dodajanje nastavitev po meri</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Shares</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Synchronize</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Skupni diski</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sinhroniziraj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start the <link linkend=\"shares_view_synchronization\">synchronization</"
"link> of a share with a local copy or vice versa. This menu entry is only "
"enabled if you installed the program <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> and a share is selected."
msgstr ""
"Začnite <link linkend=\"shares_view_synchronization\">sinhronizacijo</link> "
"skupnega diska z lokalno kopijo ali obratno. Ta vnos v meniju je omogočen "
"le, če ste namestili program <ulink url=\"man:/rsync"
"\"><citerefentry><refentrytitle>rsync</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry></ulink> in izbran je skupni disk."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Shares</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open with Konsole</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Skupni disk</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri s Konsole</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the base folder of the selected share in &konsole;."
msgstr "Odprite osnovno mapo izbranega skupnega diska v &konsole;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Shares</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open with File Manager</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Skupni disk</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri z upravljalnikom "
"datotek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the contents of the selected share in the default file manager (&eg; "
"&dolphin;)."
msgstr ""
"Odpri vsebino izbranega skupnega diska v privzetem upravljalniku datotek "
"(&eg; &dolphin;)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4522
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bookmarks Menu"
msgstr "Meni z zaznamki"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4527
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit Bookmarks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Urejanje zaznamkov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <link linkend=\"bookmarks_editor\">bookmark editor</link>. This "
"action is disabled if there are no bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"Odpri <link linkend=\"bookmarks_editor\">urejevalnik zaznamkov</link>. To "
"dejanje je onemogočeno, če ni zaznamkov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:4538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj zaznamek</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add one or several bookmarks. At least one share has to be selected to "
"enable this action."
msgstr ""
"Dodaj enega ali več zaznamkov. Za omogočanje tega dejanja mora biti izbran "
"vsaj en skupni disk."

