msgstr "Odpri konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4648
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &smb4k; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu "
"items, for more information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; "
"Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &smb4k; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelek o <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">meniju Pomoč</ulink> programa &kde; "
"Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reporting Bugs"
msgstr "Poročanje o napakah"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before filing a bug report, please try the <ulink url=\"https://sourceforge."
"net/projects/smb4k/files/\">latest version</ulink> of &smb4k;. Maybe your "
"problem has already been fixed."
msgstr ""
"Preden oddate poročilo o napaki, poskusite <ulink url=\"https://sourceforge."
"net/projects/smb4k/files/\">najnovejšo različico</ulink> &smb4k;. Morda je "
"vaša težava že odpravljena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4662
#, no-c-format
msgid "Follow these directions for your bug report:"
msgstr "Sledite tem navodilom za poročilo o napaki:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Describe <emphasis>in detail</emphasis> what you did to receive the problem "
"you are reporting."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Podrobno</emphasis> opišite, kaj ste storili, da ste prejeli "
"težavo, ki jo prijavljate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4665
#, no-c-format
msgid "Provide the version of &smb4k; and &kde-frameworks;."
msgstr "Navedite različico &smb4k; in &kde-frameworks;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mention your operating system (&Linux;, FreeBSD, &etc;) and the distribution "
"that is running on your computer."
msgstr ""
"Omenite svoj operacijski sistem (&Linux;, FreeBSD &etc;) in distribucijo, ki "
"se izvaja v vašem računalniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4667
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include the full error message if an error dialog was displayed."
msgstr ""
"Vključite celotno sporočilo o napaki, če je bilo prikazano pogovorno okno o "
"napaki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you experienced a crash, attach a full backtrace. For this it is "
"recommended that you (re-)compile &smb4k; with debugging symbols. How this "
"is done is mentioned in the <filename>README.md</filename> file shipped in "
"the sources."
msgstr ""
"Če ste doživeli sesutje, priložite celotno povratno sled. Za to je "
"priporočljivo, da (ponovno) prevedete &smb4k; s simboli za odpravljanje "
"napak. Kako se to naredi, je omenjeno v datoteki <filename>README.md</"
"filename>, poslani v virih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add additional data, &eg; send a screen shot if you are reporting a &GUI; "
"related problem."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte dodatne podatke, &eg; pošljite posnetek zaslona, če poročate o &GUI; "
"povezani težavi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The recommended method to report a bug is to use the dialog that opens when "
"you click the <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Report Bug...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. But you can also go directly to the "
"<ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=Smb4k&amp;"
"format=guided\">KDE Bugtracking System</ulink> and fill out the form."
msgstr ""
"Priporočena metoda za prijavo napake je uporaba pogovornega okna, ki se "
"odpre, ko kliknete menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prijavi napako ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Lahko pa "
"greste tudi neposredno na <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/enter_bug.cgi?"
"product=Smb4k&amp;format=guided\">sistem za sledenje napakam KDE</ulink> in "
"izpolnite obrazec."

