"Tudi velik \"Hvala!\" gre k Rashidu N. Achilovu <email>shelton@sentry.granch."
"ru</email>, ki nas je prepričal, da prenesemo &smb4k; v FreeBSD in nam zelo "
"pomagal pri doseganju tega cilja."

