#~ msgid "Directories"
#~ msgstr "Imeniki"

#~ msgid "Mount prefix"
#~ msgstr "Predpona priklopa"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "This is the base folder (mount prefix) where &smb4k; will mount the "
#~ "remote shares. It can be changed by using the &URL; requester (Click the "
#~ "button with the folder icon.) or by directly entering the new path into "
#~ "the text box. Path variables like <envar>$HOME</envar> are recognized."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "To je osnovna mapa (predpona za priklop), kjer bo &smb4k; namestil "
#~ "oddaljene skupne diske. Spremenite ga lahko z &URL; zahtevnik (Kliknite "
#~ "gumb z ikono mape.) ali z neposrednim vnosom nove poti v besedilno polje. "
#~ "Spremenljivke poti, kot je <envar>$HOME</envar>, so prepoznane."

