#~ msgid "Force SMB protocol version 1.0 for workgroup and domain lookups"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Vsili protokol SMB različice 1.0 za iskanje delovne skupine in domene"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Select this option as a last resort, because the SMB protocol version 1.0 "
#~ "is unsafe and has been disabled in newer &Samba; and &Windows; versions. "
#~ "However, if you have trouble discovering workgroups and domains in your "
#~ "network neighborhood, you might want to consider switching this setting "
#~ "on. If you are using DNS Service Discovery (DNS-SD) or Web Services "
#~ "Dynamic Discovery (WS-Discovery), and those are working for you, you do "
#~ "not need version 1.0."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "To možnost izberite kot zadnjo možnost, ker protokol SMB različice 1.0 ni "
#~ "varen in je bil onemogočen v novejših &Samba; in &Windows; različicah. Če "
#~ "pa imate težave pri odkrivanju delovnih skupin in domen v vaši omrežni "
#~ "soseščini, razmislite o vklopu te nastavitve. Če uporabljate DNS Service "
#~ "Discovery (DNS-SD) ali Web Services Dynamic Discovery (WS-Discovery) in "
#~ "delujeta za vas, ne potrebujete različice 1.0."

